var book = {
	"name": "Jenesis",
	"numChapters": 50,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha kaba mynnyngkong U Blei u la thaw ïa ka bneng bad ïa ka khyndew.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ka pyrthei ka la long kaba khlem dur bad kaba suda, bad ka jingdum ka la long halor ka khmat ka jingjylliew, bad U Mynsiem U Blei u da khih halor ki um.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad U Blei u la ong, “To long ka jingshai”, bad ka jingshai ka la long.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad U Blei u la ïohi ïa kata ka jingshai, ba ka la long ka babha; bad U Blei u la pynïakhlad ïa kata ka jingshai na kata ka jingdum.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te U Blei u la khot “Ka Sngi” ïa kata ka jingshai, bad ïa kata ka jingdum u la khot “Ka Miet”. Bad kaba la janmiet ka la long bad ka step ruh ka la long, kawei ka sngi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te U Blei u la ong, “To long ka suiñbneng hapdeng kita ki um, bad to ai ba kan pynkhlad ïa ki um na ki um.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad U Blei u la pynlong ïa ka suiñbneng, bad u la pynkhlad ïa kita ki um kiba hapoh kata ka suiñbneng na kita ki um kiba halor kata ka suiñbneng; te ka long kumta keiñ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ïa kata ka suiñbneng, U Blei u la khot “Ka Bneng”. Bad kaba la janmiet ka la long, bad ka step ka la long, ka sngi ka ba-ar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Blei u la ong ruh, “To long ba kin ïalang sha kawei ka jaka kita ki um kiba hapoh ka bneng, bad to ai kan paw ka ryngkew:” te ka la long kumta keiñ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ïa kata ka ryngkew, U Blei u la khot “Ka Khyndew”, bad ïa kata ka jingïalang ki um u la khot “Ki Duriaw”; bad U Blei u la ïohi ba ka la long ka babha.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Blei u la ong ruh, “To long ba ka khyndew kan pynmih speh, ba ki jhur kin pynsei symbai, bad ba ki dieng soh kin sei soh ha la ka jaid ka jaid, kiba don la u symbai hapoh jong ki, halor ka khyndew.” Te ka la long kumta keiñ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kumta te ka khyndew ka la pynmih speh, bad ki jhur ruh ki la pynmih symbai ha la ka jaid ka jaid, bad ki dieng soh kiba pynsei soh ha la ka jaid ka jaid, kiba don la u symbai hapoh jong ki; te U Blei u la ïohi ba ka la long ka babha.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te kaba la janmiet ka la long, bad ka step ka la long, ka balai ka sngi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Blei u la ong ruh, “To long ki jingshai ha ka sahit bneng ban pynïakhlad hapdeng ka sngi bad ka miet; bad to ai ba kin long ïa ki dak, bad ïa ki aïom, bad ïa ki sngi, bad ïa ki snem de:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad to ai ba kin long ki jingshai ha kata ka sahit ki bneng ïa ka ban pynshai ha ka pyrthei:” te ka la long kumta ruh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad U Blei u la pynlong ïa ki ar tylli ki jingshai kiba khraw; ïa kata kaba kham khraw ïa ka ban synshar ïa kaba mynsngi, bad ïa kata kaba kham rit ïa ka ban synshar ïa kaba mynmiet: bad u la thaw ïa ki khlur ruh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad U Blei u la buh ïa ki ha kata ka sahit bneng ïa ka ban pynshai ha ka pyrthei,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ïa ka ban synshar ïa kaba mynsngi bad ïa kaba mynmiet, bad ïa ka ban pynkhlad ïa ka jingshai na ka jingdum: te U Blei u la ïohi ba ka long ka babha.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad kaba la janmiet ka la long, bad ka step ruh ka la long, ha ka sngi ka basaw.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad U Blei u la ong ruh, “To ai ba ki um kin ïaboi da kiei kiei ki kynja ba-im bapar, bad to ai ba kiei kiei ki kynja baher kin ïaher ha khmat ka sahit bneng.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te U Blei u la thaw ïa kita ki dohkha khraw kiba heh, bad ïa ki kynja ba-im bapar baroh, da kiba kita ki um ki la ïaboi, ha la ka jaid ka jaid, bad ïa kiei kiei ki kynja baher ruh de ha la ka jaid ka jaid: te U Blei u la ïohi ba ka la long ka babha.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad U Blei u la kyrkhu ïa ki, u da ong, “To da nang kha, bad to da nang roi, bad to da pyndap ruh ïa kita ki um ha ki duriaw, bad to ai ba kiei kiei ruh ki kynja baher kin ïa nang roi ha ka khyndew.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te kaba la janmiet ka la long, bad ka step ruh ka la long, ha ka sngi ka basan.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U Blei u la ong ruh, “To ai ba ka khyndew kan pynmih noh ïa kiei kiei ruh ki kynja ba-im baroh ha la ka jaid ka jaid, ïa ki jingri, bad ïa kiei kiei ruh ki kynja bapar, bad ïa u mrad khlaw jong ka ryngkew ha la ka jaid ka jaid:” te ka la long kumta keiñ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kumta U Blei u la thaw ïa u mrad ka ryngkew ha la ka jaid ka jaid, bad ïa ki jingri ha la ka jaid ka jaid, bad ïa kiei kiei ruh ki kynja bapar baroh ha ka khyndew ha la ka jaid ka jaid: te U Blei u la ïohi ba ka la long ka babha.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U Blei u la ong ruh, “To ngin ïathaw ïa u briew ha ka dur jong ngi, katba kum ka jingsyriem jong ngi hi; bad kin synshar halor ki dohkha ka duriaw, bad halor ki sim bneng, bad halor ki kynja mrad, bad halor ka pyrthei baroh, bad halor kiei kiei ki kynja bapar baroh ki bapar halor ka khyndew.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kumta U Blei u la thaw ïa u briew ha ka dur jong u hi, ha ka dur U Blei keiñ u la thaw ïa u; shynrang bad kynthei u la thaw ïa ki.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U Blei u la kyrkhu ruh ïa ki, bad U Blei u la ong ha ki, “To da nang kha, bad to da nang roi, bad to da pyndap ïa ka khyndew, bad to da pyndem ngon ïa ka: bad to synshar halor ki dohkha ka duriaw, bad halor ki sim bneng, bad halor kiei kiei ki kynja ba-im baroh bapar halor ka khyndew.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U Blei u la ong ruh, “Ha khmih, nga la ai ha phi, ban long ka jingbam, ïa u jhur baroh uba pynmih symbai, uba don halor ka khmat ka khyndew baroh, bad ïa u dieng baroh, uba don ha lade u soh jong u dieng uba pynmih symbai.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad ha u kynja mrad baroh jong ka khyndew, bad ha ki kynja baher baroh jong ka suiñbneng, bad ha ki kynja bapar baroh halor ka khyndew, ba don ka jingim ha ki, nga la ai ïa u jhur bajyrngam baroh ban long jingbam:” bad ka la long kumta ruh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hadien kata, U Blei u la ïohi ïa kiei kiei baroh ba u la lah thaw, ha khmih ruh, ka la bha eh. Te kaba la janmiet ka la long, bad kaba mynstep ruh ka la long, ha ka sngi ka bahynriew."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kumta la pyndep noh ïa ki bneng bad ïa ka pyrthei, bad ïa ki kynhun bah baroh jong ki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ha ka bahynñiew ka sngi, U Blei u la pyndep noh ïa la ka kam ïa kaba u la lah pynlong; bad ha ka bahynñiew ka sngi u la shong sngi na ka kam jong u baroh ïa kaba u la lah pynlong.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad U Blei u la kyrkhu ïa kata ka bahynñiew ka sngi, bad u la kyntang khuid ïa ka: naba ha kane ka sngi u la shong sngi na ka kam jong u baroh ïa kaba U Blei u la lah pynlong bad thaw.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kane ka long ka jingïathuhkhana shaphang ki bneng bad ka pyrthei, mynba la pynlong ïa ki ha kata ka sngi ba U Trai uba U Blei u la thaw ïa ka pyrthei bad ïa ki bneng,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ïa ki jingthung baroh jong ka lyngkha mynba kim pat la long ha ka khyndew, bad ïa u jhur baroh jong ka lyngkha mynba um pat la mih speh: naba U Trai uba U Blei um pat shym la pynhiar ïa u slap halor ka khyndew, bad haba u briew ruh um pat la don ïa ka ban rep ïa ka khyndew.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u lyoh u la mih na ka khyndew, bad u la ai um halor ka khmat ka khyndew baroh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad U Trai uba U Blei u la thaw ïa u briew na ka 'dewmet ka khyndew, bad u la pyrsad ha ki thliew khmut jong u ïa ka jingpyrsad ka jingim; bad uta u briew u la long ka mynsiem ba-im.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Trai uba U Blei ruh u la thung ïa ka kper ha ka Eden shaphang mihngi; bad u la buh hangta ïa uta u briew ïa uba u la lah thaw.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad U Trai uba U Blei u la pynlong ba kin mih na kata ka khyndew ki dieng baroh kiba itynnad ban khmih, bad kiba bit eh ïa ka ban bam; bad hapdeng kata ka kper ïa u dieng ka jingim, bad ïa u dieng ka jingtip ïa ka babha bad ïa ka basniew.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ka wah ruh ka la mih noh na Eden ïa ka ban ai um ïa kata ka kper; bad nangta ka la khlad, bad ka la long saw tnat.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka kyrteng jong ka banyngkong ka long “Ka Pison”: kata kaba tuid sawdong ïa ka ri Habilah baroh kawei, ha kaba don ka ksiar;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad ka ksiar jong kata ka ri ka long ka babha: hangta ruh don u Bdellium bad u mawlynnai Oniks.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ka kyrteng ka wah ka ba-ar ka long “Ka Gihon”: kata kaba tuid sawdong ïa ka ri Kush baroh kawei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ka kyrteng ka wah ka balai ka long “Ka Hidekel”: kata kaba tuid shaphang mihngi ïa ka ri Assyria. Bad ka wah ka basaw ka long “Ka Ïuphratis”.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad U Trai uba U Blei u la shim ïa uta u briew, bad u la buh ïa u ha ka kper Eden ïa ka ban trei bad ban sumar ïa ka.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad U Trai uba U Blei u la hukum ïa uta u briew, u da ong, “Na u dieng baroh ha ka kper, da kaba bam me lah ban bam ei:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> hynrei, na u dieng ka jingtip ïa ka babha bad ïa ka basniew men ym ïoh bam na u: naba ha kata ka sngi ba men bam na u, da kaba ïap men ïap shisha.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad U Trai uba U Blei u la ong ruh, “Ym bit ba uta u briew un sah marwei; ngan thaw ïa u ka nongsumar lem kaba biang.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad U Trai uba U Blei u la pynlong na ka khyndew ïa ki mrad ka ryngkew baroh, bad ïa ki sim bneng baroh; bad u la wallam ïa ki ha u Adam ban khmih kumno un buh kyrteng ïa ki: bad kat kumba uta u briew u la buh kyrteng ïa kita ki kynja ba-im baroh, kumta hi ka la long ka kyrteng jong ki.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Adam u la buh kyrteng ha ki kynja jingri baroh, bad ha ki sim bneng, bad ha ki mrad baroh jong ka khyndew; hynrei, ïa u Adam ym pat shym la shem ïa ka nongsumar lem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te U Trai uba U Blei u la pynngat ha u Adam da ka jingsamthiah kaba jur, u ruh u la ïohthiah: bad u la shim ïa kawei na ki shyieng krung jong u, bad u la set pat da ka doh ha ka jaka jong ka;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> te U Trai uba U Blei u la pynlong ka briew, na kata ka shyieng krung ïa kaba u la lah shim na uta u briew, bad u la wallam ïa ka ha uta u briew.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u Adam u la ong, “Kane mynta shisha ka long ka shyieng na ki shyieng jong nga, bad ka doh na ka doh jong nga: ïa kane keiñ yn khot ‘Ka Briew,’ namar ba la shim ïa ka na u Briew.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Namar kata keiñ, u briew un iehnoh ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ka kmie, bad un ïaineh bad la ka tnga: bad kin ïalong ruh kawei ka doh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ki la long kiba lyngkhuit baroh ar ngut, uta u briew bad ka tnga jong u, bad kim shym la sngewlehrain."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te uta u bseiñ u la long uba kham sian ïa ki mrad baroh ka ryngkew ïa kiba U Trai uba U Blei u la lah thaw. Bad u la ong ha kata ka briew, “Shisha ka long kumta, ba U Blei u la ong, ‘Phin ym ïoh bam na u dieng baroh ha ka kper?’ ”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad kata ka briew ka la ong ha uta u bseiñ, “Na u soh ki dieng ha ka kper ngi ïoh ban bam:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> hynrei, na u soh jong uta u dieng uba hapdeng ka kper, U Blei u la ong, ‘Phin ym ïoh bam na u, lymne ktah ïa u, ba ïoh phin ïap noh.’ ”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te uta u bseiñ u la ong ha kata ka briew, “Phin ym ïap noh shisha:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namar U Blei u tip, ba ha kata ka sngi ba phin bam na u, un sa pynpeit ïa ki khmat jong phi, bad ba phin long kum ki blei, kiba tip ïa ka babha bad ïa ka basniew.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba kata ka briew ka la ïohi ba uta u dieng u la long u babha ban bam, bad uba itynnad ïa ki khmat, bad u dieng uba bit ïa ka ban pynstad, ka la shim na u soh jong u, bad ka la bam ruh, bad ka la ai lem ruh de ha la u tnga; u ruh u la bam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hadien kata, la pynpeit ïa ki khmat jong ki baroh ar ngut bad ki la tip ba ki la long kiba lyngkhuit; bad ki la ïasuh lang ïa ki sla u dieng Dumbur, bad ki la ïathaw ïa lade ïa ki jingpanpoh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ki la ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa U Trai uba U Blei ba u da wan ïaid ha ka kper ha ka jingpyngngad ka sngi: te u Adam bad ka tnga jong u ki la ïabuhrieh ïa lade na khmat U Trai uba U Blei hapdeng ki dieng jong kata ka kper.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te U Trai uba U Blei u la khot ïa u Adam, bad u da ong ha u, “Me don shaei?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U te u la ong, “Nga la ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa jong me ha ka kper, nga te nga la sheptieng, naba nga la lyngkhuit; bad nga la buhrieh ïa lade.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad U Blei u la ong, “Uei ba la ïathuh ha me ba me la lyngkhuit? Shisha me la bam na uta u dieng ïa uba nga la adong ïa me ban ym bam na u?”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Adam u la ïathuh, “Kata ka briew ïa kaba me la buh lok bad nga, ka long ma ka keiñ kaba la ai ha nga na uta u dieng, bad nga la kum bam.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te U Trai uba U Blei u la ong ha kata ka briew, “Kaei kane ïa kaba pha la leh?” Te kata ka briew ka la ïathuh, “Uta u bseiñ u la shukor ïa nga; nga ruh nga la kum bam.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hadien kata, U Trai U Blei u la ong ha uta u bseiñ, “Namar ba me la leh ïa kane, la tim ïa me nalor ki kynja jingri baroh, bad nalor ki kynja mrad ka ryngkew baroh; da ka kpoh jong me men par, bad ïa ka 'dewmet men bam baroh ki sngi ka rta jong me.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ïa ka jingshun ruh ngan buh hapdeng jong me bad kata ka briew, bad hapdeng u symbai jong me bad u symbai jong ka; u symbai jong ka un pynlwet ïa ka khlieh jong me, bad me men pynlwet ïa ka khongdong'jat jong u.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ha kata ka briew u la ong, “Da kaba pynroi ngan pynroi ïa ki jingpang jong pha, bad ïa ka jingseng khun jong pha; ha ka jingshitom phan kha ki khun; bad ka jingkwah jong pha kan long sha u tnga jong pha, bad u un synshar halor jong pha.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ha u Adam u la ong, “Namar ba me la shahshkor ïa ka ktien ka tnga jong me, bad ba me la bam na uta u dieng, ïa uba nga la adong ïa me, da kaba ong, ‘Men ym bam na u:’ ïa ka khyndew la tim na ka bynta jong me; da ka jingshitom men bam na ka baroh ki sngi ka rta jong me;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> kan pynmih shylluit ruh ïa ki shiah bad ïa ki shiah keng ïa me; bad men bam ïa u jhur ka lyngkha.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Da ka jingsyep ka khmat jong me men bam ïa la u kpu, haduh ban da men phai dien pat sha ka khyndew; namar na ka la shim ïa me: naba ka 'dewmet me long, bad sha ka 'dewmet men leit phai pat.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Adam u la khot kyrteng ïa la ka tnga, “Ka Im”; naba la long ma ka, ka kmie jong ki ba-im baroh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ïa u Adam ruh bad ïa ka tnga jong u, U Trai uba U Blei u la thaw ïa ki jingkup snieh, bad u la pynkup ruh ïa ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Trai uba U Blei u la ong ruh, “Ha khmih, uta u briew u la wan long kum uwei na ngi hi, kat ban tip ïa ka babha bad ïa ka basniew: te mynta, ba ïoh un kner ïa la ka kti, bad shim ruh na u dieng ka jingim, bad bam, bad im junom ruh de:”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> namar kata, U Trai uba U Blei u la beh noh ïa u na ka kper Eden, ïa ka ban rep ïa ka khyndew na kaba la shim ïa u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kumta keiñ u la beh noh ïa uta u briew; bad u la buh ïa ki Kherub shaphang mihngi ka kper Eden, bad ïa kaba kum ka waitlam baphyrnai, kaba da khih talain baroh sawdong, ïa ka ban sumar ïa ka lynti sha uta u dieng ka jingim."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Adam u la ithuh ïa ka Im ka tnga jong u; bad ka la punkhun, bad ka la kha ïa u Kain, bad ka la ong, “Nga la ïoh ïa u briew na U Trai.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ka la nang kha pat sa ïa u Abel u para jong u; bad u Abel u la long u nongri langbrot, bad u Kain u la long u nongrep ïa ka khyndew.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ka la jia te ynda la kham bun sngi, ba u Kain u la wallam na u soh ka khyndew ban long ka jingainguh ïa U Trai.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Abel ruh, u la wallam na kiba la kha nyngkong ka kynhun jong u, bad na kiba kham sngaid na ki ruh. Te U Trai u la khmih hun ha u Abel bad ha ka jingainguh jong u:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> hynrei, ha u Kain bad ha ka jingainguh jong u, um shym la khmih hun keiñ. Te u Kain u la sngewbitar eh bad ka khmat jong u ka la noh liaw.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Kain, “Balei ba me la sngewbitar? bad na ka balei ba la noh liaw ka khmat jong me?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Lada me la leh bha, ym lah ma me? bad lada mem leh bha, ka pop ka shong lyngngeit ha ka jingkhang: bad sha me pleng kan long ka jingkwah jong ka, bad me ruh men synshar halor jong ka.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Kain u la kren ha u Abel u para jong u: te ka la jia, mynba ki la ïadon ha ka lyngkha, ba u Kain u la ïeng ban ïaleh ïa u Abel u para jong u, bad u la pynïap ïa u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Kain, “Shaei u Abel u para jong me?” U te u la ïathuh, “Ngam tip: nga long ma nga u nongsumar ïa u para jong nga mo?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Trai u la ong te, “Me la leh aïu? Ka jingud ka snam u para jong me ka kyang ha nga na ka khyndew.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad mynta keiñ me long ïa uba la tim na kata ka khyndew, kaba la ang ïa la ka shyntur ïa ka ban pdiang ïa ka snam u para jong me na ka kti jong me.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Haba me rep ïa ka khyndew, kan ym sei ïa la ka bor shuh ïa me; me hi ruh men long u nongïaidwir bad u nongphet ïap ha ka pyrthei.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Kain u la ong ha U Trai, “Ka jingpynshitom jong nga ka kham khraw ïa kaba nga lah ban shah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ha khmih, me la beh noh ïa nga ha kane ka sngi na khmat kane ka khyndew; bad na ka khmat jong me ruh yn buhrieh ïa nga; ngan long ruh u nongïaidwir bad u nongphet ïap ha ka pyrthei; kan jia ruh ba jar uba ïoh shem ïa nga un pynïap noh ïa nga.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u, “Mano mano ruh namar kata ba pynïap ïa u Kain, yn sa pynhiar kput halor jong u hynñiew shah.” Te U Trai u la buh ka dak ha u Kain, ba ïoh pynïap noh mano mano ruh ïa u haba ïoh shem ïa u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, u Kain u la leit noh na khmat U Trai bad u la shong duh ha ka ri Nod, shaphang mihngi na ka kper Eden.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Kain de u la ithuh ïa la ka tnga; bad ka la punkhun, bad ka la kha ïa u Enokh: te u dang thaw ïa ka nongbah, bad u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka nongbah ha ka kyrteng “u Enokh”, u khun jong u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ïa u Enokh la kha ïa u Irad: bad u Irad u la pynkha ïa u Mehujael: bad u Mehujael u la pynkha ïa u Methusael: bad u Methusael u la pynkha ïa u Lamekh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Lamekh u la shim ha lade ar ngut ki tnga: ka kyrteng jong kawei ka la long “ka Adah”, bad ka kyrteng jong kawei pat “ka Sillah”.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ka Adah ka la kha ïa u Jabal: une u la long u kpa jong kita kiba shong ha ki ïingtrep, bad jong kiba buh ki jingri.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ka kyrteng u para jong u ka la long “u Jubal”; bad u la long ma u, u kpa baroh kiba nang ban ktah ïa ka bina bad ïa ka besli.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ka Sillah ruh ka la kha ïa u Tubal-kain, uba hikai shoh thaw ïa ki kynja atiar banep baroh ha ka tama bad u nar: bad ka para jong u Tubal-kain ka la long “ka Naamah”.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u Lamekh u la ong ha ki tnga jong u, ka Adah bad ka Sillah, “To sngew ïa ka ktien jong nga; phi ki tnga jong u Lamekh, to shahshkor ïa ka jingong jong nga: naba nga la pynïap ïa u briew uba la pynmong ïa nga, bad ïa u samla uba la pynmynsaw ïa nga.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Lada ïa u Kain yn sa pynhiar kput hynñiew shah, hynrei ïa u Lamekh te hynñiewphew hynñiew sien keiñ.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Adam u la ithuh pat ïa la ka tnga; te ka la kha ïa u khun, bad ka la khot kyrteng “u Seth” ïa u: “Naba U Blei,” ka la ong, “u la ai ha nga da uwei pat u symbai ha ka jaka u Abel, ïa uba u Kain u la pynïap noh keiñ.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad ha u Seth hi ruh la kha ïa u khun, bad u la khot kyrteng “u Enosh” ïa u. Te mynkata la sdang ban khot ïa ka kyrteng U Trai."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kane ka long ka kitab shaphang ki jinghiar pateng jong u Adam. Ha kata ka sngi ba U Blei u la thaw ïa u briew, ha ka jingsyriem U Blei u la thaw ïa u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Shynrang bad kynthei u la thaw ïa ki; bad u la kyrkhu ïa ki, bad u la khot kyrteng “Adam” ïa ki, ha kata ka sngi mynba la thaw ïa ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Adam u la im shispah laiphew snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u khun ha ka jingsyriem jong u bad ha ka dur jong u hi; bad u la khot kyrteng “u Seth” ïa u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki sngi jong u Adam hadien ba u la pynkha ïa u Seth ki la long phraspah snem; bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki sngi jong u Adam baroh ba u la im ki la long khyndaispah bad laiphew snem: hadien kata, u la ïap.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U Seth ruh u la im shispah bad san snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Enosh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Seth u la im hadien ba u la pynkha ïa u Enosh phraspah bad hynñiew snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki sngi baroh jong u Seth ki la long khyndaispah bad khat-ar snem: hadien te u la ïap.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Enosh ruh u la im khyndaiphew snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Kenan.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Enosh u la im ynda u la pynkha ïa u Kenan phraspah bad khatsan snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki sngi baroh jong u Enosh ki la long khyndaispah bad san snem: hadien kata, u la ïap.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Kenan ruh u la im hynñiewphew snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Mahalalil.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Kenan u la im ynda u la pynkha ïa u Mahalalil phraspah bad sawphew snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ki sngi baroh jong u Kenan ki la long khyndaispah bad shiphew snem: hadien kata, u la ïap.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U Mahalalil u la im hynriewphew san snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Jared.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Mahalalil u la im ynda u la pynkha ïa u Jared phraspah bad laiphew snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ki sngi baroh jong u Mahalalil ki la long phraspah bad khyndaiphew san snem: hadien kata, u la ïap.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U Jared ruh u la im shispah bad hynriewphew ar snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Enokh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Jared u la im ynda u la pynkha ïa u Enokh phraspah snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ki sngi baroh jong u Jared ki la long khyndaispah bad hynriewphew ar snem; hadien kata, u la ïap.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U Enokh ruh u la im hynriewphew san snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Methuselah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Enokh u la ïaid lem bad U Blei hadien ba u la pynkha ïa u Methuselah laispah snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki sngi baroh jong u Enokh ki la long laispah bad hynriewphew san snem.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Enokh u la ïaid lem bad U Blei: bad um shym la don shuh; naba U Blei u la shim noh ïa u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U Methuselah ruh u la im shispah bad phraphew hynñiew snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Lamekh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Methuselah u la im ynda u la pynkha ïa u Lamekh hynñiewspah bad phraphew ar snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ki sngi baroh jong u Methuselah ki la long khyndaispah bad hynriewphew khyndai snem: hadien kata, u la ïap.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U Lamekh ruh u la im shispah bad phraphew ar snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u khun,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad u la khot kyrteng “u Noah” ïa u, u da ong, “Une un pyntngen ïa ngi ha ka kam jong ngi bad ha ka jingtrei minot ki kti jong ngi, namar kata ka khyndew ïa kaba U Trai u la tim.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Lamekh u la im ynda u la pynkha ïa u Noah sanspah bad khyndaiphew san snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te ki sngi baroh jong u Lamekh ki la long hynñiewspah bad hynñiewphew hynñiew snem: hadien kata, u la ïap.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u Noah u la long sanspah snem ka rta: bad u Noah u la pynkha ïa u Shem, ïa u Ham, bad ïa u Japhet."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ka la jia ruh, mynba ki briew ki la sdang ban ïaroi halor ka khmat ka khyndew, bad ba la kha ïa ki khun kynthei ïa ki,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ba ki khun shynrang U Blei ki la ïohi ïa ki khun kynthei ki jong ki briew ba ki bhabriew; bad ki la shim ki tnga ïa lade na kat kiba ki la ïa-ibha.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te U Trai u la ong, “U Mynsiem jong nga un ym ïaleh bad u briew junom, namar ba u hi u long ka doh: la kumta ruh, ki sngi jong u kin long shispah arphew snem.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki riewradbah ki la don ha ka pyrthei ha kita ki sngi; bad hadien kata ruh, mynba kita ki khun shynrang U Blei ki la leit sha kita ki khun kynthei jong u bynriew, bad ba ki la ïoh khun na ki, kine keiñ, ki la jia long ki briew bashlur eh kiba la ju long mynhyndai hynthai, kiba la donnam shibun.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te U Trai u la ïohi ba ka jingleh bymman jong u briew ka la khraw eh ha ka pyrthei, bad ba ka jingthmu baroh ki jingpyrkhat ka dohnud jong u ki la long bymman ha la ka sngi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad U Trai u la kylla-ka-bamut ba u la lah thaw ïa u briew ha ka pyrthei, bad la pynsngewsih eh ïa u ha la ka dohnud.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te U Trai u la ong, “Ngan pyndam noh ïa u briew ïa uba nga la thaw na khmat ka khyndew; naduh u briew haduh u mrad, bad haduh u kynja bapar, bad ïa ki sim bneng; naba nga kylla-ka-bamut ba nga la thaw ïa ki.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, u Noah u la shem ka jingieit isynei ha khmat U Trai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kine ki long ki jinghiar pateng jong u Noah: u Noah u la long u briew u bahok, uba beit ha ki pateng bynriew jong u, u Noah u la ïaid ryngkat bad U Blei.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Noah u la pynkha ïa lai ngut ki khun shynrang, ïa u Shem, ïa u Ham, bad ïa u Japhet.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, ka khyndew ka la pyut sniew ha khmat U Blei, bad la pyndap ruh ïa ka pyrthei da ka jingleh-jubor.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te U Blei u la khmih ïa ka pyrthei, bad, ha khmih ruh, ka la pyut sniew; naba ka doh baroh ka la lah pynpyut plak ïa la ka lynti ha ka pyrthei.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad U Blei u la ong ha u Noah, “Ka bakut ka doh baroh ka la wan ha khmat jong nga; naba da ki keiñ la pyndap ïa ka pyrthei da ka jingleh-jubor; bad ha khmih ruh, ngan pynjot noh ïa ki lem bad ka khyndew.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> To thaw ïa lade ïa ka ïinglieng da u dieng Kopher; ïa ki pulit men thaw ha kata ka ïinglieng, bad men tah ruh ïa ka da ka bsiang shapoh bad shabar.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ha kane ka rukom men thaw ïa ka: laispah pruh ka lynter jong kata ka ïinglieng, sanphew pruh ka pyngkiang jong ka, bad laiphew pruh ka jingjrong jong ka.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> To men thaw ïa ka jingpynshai ha kata ka ïinglieng; bad haduh shi pruh men kyntiew ïa ka shalor; bad ïa ka jingkhang jong ka ruh men buh sharud jong ka; bad lai pateng men thaw ïa ka.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Namar, ha khmih ma nga, ma nga hi keiñ, ngan sa wallam ïa ka jingshlei ki um halor ka pyrthei, ïa ka ban pynduh noh ïa ka doh baroh, ïa kat kiba don ka jingpyrsad ka jingim ha ki, napoh ka suiñbneng; te kin sa ïap kiei kiei baroh katba don ha ka pyrthei.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, bad me ngan pynskhem ïa la ka jutang; te shapoh kata ka ïinglieng men ïoh wan bsut: ma me bad ki khun shynrang jong me, bad ka tnga jong me, bad ki tnga ki khun shynrang jong me lem bad me.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad na kiei kiei ki kynja ba-im baroh, na ka doh baroh keiñ, men pynwan sha kata ka ïinglieng shi jur shi jur na ki, ïa ka ban ri pynim ïa ki lem bad me; bad shynrang bad kynthei ruh kin ïalong.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ki kynja sim baher ha la ka jaid ka jaid, bad na ki kynja jingri ha la ka jaid ka jaid, na ki kynja bapar halor ka khyndew ruh ha la ka jaid ka jaid, shi jur shi jur na ki keiñ kin ïawan bsut sha me, ba yn ri pynim ïa ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> To buh te ha lade na ka kynja jingbam baroh kaba bit ban bam, bad to kynshew lang ha lade; ba kan long ka jingbam ïa me bad ïa ki.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Noah u la leh kumta; katba kum baroh ba U Blei u la hukum ïa u, kumta keiñ u la leh."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Noah, “To khie leit ma me bad ka ïing jong me baroh shapoh kata ka ïinglieng; naba ïa me nga la ïohi u bahok ha khmat jong nga ha kane ka pateng bynriew.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na u kynja mrad bakhuid baroh, men shim bad me hynñiew hynñiew jur, ïa u shynrang bad la ka kynthei: bad na ki kynja mrad ki bymkhuid shi jur shi jur, ïa u shynrang bad la ka kynthei.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad na ki kynja sim bneng ruh hynñiew hynñiew jur, shynrang bad kynthei; ïa ka ban ri pynim ïa u symbai halor ka khmat ka khyndew baroh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Naba sa hynñiew sngi ngan pynhap ïa u slap halor ka khyndew sawphew sngi bad sawphew miet; bad ngan pynduh noh na khmat ka khyndew ïa kiei kiei ki kynja ba-im baroh katba nga la thaw.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Noah u la leh baroh kat kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Noah u la long hynriewspah snem ka rta mynba kata ka jingshlei ki um ka la jia long halor ka khyndew.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Noah u la leit bsut shapoh, bad ki khun shynrang jong u, bad ka tnga jong u, bad ki tnga ki khun shynrang jong u, lem bad u shapoh kata ka ïinglieng, namar kita ki um jong ka jingshlei.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ki mrad ki bakhuid, bad na ki mrad ki bymkhuid, bad na ki kynja sim, bad na kiei kiei ki kynja bapar baroh halor ka khyndew,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ki la ïaleit bsut shi jur shi jur ha u Noah shapoh kata ka ïinglieng, shynrang bad kynthei, kumba U Blei u la lah hukum ïa u Noah.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ba hadien hynñiew sngi, kita ki um ka jingshlei ki la long halor ka khyndew.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hamar ka bahynriewspah snem ka rta jong u Noah, ha u bnai u ba-ar, ha ka bakhathynñiew sngi jong uta u bnai, ha kata ka sngi hi keiñ, la pynbthei noh ïa ki um mihpohliew baroh ka jingjylliew bah, bad ïa ki jingkhang ki bneng la plie noh wang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u 'lap bah u la don halor ka khyndew sawphew sngi bad sawphew miet.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ha kata ka sngi hi keiñ, ki la leit bsut u Noah, bad u Shem, bad u Ham, bad u Japhet, ki khun shynrang u Noah, bad ka tnga jong u Noah, bad ki tnga jong ki khun shynrang jong u lai ngut lem bad ki, shapoh kata ka ïinglieng;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ma ki, bad ki kynja mrad khlaw baroh ha la ka jaid ka jaid, bad ki kynja jingri baroh ha la ka jaid ka jaid, bad u kynja bapar baroh bapar halor ka khyndew ha la ka jaid ka jaid, bad ki kynja baher baroh ha la ka jaid ka jaid, u sim baroh na ka jaid baroh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki la leit bsut sha u Noah hapoh kata ka ïinglieng, shi jur shi jur na ka doh baroh, ha kaba la don ka jingpyrsad ka jingim.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad kito kiba la ïaleit bsut, ki la ïaleit shynrang bad kynthei na ka doh baroh, kumba U Blei u la lah hukum ïa u: bad U Trai u la khang ïa u shapoh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kata ka jingshlei ka la don sawphew sngi halor ka khyndew; bad kita ki um ki la ïa nang bun, bad ki la kit ïa kata ka ïinglieng, te la kyntiew ruh ïa ka shalor ka khyndew.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad kita ki um ki la ïa nang ïoh bor, bad ki la ïa nang bun shikatdei halor ka khyndew; te kata ka ïinglieng ka la per ha sla ki um.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad kita ki um ki la ïa nang kham jur shikatdei eh halor ka khyndew; te la tap lup ïa ki lum jrong baroh kiba la long hapoh ka bneng baroh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Khatsan pruh ki la ïa nang kiew kita ki um sha jrong; te ïa ki lum la tap lup.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ka doh baroh ba la khih ha ka khyndew ki la ïap noh, ki sim, bad ki jingri, bad ki mrad khlaw, bad kiei kiei ki kynja bapar baroh kat ki bapar halor ka khyndew, bad u briew baroh de:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> baroh keiñ kiba la don ka jingpyrsad ka mynsiem ka jingim ha ki thliew khmut jong ki, na kita baroh kiba la don ha ka ryngkew, ki la ïap noh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, la pynduh noh ïa kiei kiei baroh ki kynja kiba im halor ka khmat ka khyndew, naduh u briew haduh ki jingri, bad ïa kiei kiei ki kynja bapar, bad ïa ki sim ki bneng; kumta keiñ, la pynduh noh ïa ki na khmat ka khyndew: bad la sah im sa tang u Noah, bad kita kiba la don lem bad u ha kata ka ïinglieng.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad kita ki um ki la ïa nang kham jur halor ka khyndew shispah bad sanphew sngi."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Blei u la kynmaw ïa u Noah, bad ïa kiei kiei ki kynja ba-im baroh, bad ïa ki jingri baroh katba la don lem bad u ha kata ka ïinglieng: U Blei ruh u la pynmih ïa ka lyer ban beh halor ka khyndew, te kita ki um ki la jem jai;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad ïa kita ki um mihpohliew jong kaba jylliew bad ïa ki jingkhang ki bneng la set noh ruh, bad ïa u slap na bneng la khang noh;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad kita ki um ki la ïa nang kynran mian pa mian nalor ka khyndew: bad ynda la kut kita ki shispah sanphew sngi, kita ki um ki la duna shibun.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad kata ka ïinglieng ka la shong sah ha u bahynñiew bnai, ha ka bakhathynñiew sngi jong uta u bnai, halor ki lum jong ka ri Ararat.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad kita ki um ki la ïa nang duna nang duna haduh u bashiphew bnai: ha uta u bashiphew bnai, ha ka sngi nyngkong ha uta u bnai, la ïohi ïa ki kliar ki lum.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha ka bakut sawphew sngi, ba u Noah u la plie ïa ka pongshai jong kata ka ïinglieng ïa kaba u la lah thaw:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad u la pyllait khnang ïa ka tyngab kawei, kaba la leit noh ruh da kaba ïaleit bad ïawan phai pat ha ban da la rngad noh kita ki um nalor ka khyndew.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U la pyllait noh ruh ïa ka paro na u, ban khmih lada kita ki um ki la ïarngad noh ne em nalor ka khyndew;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> hynrei, kata ka paro, naba kam shym la shem ïa ka jingjahthait ïa la ka poh'jat, ka la wan phai pat sha u shapoh kata ka ïinglieng, naba kita ki um ki ïadang sah halor ka khmat ka khyndew baroh: u te, da kaba kner ïa la ka kti, u da shim ïa ka, bad u la pynwan ïa ka sha lade shapoh kata ka ïinglieng.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U la ap pat sa kiwei pat hynñiew sngi; bad u la pyllait noh sa shi sien pat ïa kata ka paro na kata ka ïinglieng;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad kata ka paro ka la wan pat sha u, ha kaba la janmiet; bad, ha khmih, ka don ka sla u dieng Olib ba la kheit ha la ka shyntur: kumta, u Noah u la ithuh ba kita ki um ki la rngad noh nalor ka khyndew.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u la ap sa kiwei pat hynñiew sngi, bad u la pyllait noh pat ïa kata ka paro; te kam shym la wan phai pat shuh sha u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ka la long ruh ha ka bahynriewspah iwei snem, ha u bnai u banyngkong, bad ha ka sngi ka banyngkong ha uta u bnai, ba kita ki um ki la rngad noh nalor ka khyndew: te u Noah u la law noh ïa ka jingtap ka ïinglieng bad u la khmih; bad ha khmih, ka khmat ka khyndew ka la nang rkhiang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ha ka ba-arphew hynñiew sngi, ha u bnai u ba-ar, ka khyndew ka la rkhiang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad U Blei u la kren ha u Noah, u da ong,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “To mih noh na ka ïinglieng: ma me bad ka tnga jong me, bad ki khun shynrang jong me, bad ki tnga ki khun shynrang jong me lem bad me.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ïa kiei kiei ki kynja ba-im baroh ba don lem bad me, na ka doh baroh, ïa u sim, bad ïa ki jingri, bad ïa u kynja bapar baroh bapar halor ka khyndew, to da pynmih noh lem bad me; bad to ai kin kha bun ha ka khyndew, bad kin ïaman bun, bad kin ïaroi halor ka khyndew.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Noah u la mih noh bad ki khun shynrang jong u bad ka tnga jong u bad ki tnga ki khun jong u ryngkat bad u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U mrad baroh, u kynja bapar baroh, bad ki kynja baher baroh, bad kaei kaei baroh bapar halor ka khyndew, ha la ka jaid ka jaid ki la ïamih noh na kata ka ïinglieng.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Noah u la tei ïa ka duwan ha U Trai; bad u la shim na ki mrad bakhuid baroh, bad na ki kynja sim bakhuid baroh, bad u la ainguh da ki jingainguh thang halor kata ka duwan.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te U Trai u la iw ïa ka jingiw baiwbih; bad U Trai u la ong ha la ka dohnud, “Ngan ym tim shuh ïa ka khyndew pat na ka bynta u briew; la ka jingpyrkhat ka dohnud u briew ka basniew naduh myndanglong samla jong u; bad ngan ym shoh ïap pat shuh ïa ki kynja ba-im baroh, kumba nga la leh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Katba dang sah kane ka pyrthei, ka aïom bet bad ka ba-ot, ka bakhriat bad ka bashit, bad ka lyiur bad ka tlang, bad ka sngi bad ka miet, kin ym pep shuh.”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Blei u la kyrkhu ïa u Noah bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u, u la ong ruh ha ki, “To da nang kha, bad to da pyndap pat ïa ka pyrthei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ka jingtieng ïa phi ruh bad ka jingsngewkyiuh ïa phi kin long ha ki mrad baroh ka pyrthei, bad ha ki sim bneng baroh, bad ha ki kynja bapar baroh halor ka khyndew, bad ha ki dohkha baroh ha ka duriaw; ha ka kti jong phi la aiti ïa ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U kynja bakhih baroh ba-im un long jingbam ïa phi; kumba nga la ai ïa u kynja jhur bajyrngam, kumta keiñ nga ai baroh ha phi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, tang ïa ka doh kaba dang sah ka snam ka jingim ha ka, phin ym bam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad shisha ïa ka snam ka jingim jong phi ruh ngan dawa; na ka kti u mrad baroh ngan dawa ïa ka, bad na ka kti u briew ruh, bad na ka kti u parabriew baroh ngan dawa keiñ ïa ka jingim jong u briew.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Jar uba pynmih ïa ka snam u briew, da u briew keiñ yn sa pynmih ïa ka snam jong u ruh: naba ha ka dur U Blei la thaw ïa u briew.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Te ma phi, to da nang kha, to da nang roi ruh; to da pynmih noh bun eh u symbai ha ka pyrthei, bad to da pynbun ha ka.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad U Blei u la ïathuh ha u Noah, bad ha ki khun shynrang jong u lem bad u, u da ong,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Ha khmih te ma nga, nga pynlong skhem ïa la ka jutang bad phi, bad u symbai jong phi ruh hadien jong phi;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad lem bad kiei kiei ki kynja ba-im baroh kiba don ryngkat bad phi, bad ki sim, bad ki jingri, bad ki kynja mrad baroh ka pyrthei kiba don lem bad phi; naduh kito baroh kiba la mih noh na kata ka ïinglieng, haduh ki mrad ki mreng ka pyrthei baroh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nga te, ngan pynlong skhem ïa la ka jutang bad phi; ba da ki um ka jingshlei yn ym ot noh shuh ïa ka doh baroh: Lymne yn ym long shuh ka jingshlei ïa ka ban pynjot noh ïa ka pyrthei.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad U Blei u la ong, “Kane ka long ka dak jong kata ka jutang ïa kaba nga buh junom hapdeng jong nga bad phi bad kiei kiei ki kynja ba-im baroh ba don lem bad phi, ha ban da kut ka rta ka pyrthei:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nga buh ïa la ka ryntieh ha u lyoh, bad kan long ka dak jong ka jutang hapdeng jong nga bad ka pyrthei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kan jia ruh, ha kaba ngan pynmih ïa u lyoh halor ka khyndew, ba kata ka ryntieh kan paw ha uta u lyoh,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> te ngan kynmaw ruh ïa la ka jutang kaba hapdeng jong nga bad phi bad kiei kiei ki kynja ba-im baroh na ka doh baroh; bad kita ki um kin ym man long ka jingshlei shuh ïa ka ban pynjot ïa ka doh baroh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad kata ka ryntieh kan long ha uta u lyoh; nga te ngan khmih ïa ka, ïa ka ban kynmaw ïa ka jutang ka bymjukut hapdeng U Blei bad kiei kiei ki kynja ba-im baroh na ka doh baroh katba don ha ka pyrthei.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad U Blei u la ong ha u Noah, “Kane ka long ka dak jong kata ka jutang, ïa kaba nga la pynlong skhem hapdeng jong nga bad ka doh baroh katba don ha ka pyrthei.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ki khun shynrang u Noah, kiba la ïawan mih noh na kata ka ïinglieng, ki la long u Shem, bad u Ham, bad u Japhet: bad u Ham u la long u kpa jong u Kanaan.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kine lai ngut ki la long ki khun shynrang u Noah: bad na kine hi la pynphriang ïa ka pyrthei baroh da ki briew.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hadien kata, u Noah u la sdang ban long u nongrep, bad u la thung ïa ka brisoh Waiñ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U la dih ruh na ka umsoh Waiñ, bad u la buaid; bad u la shah lyngkhuit hapdeng ka ïingjaiñ jong u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Ham, uba u kpa u Kanaan, u la ïohi ïa ka jinglyngkhuit u kpa jong u, bad u la leit ïathuh ha ki baroh ar ngut ki hynmen jong u sha bar.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u Shem bad u Japhet ki la ïashim ïa ka jaiñkup, bad ki la ïabuh ïa ka halor ki tyrpeng jong ki baroh ar ngut, bad ki la ïaïaid da dien, bad ki la ïatap ïa ka jinglyngkhuit u kpa jong ki; bad ïa ki khmat jong ki la pynphai da dien keiñ, ba kin ym ïohi ïa ka jinglyngkhuit u kpa jong ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Noah u la kyndit noh na ka jingbuaid jong u, bad u la tip ïa kaei ba u khun khatduh jong u, u la lah leh ïa u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u la ong, “Long ba la tim ïa u Kanaan; un long u mraw jong ki mraw ha ki hynmen jong u.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u la ong, “To long ba la kyrkhu ïa u Shem da U Trai uba U Blei jong nga; bad u Kanaan un long u shakri jong u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U Blei un pynkhraw ïa u Japhet, bad un shong sah ha ki ïingjaiñ u Shem; bad u Kanaan un long u shakri jong u.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u Noah u la im hadien kata ka jingshlei, laispah bad sanphew snem.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kumta ki sngi baroh jong u Noah ki la long khyndaispah bad sanphew snem: bad u la ïap noh."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kine ki long ki jingkha pateng jaid bynriew ki khun shynrang jong u Noah: u Shem, u Ham, bad u Japhet; bad ha ki la kha ïa ki khun shynrang hadien kata ka jingshlei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ki khun shynrang ki jong u Japhet: u Gomer, bad u Magog, bad u Madai, bad u Jaban, bad u Tubal, bad u Meshekh, bad u Tiras.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang ki jong u Gomer: u Ashkenas, bad u Riphath, bad u Togarmah.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Jaban: u Elishah, bad u Tarshish, ki Kittim, bad ki Dodanim.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na kine, la pynïabynta ïa ki 'dewlynnong ki jaid bynriew ha ki khyndew jong ki, baroh ha la ka jong ka jong ka ktien, ha la ki jong ki jong ki ïing, bad ha la ki jong ki jong ki jaid bynriew.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang ki jong u Ham: u Kush, bad u Misraim, bad u Put, bad u Kanaan.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang ki jong u Kush: u Seba, bad u Habilah, bad u Sabtah, bad u Raamah, bad u Sabtekha; bad ki khun shynrang ki jong u Raamah: u Sheba bad u Dedan.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Kush ruh u la pynkha ïa u Nimrod; une u la sdang ban long u bakhrawbor ha ka khyndew.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U la long ruh u nongbeh mrad uba don bor ha khmat U Trai: namar kane, la ju ong, “Kum u Nimrod uba u nongbeh mrad u bakhrawbor ha khmat U Trai.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ka jingsdang ka hima jong u ka la long ka Babel, bad ka Erekh, bad ka Akkad, bad ka Kalneh, ha ka ri Shinar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na kata ka ri u la leit mih noh sha ka Asshur, bad u la tei ïa ka Ninebeh, bad ïa ka nongbah Rehoboth, bad ïa ka Kalah,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad ïa ka Resen hapdeng ka Ninebeh bad ka Kalah; kaba long ka shnong ka bakhraw.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Misraim u la pynkha ïa ki Lud, bad ïa ki Anam, bad ïa ki Lehab, bad ïa ki Naphtuh,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad ïa ki Pathrus, bad ïa ki Kasluh, (na kiba la wan mih ki Philistia), bad ïa ki Kaphtor.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Kanaan u la pynkha ïa u Sidon, u khun nyngkong jong u, bad ïa u Heth,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ïa ki Jebus, bad ïa ki Amor, bad ïa ki Girgash,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad ïa ki Hib, bad ïa ki Ark, bad ïa ki Sin,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ïa ki Arbad, bad ïa ki Semar, bad ïa ki Hamath; hadien kata, ki ïing jong u Kanaan ki la ïaphriang kylleng.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ka pud ka jong ki Kanaan ka la long naduh ka Sidon, haba me ïaid shaphang ka Gerar, haduh ka Gasa; haba me leit shaphang Sodom, bad Gomorra, bad Admah, bad Seboim, wat haduh ka Lasha.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Ham, ha la ki ïing ki ïing, ha la ki ktien ki ktien, ha la ki ri ki ri, bad ha la ki jaid ki jaid.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ha u Shem ruh, u kthaw ki khun u Eber, u hynmen u Japhet, la kha ki khun.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Shem: u Elam, bad u Asshur, bad u Arphakshad, bad u Lud, bad u Aram.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang jong u Aram: u Us, bad u Hul, bad u Gether, bad u Mash.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Arphakshad u la pynkha ïa u Shelah, bad u Shelah u la pynkha ïa u Eber.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ha u Eber ruh la kha ar ngut ki khun shynrang; ka kyrteng jong uwei ka la long “u Peleg”; naba ha ki sngi jong u la pynïabynta ïa ka khyndew; bad ka kyrteng u para jong u ka la long “u Joktan”.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Joktan u la pynkha ïa u Almodad, bad ïa u Sheleph, bad ïa u Hasarmabeth, bad ïa u Jerah,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad ïa u Hadoram, bad ïa u Usal, bad ïa u Diklah,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad ïa u Obal, bad ïa u Abimael, bad ïa u Sheba,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad ïa u Ophir, bad ïa u Habilah, bad ïa u Jobab; kine baroh ki la long ki khun shynrang jong u Joktan.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad ka jingshong duh jong ki, ka la long naduh ka Mesha, haba me leit shaphang u lum Sephar, sha mihngi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kine ki long ki khun shynrang ki jong u Shem, ha la ki ïing ki ïing, ha la ki ktien ki ktien, ha la ki ri ki ri, bad ha la ki jaid ki jaid bynriew.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te kine ki long ki ïing ki khun shynrang jong u Noah, ha la ki jingkha pateng, ha la ki jaid ki jaid bynriew; bad da kine keiñ la pynïabynta ïa ki jaid bynriew ha ka pyrthei hadien kata ka jingshlei."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ka pyrthei baroh ka la long kawei ka ktien, bad kawei ka jingkren.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba ki nang ïaleit kynriah noh na mihngi, ba ki la shem ïa ka 'dewmadan heh ha ka ri Shinar; bad hangta ki la ïashong duh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki la ïa-ong paralok hi, “Ïa, ngin ïathaw ïa ki maw-it, bad ngin ïathang bha ïa ki.” Te ki maw-it ki la don ha ka jaka ki maw, bad ka bsiang ka la don ha ka jaka ka sorki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki la ïa-ong ruh, “Ïa, ngin ïatei ïa ka nongbah kawei ïa lade bad ïa ka kut ruh kawei, kaba ka kliar jong ka kan kot haduh ka bneng; bad to ngin ïathaw nam ïa lade, ba ïoh yn pynsakma kylleng ïa ngi ha khmat ka pyrthei baroh.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad U Trai u la wan hiar ïa ka ban khmih ïa kata ka nongbah bad ïa kata ka kut, ïa kaba ki la lah ïatei ki khun bynriew.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U Trai u la ong ruh, “Ha khmih, ki briew ki long uwei u paidlang, bad ki don baroh tang kawei ka ktien; bad ïa kane ki ïasdang ban leh: te mynta kaei kaei ruh em kan ym khang ïa ki ban leh, ïa kaba ki la lah ïathmu keiñ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ïa, ngin ïaleit hiar, bad ngin ïa-pynbakla ïa ka ktien jong ki hangta, ba kin ym ïasngewthuh shuh ïa ka ktien paralok hi.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, U Trai u la pynsakma ïa ki kylleng nangta ha khmat ka pyrthei baroh; te ki la ïapep noh na ka ban ïatei ïa kata ka nongbah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar kata, la khot “Babel” ïa ka; naba U Trai u la pynbakla hangta ïa ka ktien ka pyrthei baroh: bad nangta ruh U Trai u la pynsakma ïa ki kylleng ha khmat ka pyrthei baroh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kine ki long ki jinghiar pateng jong u Shem: u Shem u la long shispah snem ka rta, bad u la pynkha ïa u Arphakshad ar snem hadien kata ka jingshlei:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad u Shem u la im hadien ba u la pynkha ïa u Arphakshad, sanspah snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Arphakshad u la im laiphew san snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Shelah:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad u Arphakshad u la im hadien ba u la pynkha ïa u Shelah, sawspah lai snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Shelah u la im laiphew snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Eber:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad u Shelah u la im hadien ba u la pynkha ïa u Eber, sawspah lai snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Eber u la im laiphew saw snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Peleg:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad u Eber u la im hadien ba u la pynkha ïa u Peleg, sawspah laiphew snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Peleg u la im laiphew snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Reu:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad u Peleg u la im hadien ba u la pynkha ïa u Reu, arspah khyndai snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Reu u la im laiphew ar snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Serug:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad u Reu u la im hadien ba u la pynkha ïa u Serug, arspah hynñiew snem bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Serug u la im laiphew snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Nahor:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad u Serug u la im hadien ba u la pynkha ïa u Nahor, arspah snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Nahor u la im arphew khyndai snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Terah:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad u Nahor u la im hadien ba u la pynkha ïa u Terah, shispah khatkhyndai snem, bad u la pynkha ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ki khun kynthei.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Terah u la im hynñiewphew snem, bad u la pynkha ïa u Abram, ïa u Nahor, bad ïa u Haran.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad kine ki long ki jinghiar pateng bynriew jong u Terah: u Terah u la pynkha ïa u Abram, ïa u Nahor, bad ïa u Haran; bad u Haran u la pynkha ïa u Lot.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u Haran u la ïap mynshuwa ïa u Terah u kpa jong u ha ka ri ba kha ïa u, ha ka shnong Ur kaba ha ka ri ki Khaldi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u Abram bad u Nahor ki la ïoh ïa la ka tnga ka tnga: ka kyrteng ka tnga u Abram ka la long “ka Sarai”: bad ka kyrteng ka tnga u Nahor ka la long “ka Milkah”, ka khun u Haran, u kpa ka Milkah, bad u kpa ka Iskah.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad ka Sarai ka la long kaba lyngki; kam shym ïoh khun.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u Terah u la shim ïa u Abram u khun jong u, bad ïa u Lot u khun u Haran, u ksiew jong u, bad ïa ka Sarai ka pyrsa kurim jong u, ka tnga u Abram u khun jong u; bad ki la ïaleit mih noh lang na ka shnong Ur, kaba ha ka ri ki Khaldi, ïa ka ban leit sha ka ri Kanaan; bad ki la ïawan poi sha Haran, bad ki la ïashong sah hangta.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te ki sngi jong u Terah ki la long arspah san snem: bad u Terah u la ïap ha Haran."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Abram, “To khie leit noh ma me hi na la ka ri, bad na la ki kur, bad na ka ïing u kpa jong me, sha kata ka ri ïa kaba ngan pyni ha me:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad ngan pynlong na me ïa ka jaid bynriew kaba khraw, bad ngan kyrkhu ïa me, bad ngan pynkhraw ïa ka kyrteng jong me; me ruh men long ka jingkyrkhu:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ngan kyrkhu ïa kita kiba kyrkhu ïa me, bad ngan tim ïa uta uba tim ïa me: bad ïa ki jaid bynriew baroh ha ka pyrthei kin long ba la kyrkhu ha me.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kumta u Abram u la leit noh kumba U Trai u la lah kren ha u; u Lot ruh u la leit lem bad u: bad u Abram u la long hynñiewphew san snem ka rta mynba u la leit noh na Haran.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Abram u la shim ïa ka Sarai ka tnga jong u, bad ïa u Lot u khun u para jong u, bad ïa ka spah baroh jong ki katba ki la lah ïoh kynshew, bad ïa ki mynsiem ba ki la lah ïaïoh ha Haran; bad ki la ïamih noh ruh ïa ka ban leit sha ka ri Kanaan; bad ki la ïapoi sha ka ri Kanaan.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Abram u la ïaid lyngba kata ka ri sha ka jaka ba la khot “Shekem”, haduh u dieng soh Shanam Dngiem u Moreh. Bad ki Kanaan ki la don mynkata ha kata ka ri.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad U Trai u la mihpaw ha u Abram, u da ong, “Ha u symbai jong me ngan ai ïa kane ka ri”: bad hangta u la tei ïa ka duwan ha U Trai uba la lah mihpaw ha u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad nangta u la kynriah noh sha u lum uba ha ka Bethel shaphang mihngi, bad u la pynïeng ïa la ka ïingtrep, ba la don ka Bethel sha sepngi, bad ka Ai sha mihngi: bad hangta ruh, u la tei ïa ka duwan ha U Trai, bad u la khot ha ka kyrteng U Trai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Abram u la nang ïaid, u da nang leit shuh shuh shaphang shathie.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ka la don ka 'nemsniew ha kata ka ri: kumta, u Abram u la leit hiar sha ka ri Ijipt ban shong nongwei hangta katto katne; naba ka jur eh ka 'nemsniew ha kata ka ri.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba u la poi jan ban leit bsut ha ka ri Ijipt, ba u la ong ha ka Sarai ka tnga jong u, “Ha khmih mynta, nga tip ba pha long kaba ibhabriew ban khmih:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> te kan lah jia, ba haba ki Ijipt kin ïohi ïa pha, kin ïa-ong, ‘Ha khmih kane ka long ka tnga jong u’: bad kin ïa-pynïap noh ïa nga, hynrei, ïa pha kin sa pynim keiñ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> To ïathuh, nga kyrpad ïa pha, ba pha long ka para jong nga: ba kan long bha ïa nga na ka bynta jong pha; bad ba ngan ïoh im ka mynsiem na ka bynta jong pha.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ba haba u Abram u la poi sha ka ri Ijipt, ba ki Ijipt ki la ïakhmih ïa kata ka briew ba ka ibhabriew eh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki myntri syiem ruh jong u Pharaoh ki la ïohi ïa ka, bad ki la ïaroh ïa ka ha khmat u Pharaoh: te la shim ïa kata ka briew sha ïing u Pharaoh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te uta u la leh bha ïa u Abram na ka bynta jong ka: bad u la ïoh ki langbrot, bad ki masi, bad ki kadda shynrang, bad ki shakri shynrang, bad ki shakri kynthei, bad ki kadda kynthei, bad ki ut.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te U Trai u la shoh ïa u Pharaoh bad ïa ka ïing jong u da ki jingpang khlam bakhraw namar ka Sarai ka tnga jong u Abram.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Pharaoh u la khot ïa u Abram, bad u la ong, “Kaei kane ba me la leh ïa nga? Balei mem shym la ïathuh ha nga ba ka la long ka tnga jong me?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Balei me la ïathuh, ‘Ka long ka para jong nga?’ ba kumta ngan da lah ban shim tnga ha lade ïa ka: te mynta ha khmih ka tnga jong me, to shim noh ïa ka, bad to khie leit noh ruh.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Pharaoh u la hukum ïa la ki briew shaphang jong u: bad ki la ïaphah noh ïa u, bad ïa ka tnga jong u, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh katba u don."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Abram u la leit kiew noh na ka ri Ijipt; ma u bad ka tnga jong u, bad kiei kiei baroh katba u don, bad u Lot lem bad u, shaphang shathie ka ri Kanaan.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Abram u la riewbha eh ha ki jingri, ha ka rupa, bad ha ka ksiar.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la nang leit ha la ki jingleit na shathie shaduh Bethel, shaduh ka jaka ha kaba u la lah pynïeng ïa la ka ïingtrep mynnyngkong, hapdeng Bethel bad Ai;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> sha kata ka jaka jong ka duwan, ïa kaba u la thaw hangta mynnyngkong: bad hangta u Abram u la khot ïa ka kyrteng jong U Trai.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ïa u Lot ruh de, uba la leit ryngkat bad u Abram, la don ki langbrot, bad ki masi, bad ki ïingtrep.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te kata ka ri kam lah bsa ïa ki ban shong sah lang: naba kiei kiei ka spah jong ki ka la bun, kumta keiñ kim lah shuh ïashong sah ryngkat.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ka la don ruh ka jingïakajia hapdeng ki nongap jingri jong u Abram bad ki nongap jingri jong u Lot: bad ki Kanaan ruh bad ki Peris mynkata ki la ïashong sah ha kata ka ri.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Abram u la ong ha u Lot, “Nga kyrpad ïa me to wat ai ba kan long kaba ïakajia bad nga bad me, lymne bad ki nongap jingri jong nga bad ki nongap jingri jong me; namar ngi long shipara.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ka khyndew baroh kam long ha khmat jong me? Te nga kyrpad ïa me, to da khlad noh na nga: lada men phai sha kadiang, nga te ngan leit phai sha kamon; ne lada men phai sha kamon, nga te ngan leit phai sha kadiang.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Lot u la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad u la ïohi ïa ka ri madan baroh ka wah Jordan, ba ka la long baroh kylleng ïa kaba la don um bha, mynshuwa ba U Trai u la pynjot noh ïa ka Sodom bad ïa ka Gomorra, kum ka kper U Trai ne kum ka ri Ijipt katba me leit shaphang Soar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Lot u la jied ïa lade ïa kata ka ri madan baroh ka Jordan; u Lot ruh u la leit noh shaphang mihngi: kumta keiñ, ki la ïakhlad lok noh paralok hi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Abram u la shong sah ha ka ri Kanaan, bad u Lot u la shong sah ha ki nongbah ka ri madan, bad u la pynïeng ïa la ka ïingtrep shaphang Sodom.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, ki Sodom ki la long ki bymman bad kiba leh pop shikatdei eh ha khmat U Trai.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Abram, hadien ba u Lot u la khlad noh na u, “To khmied mynta ïa la ki khmat, bad to khmih ruh na kata ka jaka ha kaba me don shaphang shatei, bad shaphang shathie, bad shaphang mihngi, bad shaphang sepngi:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> naba ïa kata ka ri baroh katba me ïohi, ngan ai ha me bad ha u symbai jong me ha la ka rta.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngan pynlong ruh ïa u symbai jong me kum ka 'dewmet ka khyndew: kumta keiñ, ba lada u briew u lah ban ñiew ïa ka 'dewmet ka khyndew, kumta te ïa u symbai jong me ruh yn lah ban ñiew.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> To khie noh, to ïaid lyngba ïa kata ka ri, ïa ka lynter jong ka, bad ïa ka pyngkiang jong ka; naba ha me keiñ ngan sa ai ïa ka.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Abram u la pynkynriah noh ïa la ka ïingtrep, bad u la wan shong sah hajan ki dieng Sning u Mamre, kiba ha Hebron, bad u la tei hangta ïa ka duwan ha U Trai."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha ki sngi jong u Amraphel u syiem ka Shinar, u Ariokh u syiem ka Ellasar, u Khedorlaomer u syiem ka Elam, bad u Thidal u syiem ki Goiim;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ba kine ki la ïaleh thma bad u Bera u syiem ka Sodom, bad u Birsha u syiem ka Gomorra, u Shinab u syiem ka Admah, bad u Shemeber u syiem ki Seboim, bad u syiem ka Bela ruh de, kaba long ka shnong Soar.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kine baroh, ki la ïashem lang ha ka pynthor Siddim, kaba long ka Duriaw Mluh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Haduh khat-ar snem ki la lah ïakohnguh ïa u Khedorlaomer, hynrei, ha ka bakhatlai ka snem ki la ïaleh thma ïa u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ha ka bakhatsaw ka snem, la wan u Khedorlaomer, bad kita ki syiem kiba la long ryngkat bad u, bad ki la ïashoh noh ïa ki Rephaim ha Ashteroth Karnaim, bad ïa ki Sus ha Ham, bad ïa ki Emim ha ka 'dewmadan ka shnong Kiriathaim,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad ïa ki Hor ha u lum Seir jong ki, haduh ka 'dewmadan jong ka Paran, kaba hajan kata ka ri khlaw.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ki la ïawan phai noh, bad ki la ïapoi ha En-mishpat, kaba long ka Kadesh, bad ki la ïashoh noh ïa ka ri baroh kawei jong ki Amalek, bad ïa ki Amor ruh de, kiba la ju ïashong sah ha Hasson-tamar.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te la mih ruh u syiem ka Sodom, bad u syiem ka Gomorra, bad u syiem ka Admah, bad u syiem ki Seboim, bad u syiem ka Bela, kaba long ka Soar; bad ki la ïaïeng riang ban ïapom bad kita ha ka pynthor Siddim;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> kata ka long pyrshah ïa u Khedorlaomer u syiem ka Elam, bad ïa u Thidal u syiem ki Goiim, bad ïa u Amraphel u syiem ka Shinar, bad ïa u Ariokh u syiem ka Ellasar; ki saw syiem kiba ïaleh ïa ki san.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ka pynthor Siddim ka la dap da ki thliew bsiang; bad ki syiem ka Sodom bad ka Gomorra ki la ïaphet ïap, bad ki la ïahap ruh ha kita; te kita kiba la dang sah ki la ïaphet ïap sha ki lum.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki la ïarong noh ïa ka spah baroh jong ki Sodom bad Gomorra, bad ïa kiei kiei ki kynja jingbam baroh jong ki, hadien kata, ki la ïaleit noh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ïa u Lot, uba shong ha Sodom, u khunruid jong u Abram, bad ïa ka spah jong u ruh, ki la ïashim noh, hadien kata, ki la ïaleit noh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te la wan u nongphet ïap uwei, bad u la ïathuh ha u Abram u Hebru, uba la shong hajan ki dieng Sning u Mamre u kynja Amor, u para u Eshkol, bad u para u Aner: bad kine ki la ïasylla lok bad u Abram.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ynda u Abram u la ïohsngew ba la kem mraw ïa u khunruid jong u, u la phah kieng atiar ïa ki shakri jong u ïa kiba la lah ïoh hikai, bad ba la kha ïa ki ha ïing jong u hi, ïa laispah bad khatphra ngut, te u la beh ïa kita haduh ka shnong Dan.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la pynïakhlad ïa lade ban ïaleh ïa ki, ma u bad ki shakri jong u mynmiet, bad u la shoh noh ïa ki, bad u la beh noh ïa ki, haduh ka Hobah, kaba long sha kadiang ïa ka Damaskos.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la wallam pat ïa kata ka spah baroh, bad ïa u Lot ruh u khunruid jong u, bad ïa ka spah jong u ruh, u la wallam pat keiñ, bad ïa ki kynthei ruh de, bad ïa u paidlang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u syiem ka Sodom u la wan tan ïa u Abram haba u wan phai na kaba shoh noh ïa u Khedorlaomer, bad ïa kita ki syiem kiba la don lem bad u, ha ka pynthor Shabeh, kaba long ka pynthor u syiem.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Melkhisedek u syiem ka Salem u la wallam ïa u kpu bad ïa ka umsoh Waiñ: bad u la long u lyngdoh jong U Blei U Bahalor Tam Eh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u la kyrkhu ïa u, bad u da ong, “To long ba la kyrkhu ïa u Abram na U Blei U Bahalor Tam Eh, U Trai ka bneng bad ka khyndew:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad to long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Blei U Bahalor Tam Eh, uba la aiti noh ïa ki nongshun jong me ha ka kti jong me.” Te u Abram u la ai ïa kaba shiphew bynta ha u na ka jinglute baroh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u syiem ka Sodom u la ong ha u Abram, “To ai ha nga tang ïa kita ki briew, te ïa kita ki mar to shim ha lade keiñ.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Abram u la ïathuh ha u syiem ka Sodom, “Nga la kyntiew ïa la ka kti sha U Trai, uba U Blei U Bahalor Tam Eh, uba U Trai ka bneng bad ka khyndew,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ba ngan ym shim ei ei ruh em na ka jong me baroh, naduh iwei i ksai haduh i jingteh ka juti; ba ïoh men ong, ‘Nga la pynriewbha ma nga ïa u Abram.’",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Tang ïa kata hi ïa kaba la bam kita ki samla, bad ïa ka bynta kita ki briew kiba la ïaleit ryngkat bad nga, u Aner, u Eshkol, bad u Mamre; to shah ba kin ïashim ïa la ka bynta.”"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda la lah kine kiei kiei ruh, ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u Abram ha ka jingïohipaw, ka da ong, “To wat sheptieng, ko Abram: Ma nga, nga long ka stieh jong me, bad ka bainong jong me kan long kaba khraw eh.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Abram u la ong, “A Trai Jehobah jong nga, hato kaei men ai ha nga, haba nga nang long uba khlem khun, bad u trai ka ïing jong nga u long une u Elieser u nong Damaskos?”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Abram u la ong, “Ha khmih, ha nga mem shym la ai symbai: bad ha khmih, uwei ïa uba la kha ha ïing jong nga un long u nongïoh pateng jong nga.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ha khmih, ka ktien U Trai ka la wan kumne ha u, ka da ong, “Une un ym ïoh long u nongïoh pateng jong me; hynrei, uta u ban mih noh keiñ na ka kpoh jong me hi un long u nongïoh pateng jong me.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u la ïalam shabar ïa u, bad u la ong, “To khmied mynta sha bneng, bad to ñiew ïa ki khlur, lada me lah ban ñiew ïa ki:” te u la ong ruh ha u, “kumta keiñ yn long u symbai jong me.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la ngeit ha U Trai; bad u la ñiew ïa kata ïa ka ban long ka hok ïa u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U la ong ruh ha u, “Nga long U Trai uba la wallam noh ïa me na ka Ur jong ki Khaldi, ïa ka ban ai ha me ïa kane ka ri ban ïoh pateng ïa ka.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U ruh u la ong, “A Trai Jehobah, hato da kaba kumno te ngan ïoh tip ba ngan ïoh pateng ïa ka?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u, “To shim ïa nga ka masi lud kawei kaba lai snem ka rta, bad ïa ka blang kaba lai snem ka rta, bad u langbrot uba lai snem ka rta, bad ïa ka lyngdkhur kawei, bad i khun paro ruh iwei.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta keiñ, u la shim sha U ïa kine baroh, bad u la phiah ar liang ïa ki, bad u la buh ruh ïa ki dkhot kawei pa kawei marsynrap synrap: hynrei, ïa ki sim um shym la phiah ar liang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad haba ki khlieng ki la ïawan hiar halor kita ki metïap, u Abram u la beh noh ïa ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad haba ka sngi kan sa sep noh, la shoh samthiah eh ïa u Abram; bad ha khmih, ka jingsngewkyiuh bad ka jingdum ka bakhraw ka la ngat ha u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Abram, “To tip shisha ba u symbai jong me un long nongwei ha ka ri ka bymdei ka jong ki, bad kin shakri ruh ïa ki; bad kita kin ïa-pynshitom ïa ki, sawspah snem;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad ïa kata ka jaid bynriew ruh, ïa kaba ki kin ïashakri, ngan da bishar: bad hadien kata, kin ïamih noh bad ka spah shibun.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ma me, men ïoh leit sha la ki kpa ha ka jingsuk; yn sa tep ïa me ha ka jinglong tymmen bha keiñ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, ha ka basaw pateng bynriew kin ïawan phai pat shane; naba ka jingleh bymman ka jong ki Amor kam pat la dap.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ba haba la sep ka sngi, bad ba ka la dum tliw tliw, ha khmih ka lawar ba-mih tdem, bad ka sharak ba-meh ding ka khih hapdeng kita ki dkhot.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ha kata ka sngi, U Trai u la teh ka jutang bad u Abram, u da ong, “Ha u symbai jong me nga la ai ïa kane ka ri, naduh ka wah ka ri Ijipt haduh ka wah bah, kaba ka wah Ïuphratis:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ïa ki Ken, bad ïa ki Kenis, bad ïa ki Kadmon,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ïa ki Hit ruh, bad ïa ki Peris, bad ïa ki Rephaim,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad ïa ki Amor ruh, bad ïa ki Kanaan, bad ïa ki Girgash, bad ïa ki Jebus.”"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ka Sarai ka tnga u Abram kam pat shym la kha khun ïa u: bad ka la don ka shakri ka kynja Ijipt, ka kyrteng jong ka, ka la long “ka Hagar”.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ka Sarai ka la ong ha u Abram, “Ha khmih mynta, U Trai u la khang ïa nga na ka ban kha: to khie leit me shapoh ha ka shakri jong nga; lehse yn ïoh mih khun ïa nga na ka.” Te u Abram u la shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong ka Sarai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ka Sarai ka tnga u Abram ka la shim ïa ka Hagar, kata ka kynja Ijipt ka shakri jong ka, ynda u Abram u la lah shong shiphew snem ha ka ri Kanaan, bad ka la ai ïa ka ha u Abram u tnga jong ka, ïa ka ban long ka tnga jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kumta keiñ, u la leit bsut shapoh ha ka Hagar, bad ka la punkhun; bad ynda ka la ïohi ba ka la lah punkhun, ka la ibeiñ ïa la ka kynrad.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda kumta, ka Sarai ka la ïathuh ha u Abram, “Kaba shah bymdei jong nga kan long halor ka khlieh jong me: ma nga hi keiñ nga la ai ïa la ka shakri ha ka shadem jong me; te haba ka la ïohi ba ka la punkhun, ka la ibeiñ ïa nga: U Trai un da bishar hapdeng jong nga bad me.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, u Abram u la ïathuh ha ka Sarai, “Ha khmih, ka shakri jong pha ka long ha ka kti jong pha hi; to leh ïa ka katba pha ibit hi.” Te ka Sarai ka la leh tyngeh ïa ka katta, ba ka la phet noh na khmat jong ka.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u angel U Trai u la shem ïa ka hajan kaba mih umpohliew ha ka ri khlaw, hajan kata ka pukri kaba ha ka lynti sha Shur keiñ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u la ong, “Ko Hagar, ka shakri jong ka Sarai, hato na-ei pha la wan? bad shaei phan leit?” Bad ka la ïathuh, “Nga phet noh keiñ na khmat ka Sarai ka kynrad jong nga.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad uta u angel U Trai u la ong ha ka, “To leit phai pat sha la ka kynrad, bad to pynkohnguh ïa lade hapoh ka kti jong ka.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad uta u angel U Trai u la ong ruh ha ka, “Ngan pynroi ïa u symbai jong pha shikatdei eh katta, ba yn ym lah shuh ban ñiew ïa u namar ka jingman bun jong u.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad uta u angel U Trai u la ong ruh ha ka, “Ha khmih, pha la punkhun bad phan kha ïa u khun, bad phan khot kyrteng ‘u Ishmael’ ïa u; naba U Trai u la shahshkor ïa ka jingsngewjynjar jong pha.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te un long u briew kum u kadda khlaw; ka kti jong u kan long ban ïaleh ïa u briew baroh, bad ka kti u briew baroh kan ïaleh ïa u; bad ha khmat la ki para baroh un shong dara.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ka te ka la khot ïa ka kyrteng U Trai uba la kren ha ka, “Ma me, A Blei, me ïohi ïa nga”: naba ka la ong, “Shisha te nga dang ïohi hangne ruh ïa uta ynda u la paw ha nga?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Namar kata, la khot ïa kata ka pukri “ka Beer-lahai-roi”; ha khmih, ka don hapdeng ka Kadesh bad ka Bered.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ka Hagar ka la kha ïa u khun ïa u Abram: bad u Abram u la khot kyrteng “u Ishmael” ïa u khun jong u, ïa uba la lah kha ka Hagar.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Abram u la long phraphew hynriew snem, mynba ka Hagar ka la kha ïa u Ishmael ha u Abram."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Abram u la long khyndaiphew khyndai snem, bad U Trai u la paw ha u Abram, bad u la ong ha u, “Nga long U Blei U Badonbor Baroh; to ïaid ha khmat jong nga, bad to long me uba janai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad nga ruh ngan pynlong ïa la ka jutang hapdeng jong nga bad me, bad ngan pynroi ïa me shikatdei eh.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abram u la nguh ngon haduh khyndew: U Blei te u la kren bad u, u da ong,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Shaphang jong nga, ha khmih, ka jutang jong nga ka long bad me, bad me men long u kpa ïa ki jaid bynriew babun byllien.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad yn ym khot kyrteng shuh ‘u Abram’ ïa me; hynrei, ka kyrteng jong me kan long ‘u Abraham’; naba nga la pynlong ïa me u kpa ïa ki jaid bynriew babun byllien.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ngan pynlong ïa me uba kharoi shikatdei eh, bad ngan pynlong ïa ki jaid bynriew na me, bad ki syiem ruh de kin mih noh na me.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ngan pynskhem ïa la ka jutang hapdeng jong nga bad me bad u symbai jong me hadien jong me ruh, ha ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong ki, ban long ka jutang ka baïaineh junom, ban long U Blei ïa me, bad ïa u symbai jong me hadien jong me.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ngan ai ha me, bad ha u symbai jong me hadien jong me, ïa ka ri ha kaba me shong nongwei, ïa ka ri Kanaan baroh kawei keiñ, ïa ka ban long ka bynta trai ba-neh junom; bad ngan long U Blei jong ki.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad U Blei u la ong ruh ha u Abraham, “Ma me, hynrei, to men rakhe ïa ka jutang jong nga; ma me bad u symbai jong me hadien jong me keiñ, ha ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kane ka long ka jutang jong nga ïa kaba phin rakhe, hapdeng jong nga bad phi bad u symbai jong me hadien jong me, kaba long: Ban otsher ïa u shynrang baroh hapdeng jong phi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad phin otsher ïa ka doh sher jong phi; bad kata kan long ka dak jong kata ka jutang hapdeng jong nga bad phi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ïa u khun shynrang baroh, haba u dang phra sngi ka rta, yn sa otsher hapdeng jong phi ha ki jingkha pateng la pateng jong phi, ïa uta keiñ ïa u ba'n kha ha ïing, bad ïa u ba'n thied da ki sbai na uno uno u nongwei, u bymlong na u symbai jong me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ka dei ban otsher keiñ ïa uta ïa u ba'n kha ha ïing jong me, bad ïa uta ïa u ba'n thied da ki sbai jong me: bad ka jutang jong nga kan long ka jutang baïaineh junom ha ka doh jong phi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad uta u khun shynrang baroh ïa u bym-otsher, ïa u bym shym la otsher ïa ka doh ka jingbym-otsher jong u, yn sa ot noh ïa kata ka mynsiem na u paidlang jong u; u la pynkheiñ ïa ka jutang jong nga.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U Blei u la ong ruh ha u Abraham, “Ïa ka Sarai ka tnga jong me, men ym khot kyrteng shuh ‘ka Sarai’ ïa ka, hynrei, ‘ka Sara’ kan long ka kyrteng jong ka.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngan kyrkhu ïa ka ruh, bad ngan ai ha me ïa u khun ruh na ka: ho-oid keiñ ngan kyrkhu ïa ka, ba kan man long ka kmie ki jaid bynriew; bad ki syiem ki paidlang bynriew kin mih na ka.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abraham u la nguh ngon haduh khyndew, bad u la rkhie, bad u la ong ha la ka dohnud, “Shisha yn sa kha ïa u khun ïa u briew uba la shispah snem ka rta? bad ka Sara shisha kan ïoh kha khun, haba ka long kaba khyndaiphew snem ka rta?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Abraham u la ong ha U Blei, “A tang ba un da ïoh im u Ishmael ha khmat jong me!”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad U Blei u la ong, “Shisha keiñ ka Sara ka tnga jong me kan kha ïa u khun ïa me; bad men khot kyrteng ‘u Isaak’ ïa u: bad nga ngan pynskhem ïa ka jutang jong nga bad u, ïa ka ban long ka jutang ka baïaineh junom, bad u symbai jong u hadien jong u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad shaphang u Ishmael ruh, nga la shahshkor ïa me; ha khmih, nga la kyrkhu ïa u, bad ngan pynlong ïa u, u ban kharoi, bad ngan pynroi ïa u shikatdei eh; ïa ki khat-ar ngut ki syiem un pynkha, bad ngan pynlong ïa u ka jaid bynriew ka bakhraw.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, ïa la ka jutang ngan pynskhem bad u Isaak, ïa uba ka Sara kan sa kha ïa me kum ha kane ka Ïa hi ha ka snem ka ban sa mih.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, U Blei u la wai noh ban kren ha u, bad U Blei u la leit kiew noh na u Abraham.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u Abraham u la shim ïa u Ishmael u khun jong u bad ïa ki baroh kat kiba la kha ha ka ïing jong u, bad ïa ki baroh ruh kat kiba la thied da ki sbai jong u, ïa u shynrang baroh keiñ na ki rangbah ka ïing u Abraham; bad u la otsher ïa ka doh ka jingbym-otsher jong ki ha kata ka sngi hi, kumba U Blei u la lah kren ha u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Abraham u la long khyndaiphew khyndai snem ka rta mynba la otsher ïa ka doh ka jingbym-otsher jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Ishmael ruh u khun jong u, u la long uba khatlai snem ka rta, mynba la otsher ïa ka doh ka jingbym-otsher jong u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ha kata ka sngi hi, la otsher ïa u Abraham, bad ïa u Ishmael u khun jong u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ïa ki rangbah baroh na ka ïing jong u, ïa kiba la kha ha ka ïing jong u, bad ïa kiba la thied ruh da ki sbai na u nongwei, la otsher lem bad u."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hadien kata, U Trai u la mihpaw ha u hajan ki dieng Sning u Mamre; mynba u da shong ha ka jingkhang ka ïingtrep jong u, haba dang shit ka sngi;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u la khmied ïa la ki khmat u da khmih ruh, bad ha khmih, lai ngut ki rangbah ki la ïeng ha khmat jong u; bad haba u dang shu lah ïohi ïa ki, u la phet na ka jingkhang ka ïingtrep ban tan ïa ki, bad u la nguh dem ïa ki haduh ka khyndew,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> u da ong, “Ko kynrad jong nga, lada mynta nga la ïoh ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong me, to wat da ïaid lait noh, nga kyrpad ïa me na la u shakri:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> to shah ba yn wanlam khyndiat ka um, nga kyrpad ïa phi, bad to da sait ïa la ki sla'jat, bad to da shongthait ruh hapoh une u dieng:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> nga ruh ngan wallam khyndiat u kpu, bad to phin pyntngen ïa ki dohnud jong phi; hadien kata, phin ïoh nang leit noh: naba na ka bynta kata, phi la ïawan ïaid lait sha la u shakri.” Ki te ki la ïa-ong, “To leh kumta, kat kumba me la ïathuh.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Abraham u la leit jang jang sha kata ka ïingtrep ha ka Sara, u la ong ruh, “To pynkhreh noh kloi kloi lai pyrha u 'purew bani, bad to da khñiot ruh, bad to shet ïa ki kpu ha ka dpei.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Abraham u la phet sha ki jingri, bad u la shim ïa u khun masi uwei uba lkhai bad u babha, bad u la ai ruh ha u samla; bad u la pynkloi ban khreh ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u la wallam ruh ïa ka makhon, bad ïa ka dud, bad ïa uta u khun masi ïa uba u la lah pynkhreh, bad u la buh ïa kita ha khmat jong ki; bad u la ïeng bad ki hapoh uta u dieng, ki ruh ki la ïabam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïakylli ha u, “Ha-ei ka Sara ka tnga jong me?” U te u la ïathuh, “Ha khmih, ka don ha ka ïingtrep.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad uwei u la ong, “Shisha ngan wan phai pat sha me hamar kaba ka aïom ka jingim keiñ; bad ha khmih, ka Sara ka tnga jong me kan ïoh khun.” Bad ka Sara ka la ïohsngew ha ka jingkhang ka ïingtrep, kaba long na shadien jong u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Abraham ruh bad ka Sara ki la lah tymmen, kiba la slem ki sngi ka rta jong ki: bad ka la lah wai noh ïa ka Sara ban long katba kum ka rukom ki kynthei.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Namar kata, ka Sara ka la rkhie sammut ha lade, ka da ong ha lade, “Wa! ynda nga la tymmen ngan ïoh kum ïa kane ka jingsngewbha hun mo? bad u kynrad jong nga ruh u la lah tymmen putet?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Abraham, “Hato balei ba ka rkhie ka Sara kumne, bad ba ka da ong, ‘Shisha ngan kha khun haba nga la tymmen?’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Don kaei kaei ruh ïa kaba um lah U Trai? Ha kata ka Ïa ba la lah buh ngan wan phai pat keiñ sha me, hamar kaba ka aïom ka jingim, te ka Sara kan ïoh u khun.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ynda kumta, ka Sara ka la len, ka da ong, “Ngam shym rkhie”; naba ka la sheptieng. U te u la ong, “Em, hynrei, pha la rkhie.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hadien kata, kita ki briew ki la ïamih noh nangta, bad ki la khmih shaphang ka Sodom: bad u Abraham u la leit on ïa ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong, “Ngan buhrieh na u Abraham ïa kaba ngan sa leh?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Naba u Abraham shisha un man long ka jaid bynriew ka bakhraw bad ka badonbor, bad ha u yn kyrkhu ïa ki jaid bynriew baroh jong ka pyrthei.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Naba nga ithuh ïa u, ba un hukum ïa la ki khun bad ïa la ki ïing hadien jong u, ba kin ïoh rakhe ïa ka lynti jong U Trai, ïa ka ban leh ïa ka hok bad ïa ka jingleh adkar; ba U Trai un ïoh pynwan ha u Abraham ïa kata ïa kaba u la ong shaphang jong u.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te U Trai u la ong, “Namar ba ka jingpyrta shaphang Sodom bad Gomorra ka la jam eh, bad namar ka pop jong ki ka la khia eh keiñ;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ngan leit hiar mynta, ngan da khmih ruh la shisha ne em ba ki la leh syndon kumba la long kata ka jingpyrta jong ki, kaba la poi haduh ha nga; te lymda kumta, ngan ïoh tip ïa kata.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad kita ki briew ki la phai noh ïa la ki khmat nangta, bad ki la nang ïaid shaphang Sodom: hynrei, u Abraham u dang ïeng ha khmat U Trai.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u Abraham u la kham kynshur hajan, u da ong, “Hato men pynjot noh ïa u bahok ruh lem bad u bymhok?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, lehse don sanphew ki bahok hapoh kata ka nongbah; shisha men pynduh bad men ym pynim ïa ka jaka na ka bynta ki sanphew ki riewhok kiba lah ban don ha ka?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> To ai kan long jngai na me ban leh ha kane ka rukom, ban pynïap ïa u bahok lem bad u bymman, kat ban pynlong ïa u bahok kum u bymman; to ai kan long jngai na me kata: u Nongbishar ka pyrthei baroh kawei un ym leh hok mo?”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U Trai ruh u la ïathuh, “Lada nga shem ha Sodom sanphew ki riewhok hapoh kata ka nongbah, te kumta, ngan pynsah im ïa kata ka jaka baroh na ka bynta jong ki.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u Abraham u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Ha khmih mynta, nga la sngewshlur ban kren ha U Trai jong nga, la nga long tang ka 'dewmet bad ki dpei:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> hynrei, lehse don duna san ngut na kita ki sanphew ki bahok: hato men pynjot noh ïa kata ka nongbah baroh kawei namar ba duna kita ki san ngut?” U ruh u la ong, “Ngan ym pynjot noh ïa ka, lada nga shem sawphew san ngut ki riewhok.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u la nang ïakren pat bad U, u la ong ruh, “Hynrei, lehse yn shem sawphew hangta?” U ruh u la ong, “Ngan ym leh ïa kata keiñ na ka bynta kita ki sawphew.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Abraham u la ong shuh, “A ba un ym da sngewbitar U Trai jong nga, lada nga da nang kren shuh: Lehse un shem laiphew hangta?” U ruh u la ong, “Ngan ym leh ïa kata, lada nga shem laiphew hangta.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u Abraham u la ong pat, “Ha khmih mynta, nga la shlur ban kren ha U Trai jong nga: Lehse yn shem arphew hangta?” U ruh u la ong, “Ngan ym pynjot noh ïa ka na ka bynta ki arphew keiñ.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Hadien kata, u Abraham u la ong, “A ba un ym da sngewbitar U Trai jong nga, nga te ngan kren sa tang kane shi sien pat: Lehse yn shem shiphew ngut hangta?” U ruh u la ong, “Ngan ym pynjot noh ïa ka na ka bynta ki shiphew keiñ.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hadien kata, U Trai u la leit noh haba u tang shu la lah wai ïakren bad u Abraham: bad u Abraham ruh u la leit phai noh sha la ka jaka."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad kita ki ar ngut ki angel ki la ïawan poi sha Sodom la janmiet; bad u Lot u da shong ha ka khyrdop ka Sodom: bad haba u Lot u la ïohi ïa ki, u la ïeng ban leit tan ïa ki; bad u la dem khrup ïa la ka khmat haduh ka khyndew;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u la ong, “Ha khmih mynta, ko ki kynrad jong nga, to phai noh, nga kyrpad ïa phi, sha ka ïing u shakri jong phi, bad to da sah miet, bad to phin sait ïa la ki sla'jat, ynda kumta, phin ïoh khie dang step, bad ban nang leit noh ha ka jingleit jong phi.” Ki te ki la ïathuh, “Em, namar ba ngin sah ha ka lynti baroh shi miet.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u la ban kyntu eh ïa ki; hadien kata, ki la ïaphai sha u, bad ki la ïawan bsut sha ka ïing jong u; bad u la thaw ïa ka jingkhawai ïa ki, bad u la shet ïa u kpu bakhlem thiat, ki ruh ki la ïabam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei haba kim pat ïoh leit thiah, ki briew jong kata ka nongbah, ki briew jong ka shnong Sodom keiñ ki la ïaker kut sawdong ïa kata ka ïing, bad ki samla bad ki tymmen, u paidlang baroh keiñ na ka jaka baroh:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ki la ïakhot ïa u Lot, bad ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Ha-ei kito ki briew kiba la ïawan sha me ha kane ka miet? to da pynmih shabar ïa ki sha ngi, ba ngin ïoh ithuh ïa ki.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, u Lot u la wan sha ki ha ka jingkhang, u la khang ruh artad ïa ka jingkhang hadien jong u,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad u la ong, “Ha sngap, ko ki para, to wat da leh bymman kumta.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ha khmih mynta, nga don ar ngut ki khun kynthei ki bym pat shym la ithuh ïa u briew; to ai, nga kyrpad ïa phi, ba ngan wanlam noh ïa ki shabar sha phi mynta, bad to da leh ïa ki katba phi ibit: tang ïa kine ki briew to wat leh ei ei ruh em; namar na ka bynta kata ki la ïawan hapoh ka synrang ka jingsop jong nga.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ki te ki la ïathuh, “Da shuh noh me ho.” Ki la ïa-ong ruh artad, “Une u la shu wan long u sohshnong shane, bad mynta un man long u nongbishar pynban: mynta ngin kham ïaleh sniew ha me, ban ïa kaba ha ki.” Bad ki la ïaban khia eh ïa uta u briew, ïa u Lot keiñ, bad ki la ïakyntur hajan ruh ban pynpait ïa ka jingkhang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, kita ki briew haba ki la kner ïa la ki kti, ki la ïashim ñiat bad ki la ïaring ïa u Lot ha lade shapoh kata ka ïing, bad ki la khang ruh ïa kata ka jingkhang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ki la shoh ruh ïa kita ki briew kiba hajan ka jingkhang kata ka ïing da ka jingmatlah, naduh u barit haduh u bakhraw: tad ynda ki da thait ban wad ïa kata ka jingkhang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te kita ki briew ki la ong ha u Lot, “Me dang don shuh kino kino ruh hangne? ïa u pyrsa kurim, bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong me, bad ïa ki khun kynthei jong me, bad ïa kino kino ruh baroh kat kiba dei ki jong me ha kane ka nongbah, to men ïalam noh shabar na kane ka jaka:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> namar ngin sa pynduh noh thiaw ïa kane ka jaka, naba ka jingpyrta ki jinglehsniew jong ki ka la nang man jur eh ha khmat U Trai; te U Trai u la phah ïa ngi keiñ ban pynduh noh thiaw ïa ka.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Lot, namar kata, u la leit shabar, bad u la kren ha la ki pyrsa kurim, kiba la shongkurim bad ki khun kynthei jong u, bad u la ong, “To phin khie joit, to da wan noh na kane ka jaka; naba U Trai un sa pynduh noh thiaw ïa kane ka nongbah.” Hynrei, ha khmat la ki pyrsa kurim u la imat long kum uba kren biria.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad haba dang shai byrngut, te kita ki angel ki la ïaban kyntu eh ïa u Lot, ki da ong, “To mih joit noh, to shim ïa la ka tnga, bad ïa la ki khun kynthei ar ngut, ïa kiba me shem hangne; ba ïoh yn ing duh ma me ruh ha ka jingpynshitom ïa kane ka nongbah.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te katba u la leh tud, kita ki briew ki la bat skhem ïa ka kti jong u, bad ïa ka kti ka tnga jong u, bad ïa ka kti ki khun kynthei jong u ar ngut; naba U Trai u leh isynei ïa u: bad ki la ïalam noh shabar ïa u, bad ki la ïabuh biang ïa u shabar kata ka nongbah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ynda ki la lah ïalam shabar ïa ki, u la ong, “To da phet ïap noh me; to wat khmih kyrtiang dien, bad to wat sangeh me ha ka pyntha baroh; to da phet ïap noh sha uta u lum, ba ïoh yn ing duh ma me.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Lot u la ong ha ki, “A ym kumta, ko Kynrad jong nga;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ha khmih mynta, u shakri jong me u la shem ïa ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong me, bad me la pynkhraw ïa la ka jingisynei, ïa kaba me la pyni ha nga da kaba pynim ïa nga; te ma nga, ngam lah phet ïap noh sha uta u lum, ba ïoh yn lap kaei kaei ruh ka jingsniew ïa nga, bad ba ngan ïap noh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ha khmih mynta, kane ka shnong ka jan ban phet ïap noh sha ka, bad ka long kaba rit: A to shah ba ngan phet ïap noh shato, (kane kam long kaba rit shisha?) bad ka mynsiem jong nga kan ïohlait im.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U te u la ong ha u, “Ha khmih, nga la shah keiñ ïa me shaphang kane ruh, ba ngan ym pynkyllon noh ïa kane ka shnong, shaphang kaba me la kren.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> To da pynkloi noh, to da phet ïap noh shato; naba ngam lah leh ei ei ruh em ha ban da me la poi shato.” Namar kata, la khot ïa kata ka shnong “ka Soar”.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ka sngi ka la dang mih shalor ka khyndew hamar ba u Lot u la leit bsut ha Soar.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ynda kumta, U Trai u la pynhap slap halor ka Sodom bad Gomorra da u kyndok bad da ka ding na U Trai na bneng;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> kumta, u la pynkyllon thiaw ïa kita ki nongbah, bad ïa kata ka pynthor baroh, bad ïa ki trai-shnong jong kita ki nongbah baroh, bad ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba mih na ka khyndew.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, ka tnga jong u Lot ka la khmih kyrtiang dien na shadien jong u, te ka la man long ka païa maw mluh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u Abraham u la khie dang step phyrngab ban leit sha kata ka jaka ha kaba u la lah ïeng ha khmat U Trai:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad u la khmih shaphang Sodom bad Gomorra, bad shaphang ka ri baroh jong kata ka pynthor, bad u la ïohi, bad ha khmih, ka tdem jong kata ka khyndew ka la kiew kum ka tdem ka lawar ding.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Hynrei, U Blei, mynba u la pynduh thiaw ïa kita ki nongbah jong ka pynthor, u la kynmaw ïa u Abraham, bad u la phah noh ïa u Lot napdeng kata ka jingpynkyllon, mynba u la pynkyllon ïa kita ki nongbah ha kiba u la shong sah u Lot.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te u Lot u la leit kiew na Soar, bad u la shong sah ha uta u lum lem bad ki khun kynthei jong u ar ngut; naba u la tieng ban shong sah ha Soar: te u la shong sah hapoh kawei ka krem, ma u bad ki khun kynthei jong u ar ngut.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad kata kaba kham san na ki ka la ong ha kata kaba kham poh, “U kpa jong ngi u la tymmen, bad u briew ruh ym don ha ka pyrthei ban wan bsut sha ngi katba ka rukom ha ka pyrthei baroh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> To ïa ngin ïa-ai kyiad umsoh Waiñ ïa u kpa jong ngi ban dih, ngi ruh ngin ïathiah lem bad u, khnang ba ngin ïoh sumar symbai na la u kpa.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kumta keiñ, ki la ïa-ai kyiad umsoh Waiñ ïa u kpa jong ki ban dih ha kata ka miet: bad kata kaba kham san ka la leit bsut bad ka la thiah ryngkat bad u kpa jong ka; te um shym la tip lymne mynba ka la wan thiah, lymne mynba ka la khie.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te ka la jia ha kaba lashai pat, ba kata kaba kham san ka la ong ha kaba kham poh, “Ha khmih, nga la thiah mynhynne mynmiet ryngkat bad u kpa jong nga: to ïa ngin ïa-ai kyiad umsoh Waiñ biang ha u ban dih ha kane ka miet ruh; bad to da khie leit ma pha ruh, bad to da thiah ryngkat bad u, khnang ba ngin ïoh sumar symbai na la u kpa.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kumta, ki la ïa-ai kyiad umsoh Waiñ ïa u kpa jong ki ha kata ka miet ruh: bad kata kaba kham poh ka la khie, bad ka la thiah lem bad u; te um shym la tip lymne mynba ka la wan thiah, lymne mynba ka la khie.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kumta, kita ki khun kynthei jong u Lot baroh ar ngut ki la punkhun na u kpa jong ki hi.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad kata kaba kham san ka la kha ïa u khun, bad ka la khot kyrteng ïa u, “u Moab”: bad u la long ma u keiñ u kpa ki Moab haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad kata kaba kham poh ruh ka la kha ïa u khun, bad ka la khot kyrteng ïa u, “u Ben-ammi”: u long ma u keiñ u kpa ki khun u Ammon haduh kane ka sngi."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Abraham u la leit noh nangta sha ka ri shathie, bad u la shong sah hapdeng Kadesh bad Shur, bad u la shong basa ha Gerar.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Abraham u la ong shaphang ka Sara ka tnga jong u, “Ka long ka para jong nga”: te u Abimelekh u syiem ka Gerar u la phah, bad u la shim noh ïa ka Sara.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ynda kumta, U Blei u la wan ha u Abimelekh ha ka jingphohsniew mynmiet, bad u la ong ha u, “Ha khmih, men sa ïap namar kata ka briew ïa kaba me la shim; naba ka long ka tnga briew.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, u Abimelekh um pat shym leit hajan ïa ka: u la ïathuh te, “Ko Trai, hato men pynïap noh ruh ïa ka jaid bynriew ka bahok?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hato um shym la ïathuh ma u hi ha nga, ‘Ka long ka para jong nga’ bad ma ka hi ruh ka la ong, ‘U long u hynmen jong nga’; te ha ka jingsngewsngur ka dohnud jong nga bad ha ka jingkhuid ki kti jong nga, nga la leh ïa kane keiñ.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, U Blei u la ong ha u ha ka jingphohsniew, “Shisha, nga ruh nga tip ba ha ka jingsngewsngur ka dohnud jong me, me la leh ïa kane; te nga ruh nga la khang noh ïa me na ka ban leh pop pyrshah ïa nga: namar kata, ngam shym la shah ïa me ban ktah ïa ka.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Mynta te to da ai noh pat ïa ka tnga uta u briew; naba u long u nongïathuhlypa, bad un ïoh duwai na ka bynta jong me, bad me men ïoh im: hynrei, lada mem da ai noh pat ïa ka, to tip me ba shisha men ïap noh, ma me bad baroh kat kiba dei ki jong me.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Abimelekh u la khie la dang step eh, bad u la khot lang ïa la ki shakri baroh, bad u la ïathuh ha ki shkor jong ki, ïa kine kiei kiei ruh baroh: te kita ki briew ki la ïasheptieng shikatdei eh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Abimelekh u la khot ruh ïa u Abraham, bad u la ong ha u, “Hato kaei kane ba me la leh ïa nga? bad nga la leh pop aïu pyrshah ïa me, ba me la wallam ïa ka pop kaba khraw katta halor jong nga bad halor ka hima jong nga? me la leh ïa nga ïa ki jingleh ïa ki bymdei ban leh.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Abimelekh u la kylli ruh ha u Abraham, “Hato me la ïohi aïu, haba me la leh ïa kane?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Abraham u la ïathuh, “Naba nga la ong ha lade, ‘Shisha ym don ka jingsheptieng burom ïa U Blei ha kane ka jaka; ki te kin pynïap noh ïa nga namar ka tnga jong nga.’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ka long ka para jong nga shisha; ka long keiñ ka khun u kpa jong nga, hynrei, kam long ka khun ka kmie jong nga; bad ka long ka tnga jong nga artad.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ka la jia ruh, mynba U Blei u la pynïaid wir ïa nga na ïing u kpa jong nga, ba nga la ong ha ka, ‘Kane ka jingleh ieit jong pha ïa kaba phan leh ïa nga; ha ka jaka baroh katba kan jia ha ngi ban poi, to ong shaphang jong nga, u long u hynmen jong nga.’ ”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abimelekh u la shim ïa ki langbrot, bad ïa ki masi, bad ïa ki shakri shynrang, bad ïa ki shakri kynthei, bad u la ai ruh ïa ki ha u Abraham, bad ïa ka Sara ruh ka tnga jong u, u la ai noh pat ha u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Abimelekh u la ong, “Ha khmih, ka ri jong nga ha khmat jong me: to da shong sah kat shaba me ibit.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ha ka Sara u la ong, “Ha khmih, nga la ai ha u hynmen jong pha shi hajar rupa: ha khmih, kata kan long ka mynrain kum ka jingkah ïa ki khmat jong pha, ha kiba don bad pha baroh, bad shaphang kiei kiei baroh la pynbeit ïa pha.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abraham u la duwai ha U Blei: bad U Blei u la pynkhiah ïa u Abimelekh bad ïa ka tnga jong u, bad ïa ki shakri kynthei jong u; te ki la kha khun ruh de.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Naba U Trai u la lah set khop ïa ki kpoh ki kynthei baroh ha ïing u Abimelekh, na ka bynta ka Sara ka tnga u Abraham."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la wan-i ïa ka Sara kumba u la lah ong, bad U Trai u la leh ïa ka Sara kumba u la lah ong.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Namar ka Sara ka la punkhun, bad ka la kha ïa u khun ïa u Abraham ha ka jinglong tymmen jong u, ha kata ka Ïa keiñ ba la buh ïa kaba U Blei u la lah ong ha u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Abraham u la khot kyrteng ïa la u khun ba la kha ïa u, ïa uba la kha ka Sara ïa u, “u Isaak”.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Abraham u la otsher ïa u Isaak u khun jong u haba u dang long phra sngi ka rta, kumba la lah hukum U Blei ïa u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Abraham u la long uba shispah snem ka rta, mynba la kha ha u ïa u Isaak u khun jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ka Sara ka la ong, “U Blei u la pynrkhie kmen ïa nga, bad baroh kat kiba ïohsngew kin ïarkhie kmen lem bad nga.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ka la ong ruh, “Hato uei u ban da lah ong ha u Abraham, ba ka Sara kan da la ai buiñ ïa ki khun? naba nga la kha ïa u khun ïa u ha ka jinglong tymmen jong u keiñ.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad uta u khun khynnah u la nang san, te la pyniehnoh buiñ ïa u bad u Abraham u la thaw ka jingkhawai kaba khraw ha kata ka sngi ba la pyniehnoh buiñ ïa u Isaak.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ka Sara ka la ïohi ïa u khun ka Hagar, kata ka kynja Ijipt, ïa uba ka la lah kha ïa u Abraham, ba u da rkhiebeiñ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Namar kata, ka la ong ha u Abraham, “To da beh noh ïa kane ka mraw bad ïa u khun jong ka: naba u khun jong kane ka mraw un ym long uba ïoh bynta lem bad u khun jong nga, bad u Isaak keiñ.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te kane ka ktien ka la pynsngewsih shikatdei eh ïa u Abraham na ka bynta u khun jong u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, U Blei u la ong ha u Abraham, “Wat ai ba yn pynsngewsih ïa me na ka bynta uta u samla, bad na ka bynta ka mraw jong me; ha kiei kiei baroh ba ka Sara ka la ong ha me, to da pynshahshkor keiñ ïa ka ktien jong ka; naba ha u Isaak yn khot u symbai jong me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad shaphang u khun jong kata ka mraw ruh ngan pynlong ka jaid bynriew ïa u, namar u long u symbai jong me keiñ.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abraham u la khie dang step eh, bad u la shim ïa u kpu, bad ïa ka um shi lywa snieh, u la ai ruh ïa ki ha ka Hagar, u da buh ïa ki ha ka tyrpeng jong ka, bad ïa uta u khynnah ruh, bad u la phah noh ïa ka: ka ruh ka la leit noh, bad ka la ïaid sakma ha ka ri khlaw Beer-sheba.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kata ka um ka la lut noh ha kata ka lywa snieh, ka te ka la buh ïa uta u khynnah hapoh kawei ka bniap.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ka la leit shong weibriew kham jngai marpyrshah ïa u, kumba shi sien siat khnam: naba ka la ong, “Ngam lah ban khmih ïa uto u khynnah haba un sa ïap noh.” Kumta, ka la shong marpyrshah ïa u, bad ka la pynjam eh ïa la ka ktien, ka da ïam ruh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te U Blei u la ïohsngew ïa ka jingud lynñiar uta u khynnah; bad u angel U Blei u la khot ïa ka Hagar na bneng, bad u la ong ha ka, “Ka la jia aïu ïa pha Hagar? to wat sheptieng ho; naba U Blei u la ïohsngew ïa ka jingud lynñiar u khynnah nangtai ha kaba u don keiñ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> To da ïeng mih noh, to da shim kynthup ïa u khynnah, bad to da bat ïa u ruh da la ka kti; naba ngan pynlong ïa u ka jaid bynriew kaba khraw.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad U Blei u la pynpeit ïa ki khmat jong ka, hadien kata, ka la ïohi ïa kawei ka pukri ba-mih umpohliew; bad ka la leit bad ka la pyndap ïa la ka lywa snieh da ka um, bad ka la ai ha uta u khynnah ba un dih.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad U Blei u la long ryngkat bad uta u khynnah; te u la nang ïoh bor, bad u la shong sah ha kata ka ri khlaw, bad u la long u nongrah ryntieh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u la shong sah ha ka ri khlaw Paran: bad ka kmie jong u ka la shim ka tnga ïa u na ka ri Ijipt.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ka la jia ruh mynkata, ba u Abimelekh bad u Phikhol u nongïalam barangbah, u paidïapom jong u, ki la ïakren ha u Abraham, ki da ong, “U Blei u long bad me ha kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba me leh:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> te mynta, namar kata, to smai noh ha nga hangne ha ka kyrteng U Blei ba men ym leh shukor ïa nga, lymne ïa u khun jong nga, lymne ïa u ksiew jong nga: hynrei, kat kum kata ka jinglehsbun ïa kaba nga la leh ïa me, ba me men leh kylliang pat ïa nga, bad ïa ka ri ha kaba me la shong nongwei.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Abraham u la ong, “Ngan smai keiñ.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Abraham u la sneng ïa u Abimelekh shaphang ka pukri um, ïa kaba ki shakri jong u Abimelekh ki la lah ïaknieh da ka bor.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u Abimelekh u la ong, “Nga ngam shym la tip mano ba la leh ïa kane: ma me hi ruh mem shym la ïathuh keiñ ha nga, nga ruh ngam shym la ïohsngew shaphang kata, hynrei, tang ha kane ka sngi.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abraham u la shim ïa ki langbrot bad ïa ki masi, bad u la ai ïa ki ha u Abimelekh; bad ki la ïathaw ïa ka jutang baroh ar ngut.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u Abraham u la buh kyrpang hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot kynthei na ka kynhun.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abimelekh u la ong ha u Abraham, “Hato ïa-ei kine ki hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot kynthei ïa kiba me la buh kyrpang?”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U ruh u la ïathuh, “Naba ïa kine ki hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot kynthei men shim ma me keiñ na ka kti jong nga, ïa ka ban long ka sakhi ha nga, ba long ma nga uba la tih ïa kane ka pukri.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Namar kata, u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “ka Beer-sheba”; namar ba hangta ki la ïasmai baroh ar ngut.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kumta keiñ, ki la ïathaw ïa ka jutang ha Beer-sheba: ynda kumta, u Abimelekh, bad u Phikhol u nongïalam barangbah u paidïapom jong u, ki la ïamih joit, bad ki la ïaleit phai pat sha ka ri ki Philistia.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u Abraham u la thung ïa ka 'law kyntang ha Beer-sheba, bad hangta u la khot ha ka kyrteng U Trai, uba U Blei bymjukut.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u Abraham u la shong nongwei bun sngi eh ha ka ri ki Philistia."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ka la jia hadien kine kiei kiei ruh, ba U Blei u la tynjuh ïa u Abraham, bad u la ong ha u, “Ko Abraham”: bad u la ïathuh, “Ha khmih, ma nga.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad U Blei u la ong, “To shim mynta ïa la u khun, u khun marwei jong me keiñ, u Isaak, ïa uba me ieit eh, to khie leit ruh sha ka ri Moraïah, bad to da kñia ïa u hangta kum ka jingainguh thang halor uwei na kita ki lum ïa uba ngan ïathuh ha me.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Abraham u la khie dang step eh, bad u la teh ïa ka jin halor ka kadda jong u, bad u la shim lem bad u ïa ki samla jong u ar ngut, bad ïa u Isaak u khun jong u, bad u la thlieh ïa ki dieng ïa kata ka jingainguh thang, bad u la mih noh joit, bad u la leit ruh sha kata ka jaka ïa kaba U Blei u la lah ong ha u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ha ka balai sngi, u Abraham u la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad u la ïohi ïa kata ka jaka na jngai.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Abraham u la ong ha ki samla jong u, “To sah noh phi shane lem bad ka kadda; te ma nga bad une u samla ngin ïaleit shaduh shatai bad ngin ïamane; hadien kata, ngin ïawan kylla pat sha phi.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abraham u la shim ïa kita ki dieng ka jingainguh thang, bad u la buh ïa ki halor u Isaak u khun jong u; hynrei, ïa ka ding, bad ïa ka tari, u la shim ha la ka kti hi; kumta, ki la ïaleit baroh ar ngut ryngkat.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Isaak u la kren ha u Abraham u kpa jong u, bad u la ong, “Ko kpa jong nga”: u ruh u la ïathuh, “Ha khmih, ma nga, ko khun jong nga.” Hadien kata, u da ong, “Ha khmih ka ding bad ki dieng: hynrei, ha-ei u khun langbrot ïa ka jingkñia ainguh thang?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Abraham u la ïathuh, “Ko khun, U Blei un pynïoh lypa hi ïa lade ïa u khun langbrot ïa ka jingkñia ainguh thang”: kumta, ki la nang ïaleit baroh ar ngut ryngkat.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki la ïapoi sha kata ka jaka ïa kaba U Blei u la lah ong ha u; bad u Abraham u la tei ïa ka duwan hangta, bad u la buh beit ïa kita ki dieng halor, bad ynda u la khum ïa u Isaak u khun jong u, u la buh ïa u halor kata ka duwan halor jrong ki dieng.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Abraham u la kner ïa la ka kti, bad u la shim ïa kata ka tari ïa ka ban pynïap noh ïa la u khun.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u angel U Trai u la khot kloi ïa u na bneng, bad u la ong, “Ko Abraham, Abraham”: u te u la ong, “Ha khmih, ma nga.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u la ong, “To wat buh ïa la ka kti ha uta u samla, lymne wat leh ei ei ruh em ïa u: naba mynta nga tip keiñ ba me tieng burom ïa U Blei, haba mem shym la bat noh wat ïa la u khun, ïa u khun marwei jong me na nga.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Abraham u la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad u la khmih shaiñ, bad ha khmih u langbrot na shadien ba la suhsat na ki reng jong u ha ka bniap: te u Abraham u la leit bad u la shim ïa uta u langbrot, bad u la kñia ainguh ïa u kum ka jingkñia ainguh thang ha ka jaka u khun jong u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Abraham u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka, “Jehobah-jireh”: kumba la dang ong haduh kane ka sngi, “Ha u lum U Trai yn sa ïohi hi.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad uta u angel U Trai u la khot pat sa shi sien ïa u Abraham na bneng,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad u la ong, “Nga la smai ha lade”, ong U Trai, “namar ba me la leh ïa kane, bad ba mem shym la bat noh wat ïa la u khun, ïa u khun marwei jong me na nga:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad da kaba kyrkhu ngan da kyrkhu shisha ïa me, bad da kaba pynroi ngan da pynroi shisha ïa u symbai jong me kat ki khlur bneng, bad kum u shyiap uba harud ka duriaw; bad u symbai jong me un ïoh bat ha lade ïa ki khyrdop ki nongshun jong u;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ha u symbai jong me ki jaid bynriew baroh ka pyrthei kin ïa-pynkyrkhu ïa lade; naba me la kohnguh ïa ka ktien jong nga.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kumta, u Abraham u la leit phai pat sha ki samla jong u, bad ki la ïamih noh joit bad ki la ïaleit wan noh ryngkat ruh sha Beer-sheba; bad u Abraham u la shong duh ha Beer-sheba.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ka la jia ruh ynda la lah kine kiei kiei ruh, ba ki la ïathuh ha u Abraham, ki da ong, “Ha khmih, ka Milkah, ka ruh ka la kha ki khun ïa u Nahor u para jong me;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ïa u Hus u khun jong u ba la kha nyngkong, bad ïa u Bus u para jong u, bad ïa u Kemuel u kpa u Aram,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad ïa u Khesed, bad ïa u Haso, bad ïa u Pildash, bad ïa u Jidlaph, bad ïa u Bethuel.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U Bethuel u la pynkha ïa ka Rebekka: ïa kine phra ngut ka Milkah ka la kha ïa u Nahor, u para u Abraham.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ka tnga kaba kham poh jong u, kaba ka kyrteng jong ka, ka la long “ka Reumah”, ka ruh ka la kha ïa u Tebah, bad ïa u Gaham, bad ïa u Thahash, bad ïa u Maakah."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ka rta ka Sara ka la long shispah arphew hynñiew snem: kine keiñ ki la long ki snem ka jingim jong ka Sara.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ka Sara ka la ïap noh ha Kirjath-arba; kaba long ka Hebron ha ka ri Kanaan: bad u Abraham u la wan ban leh sngewsih namar ka Sara, bad ban ïam namar jong ka.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Abraham u la ïeng noh joit na khmat ka metïap jong u, bad u la kren ruh de ha ki khun shynrang u Heth, u da ong,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Nga long u nongwei bad u nongwan hap hapdeng jong phi: to ai duh ha nga ïa ka jaka tep hapdeng jong phi, khnang ba ngan ïoh tep ïa la ka baïap na khmat jong nga.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te kita ki khun u Heth ki la ïathuh ha u Abraham, ki da ong,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “To sngap ïa ngi, ko kynrad jong nga: me long u syiem uba na U Blei hapdeng jong ngi: to tep ïa ka baïap jong me ha kaba jied ïa ka babha tam na ki jingtep jong ngi; ym don mano mano ruh na ngi u ban khang ïa la ka jingtep na me, ba men ïoh tep ïa ka baïap jong me.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abraham u la ïeng joit, bad u la nguh khlieh ïa lade ruh ïa ki trai kata ka khyndew, ha khmat keiñ ki khun shynrang u Heth.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u la kren ïasyllok bad ki, u da ong, “Lada phi mon ba ngan ïoh tep ïa ka baïap jong nga na khmat jong nga; to sngap ïa nga, bad to da ïakren kyrpad na ka bynta jong nga bad u Ephron u khun u Sohar;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ba un ai duh ha nga ïa kata ka krem Makhpelah ïa kaba u don, bad kaba long ha ka bakut ka lyngkha jong u; na ka bynta ka dor kaba dap biang ha ka rupa un ai duh ïa ka ha nga, ïa ka ban long ka jingïoh trai keiñ ka jaka jingtep ïa nga hapdeng jong phi.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Ephron u da shong hapdeng kita ki khun shynrang u Heth: bad uta u Ephron u khun u Heth u la ïathuh ha u Abraham ha kaba ki ïohsngew ki khun u Heth, ha khmat jong ki baroh keiñ, kat kiba la wan bsut ha ka khyrdop ka nongbah jong u, u da ong,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Em, ko kynrad jong nga, to sngew ïa nga: ïa kata ka lyngkha nga shu ai duh ha me, bad ïa kata ka krem ruh kaba hapoh jong ka, ha me keiñ nga ai duh ïa ka; ha khmat ki khun shynrang u paidlang jong nga, nga ai duh ïa ka ha me; to tep noh ïa ka baïap jong me.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Abraham u la nguh khlieh ïa lade ha khmat ki trai jong kata ka ri.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u la kren ha u Ephron ha kaba ki da ïohsngew ki trai jong kata ka ri, u da ong, “Hynrei, lada men ai duh ïa ka, to sngew ïa nga, nga kyrpad ïa me: ngan ai ha me ïa ka dor rupa jong kata ka lyngkha; to shim ïa ka na nga, bad ngan tep noh ïa ka baïap jong nga hangta.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Ephron u la ïathuh ha u Abraham, u da ong ha u,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Ko kynrad, to sngew ïa nga: ka khyndew kaba sawspah shekel ha ka rupa; kata ka long aïu eh hapdeng jong nga bad me? To tep noh namar kata ïa ka baïap jong me.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u Abraham ynda u la ïohsngew ïa u Ephron, u la thew ïa kita ki rupa ha u Ephron, kumba u la lah ong hi ha kaba ki da ïohsngew kita ki khun shynrang u Heth, ïa sawspah shekel ha ka rupa kiba ïaid biang keiñ bad ki nongkhaïi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumta, la pynïoh skhem ïa kata ka lyngkha u Ephron, kaba ha Makhpelah, kaba marpyrshah ïa ka shnong Mamre, ïa kata ka lyngkha bad ïa kata ka krem ruh kaba hapoh jong ka, bad ïa ki dieng baroh katba don ha kata ka lyngkha, bad hapoh ki pud jong ka baroh sawdong,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ïa ka ban long ka jingïoh trai ïa u Abraham ha khmat kita ki khun shynrang u Heth, bad ha khmat baroh keiñ kat kiba la leit bsut ha ka khyrdop ka nongbah jong u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ynda kumta, u Abraham u la tep noh ïa ka Sara ka tnga jong u ha kata ka krem jong ka lyngkha ka Makhpelah, marpyrshah ïa ka Mamre: kaba long keiñ ka Hebron ha ka ri Kanaan.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ïa kata ka lyngkha, bad ïa kata ka krem ruh kaba hapoh jong ka, la pynïoh skhem ïa u Abraham ïa ka ban long ka jingïoh trai ka jaka jingtep ïa u na ki khun shynrang u Heth."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Abraham u la tymmen, ki sngi ka rta jong u ki la dier bun eh: bad U Trai u la lah kyrkhu ïa u ha kiei kiei baroh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Abraham u la ong ha la u shakri uba kham shuwa eh ka rta ha ka ïing jong u, bad uba synshar halor kiei kiei baroh katba u don, “To buh, nga kyrpad ïa me, ïa la ka kti hapoh ka ksang lbong jong nga:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ngan pynsmai ïa me da U Trai uba U Blei jong ka bneng, bad U Blei jong ka khyndew, ba men ym shim ka tnga ïa u khun jong nga na ki khun kynthei jong ki kynja Kanaan, kiba nga shong sah hapdeng jong ki:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> hynrei, men leit sha ka ri jong nga, bad sha ki parakher paramer jong nga hi, bad men shim ka tnga ïa u Isaak u khun jong nga nangta keiñ.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad uta u shakri u la ong ha u, “Lehse kata ka briew kam mon ban wan bud ïa nga sha kane ka ri: hato ka dei shisha ba ngan leit ïalam pat ïa u khun jong me sha kata ka ri na kaba me la wan noh?”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Abraham u la ïathuh ha u, “To sumar ba men ym ïalam pat shatai ïa u khun jong nga.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Trai uba U Blei jong ka bneng uba la shim noh ïa nga na ka ïing u kpa jong nga, bad na ka ri ki kur jong nga, bad uba la ïakren bad nga, bad uba la smai ruh ha nga, u da ong, ‘Ha u symbai jong me ngan ai duh ïa kane ka khyndew;’ un phah ïa la u angel ha shuwa jong me, bad me ruh men shim ka tnga ïa u khun jong nga nangtai keiñ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, lada kata ka briew kam da mon ban wan bud ïa me, me te men long ba la khuid na kane ka jingsmai jong nga: tangba men ym ïalam pat ïa u khun jong nga shatai.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te uta u shakri u la buh ïa la ka kti hapoh ka ksang lbong u Abraham u kynrad jong u, bad u la smai ha u shaphang kane ka kam.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad uta u shakri u la shim shiphew tylli ki ut na ki ut u kynrad jong u, bad u la leit noh; bad na kiei kiei baroh kiba kham bha ba dei ïa u kynrad jong u ha la ka kti: bad u la khie, bad u la leit noh sha ka ri Mesopotamia, sha ka shnong u Nahor.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u la pyndem khohsiew ïa kita ki ut shabar kata ka shnong hajan ka pukri tong um la janmiet, hamar ka por ba ki ju wan ki kynthei ban tong um.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U la duwai te, “Ko Trai uba U Blei u Abraham u kynrad jong nga, nga kyrpad ïa me, to pyllaitluid bha ïa ka lynti ha khmat jong nga ha kane ka sngi, bad to pyni ïa ka jinglehsbun ïa u Abraham u kynrad jong nga.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ha khmih, nga ïeng hangne hajan kane ka pukri tong um; bad ki khun kynthei ki trai jong kane ka shnong ki ïawan ïa ka ban tong um.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> To shah ba kan jia ruh, ba kata ka samla ha kaba ngan ong, ‘To da pynhiar noh ïa la u khiew, nga kyrpad ïa pha, ba ngan ïoh dih;’ te lada kan ong, ‘To dih, bad ïa ki ut jong me ruh ngan ai ban dih;’ to ai ba kata kan long ïa kaba me la thmu ïa u Isaak u shakri jong me; bad na kata keiñ, ngan ïoh tip ba me la pyni ïa ka jinglehsbun ïa u kynrad jong nga.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba um pat la lah wai ban kren; ba ha khmih, ka Rebekka ka la wan mih noh, ïa kaba la kha ïa u Bethuel, u khun ka Milkah, ka tnga u Nahor, u para u Abraham, bad u khiew tong um jong ka ha la ka tyrpeng.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad kata ka samla ka la long kaba ibhabriew eh, ka theisotti keiñ, namar uno uno ruh em u briew um shym la ithuh ïa ka: bad ka la leit hiar sha kata ka pukri, bad ynda ka la pyndap ïa la u khiew tong um, ka la wan kiew pat.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te uta u shakri u la phet ban ïashem bad ka, bad u la ong ruh, “To shah ïa nga mynta, nga kyrpad ïa pha, ban shu kjit khyndiat ka um na u khiew um jong pha.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ka te ka la ong, “To dih, ko kynrad”: bad ka la pynkloi, bad ka la pynhiar noh ïa la u khiew um ha la ka kti bad ka la ai ha u ban dih.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ynda ka la lah ai ha u ban dih, ka la ong, “Ngan da tong um ïa ki ut jong me ruh, ha ban da ki la kdang.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ka la pynkloi, bad ka la theh lut ïa la u khiew um ha ka shyngoid, bad ka la phet biang pat sha kata ka pukri ban tong um, bad ka la tong um kumta ïa ki ut jong u baroh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad uta u briew ba u da iphylla ïa ka u da sngap jar noh, ïa ka ban tip lada U Trai u la lah pynman bha ne em ïa ka jingwan jong u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ynda ki la lah dih kita ki ut, ba uta u briew u la shim ïa ka nod ksiar kawei, kaba shong kumba shiteng tola, bad ïa ki ar tylli ki khadu ïa ki ryndang kti jong ka kiba shong kumba shiphew tola da ka ksiar;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad u la kylli, “Hato pha long ka khun jongno? to ïathuh ha nga mynta, nga kyrpad ïa pha: don ka jaka ne em ha ïing u kpa jong pha ba ngin ïashong basa?”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ka te ka la ïathuh ha u, “Ma nga, nga long ka khun u Bethuel u khun ka Milkah, ïa uba ka la kha ïa u Nahor.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ka la nang ïathuh ha u, “Ngi don u skum phlang bad u stait bam ba dap biang, bad ka jaka ïa ka ban shong basa ruh de.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad uta u briew u la nguh la ka khlieh, bad u la mane ïa U Trai.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u la ong, “To long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai uba U Blei u Abraham u kynrad jong nga, u bym shym la shim noh khoit ïa la ka jingleh isynei bad ïa la ka jingneh shisha na u kynrad jong nga: mynba nga dang long keiñ ha ka lynti, U Trai u la ïalam ïa nga sha ka ïing ki hynmen hynbew u kynrad jong nga.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad kata ka samla ka la phet, bad ka la ïathuh ha ka ïing ka kmie jong ka ïa kine kiei kiei ruh katba long.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ka Rebekka ka la don u hynmen, bad ka kyrteng jong u ka la long “u Laban”: bad u Laban u la phet shabar sha uta u briew, haduh ka pukri.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ynda u la ïohi ïa kata ka nod ksiar khmut, bad ïa kita ki khadu ha ki ryndang kti ka para jong u, bad ynda u la ïohsngew ïa ki ktien ka Rebekka ka para jong u, ba ka da ong, “Kumne u la kren uta u briew ha nga”; ba u ruh u la leit jang jang sha uta u briew; bad ha khmih, u dang ïeng bad kita ki ut hajan kata ka pukri.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u la ong, “To ale wan shapoh ïing, me uba la kyrkhu jong U Trai; balei me ïeng shabar? namar nga la lah pynkhreh ïa ka ïing, bad ïa ka jaka ruh ïa kita ki ut.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te uta u briew u la leit shapoh ka ïing: bad u Laban u la phah law panpoh ïa kita ki ut jong u, bad u la ai ruh ïa ka skum phlang bad ïa ka jingbam stait ha kita ki ut, bad ïa ka um ban sait ïa ki sla'jat jong u, bad ïa ki sla'jat jong kita ki briew kiba don lem bad u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u la buh ei ei ruh ha khmat jong u ban bam: te uta u briew u la ong, “Ngan ym bam keiñ, tad ynda nga la ïathuh ïa ki ktien ba nga donkam ban kren.” U te u la ong, “To da ïathuh noh.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u la ong, “Nga long u shakri jong u Abraham.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad U Trai u la kyrkhu shibun eh ïa u kynrad jong nga, bad u la man bakhraw: bad u la ai ha u ïa ki kynhun langbrot, bad ïa ki kynhun masi bad ïa ka rupa, bad ïa ka ksiar, bad ïa ki shakri shynrang, bad ki shakri kynthei, bad ïa ki ut, bad ïa ki kadda ruh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad ka Sara ruh ka tnga u kynrad jong nga ka la kha ïa u khun ïa u kynrad jong nga ynda ka la lah tymmen: bad u la ai duh ha u ïa kiei kiei baroh katba u don.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad u kynrad jong nga u la pynsmai ïa nga, u da ong, ‘Men ym shim ka tnga ïa u khun jong nga na ki khun kynthei ki kynja Kanaan, kiba ha ka khyndew jong kiba nga shong sah:",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> hynrei, men leit sha ka ïing u kpa jong nga, bad sha ki kur jong nga bad men shim ka tnga ïa u khun jong nga.’",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te nga la ong ha u kynrad jong nga, ‘Lehse kata ka briew kan ym wan bud ïa nga.’",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad u la ong ha nga, ‘U Trai, uba ha khmat jong U nga ïaid, un phah ïa la u angel lem bad me, bad un pynpoi bha ïa ka lynti jong me; bad men shim ka tnga ïa u khun jong nga na ki ba-ha-ïing jong nga hi, bad na ka ïing u kpa jong nga:",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> ynda kumta, men long ba lait khuid na ka jingsmai jong nga haba me leit poi sha kiba na ïing jong nga; te lada kim ai kawei ha me, me men lait khuid na ka jingsmai jong nga.’",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> “Te nga la wan poi sha kane ka pukri mynta ka sngi, bad nga la ong, ‘A Trai uba U Blei u Abraham u kynrad jong nga, lada mynta me pynpoi bha ïa ka lynti ha kaba nga ïaid:",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> ha khmih, nga ïeng mynta hajan kane ka pukri um; to shah ba kan jia, ba kata ka samla ka ban sa wan ïa ka ban tong um, bad ha kaba ngan sa ong, “To shah, nga kyrpad ïa pha, ba ngan dih khyndiat na u khiew um jong pha;”",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> bad ba ka kan ïoh ong ha nga, “To ma me men dih, bad ïa ki ut jong me ruh ngan tong um:” to ai ba kata hi keiñ kan long ïa kaba U Trai u la thung shai ban long ka tnga ïa u khun u kynrad jong nga.’",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> “Te haba ngam pat la dep ong ïa kane ha la ka dohnud, ha khmih, ka Rebekka ka wan mih noh bad la u khiew um ha ka tyrpeng jong ka; bad ka la leit hiar sha kata ka pukri, bad ka la tong um ruh: ynda kumta, nga la ong ha ka, ‘To ai ha nga ban dih, nga kyrpad ïa pha.’",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ka te ka la pynkloi, bad ka la pynhiar ïa la u khiew um na la ka tyrpeng, bad ka da ong artad, ‘To dih, bad ha ki ut jong me ruh ngan ai ban dih:’ kumta keiñ, nga la dih, bad ka la pyndih ïa ki ut ruh de.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Bad nga la kylli ïa ka, nga da ong, ‘Pha long ka khun jongno?’ Ka ruh ka la ïathuh, ‘Ka khun u Bethuel, u khun u Nahor, ïa uba ka Milkah ka la kha ïa u’: ynda kumta, nga la buh ïa ka nod khmut ksiar ha ka shyllangmat jong ka, bad ïa ki khadu ha ki ryndang kti jong ka.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Bad nga la nguh la ka khlieh, bad nga la mane ïa U Trai, bad nga la kyrkhu ïa U Trai uba U Blei u Abraham u kynrad jong nga, uba la ïalam ïa nga ha ka lynti kaba dei khnang ba ngan shim ïa ka khunruid u kynrad jong nga ïa u khun jong u.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Te mynta lada phi don ka mon ban leh ïa ka jingsbun bad ka jingshisha ïa u kynrad jong nga, to ïathuh ha nga: bad lada phim mon, to ïathuh keiñ ha nga, ba ngan ïoh phai shawei sha ka kti kamon, lane sha kadiang.”",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Ynda kumta, u Laban bad u Bethuel ki la ïathuh, ki da ong, “Kane shisha ka mih na U Trai: ngim lah ban ong ei ei pat ma ngi ha me lane ka basniew lane ka babha.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Ha khmih, ka Rebekka ka long ha khmat jong me, to shim ïa ka, bad to khie leit ruh, bad to ai ba kan long ka tnga ïa u khun u kynrad jong me, kumba la kren U Trai.”",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Te ynda u shakri jong u Abraham u la ïohsngew ïa kine ki ktien jong ki, u la nguh ngon ïa lade haduh ka khyndew ha khmat U Trai.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Bad uta u shakri u la sei noh ïa ki jingdeng rupa, bad ïa ki jingdeng ksiar, bad ïa ki jaiñkup, bad u la ai ïa ki ha ka Rebekka: bad ïa kiei kiei kiba kordor u la ai ha u hynmen jong ka bad ha ka kmie jong ka.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Bad ki la ïabam bad ki la ïadih: ma u bad kita ki briew kiba don ryngkat bad u; bad ki la ïasah baroh shi miet hangta; bad ki la ïakhie kum lashai mynstep, bad u la ong, “To phah noh ïa nga sha u kynrad jong nga.”",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Bad u hynmen jong ka Rebekka bad ka kmie jong ka ki la ïa-ong, “To shah ba kane ka samla kan sah lem bad ngi sa khyndiat sngi, haba kumno kumno ruh haduh shiphew sngi; hadien kata kan sa ïoh leit.”",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Hynrei, u la ïathuh ha ki, “Wat khang ïa nga mynta haba ïohi ba U Trai u la pynpoi bha ïa ka jingleit jong nga; to pyllait ïa nga keiñ ba ngan ïoh leit phai pat sha u kynrad jong nga.”",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Ki pat te ki la ïa-ong, “Ngin khot ïa kata ka samla, ba ngin ïakylli ïa ka hi.”",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la khot ïa ka Rebekka, bad ki la ïa-ong ha ka, “Pha mon ban leit noh bad une u briew?” Ka te ka la ïathuh, “Ngan leit noh keiñ.”",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Kumta, ki la ïapyllait noh ïa ka Rebekka ka para jong ki, bad ïa ka aïa jong ka, bad ïa u shakri u Abraham, bad ïa ki briew jong u.",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Bad ki la ïakyrkhu ïa ka Rebekka, bad ki la ong ha ka, “Pha long ka para jong ngi, to long ma pha ka kmie ïa ki hajar hajar bynriew, bad to ai ba u symbai jong pha un ïoh bat ïa ka khyrdop jong kita kiba shun ïa ki.”",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Ynda kumta, ka Rebekka ka la mih noh, bad ki shakri kynthei jong ka, bad ki la ïashong halor kita ki ut, bad ki la leit ïabud ïa uta u briew: kumta, uta u shakri u la shim ïa ka Rebekka, bad u la leit noh.",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Bad u Isaak u wan ïaid na ka lynti ka pukri Lahai-roi; naba u la shong ha ka ri shathie.",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> Bad u Isaak u la leit ïaid kai shabar ïa ka ban pyrkhat ha ka lyngkha la janmiet: bad u la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad u la ïohi ruh, bad ha khmih, kita ki ut ki ïawan.",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> Bad ka Rebekka ruh ka la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad haba ka la ïohi ïa u Isaak, ka la hiar noh na kata ka ut.",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> Namar ka la lah kylli ha uta u shakri, “Hato uei une u briew uba wan ïaid kai ban ïashem bad ngi?” Bad uta u shakri ruh u la lah ong, “Une u long keiñ u kynrad jong nga:” bad ka la shim ïa ka jingkah, bad ka la pynkah ïa lade ruh.",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> Bad uta u shakri u la ïathuh ha u Isaak ïa kiei kiei baroh ba u la lah leh.",
			"67": "<sup>67</sup> Ynda kumta, u Isaak u la ïalam ïa ka shapoh ka ïingtrep jong ka Sara ka kmie jong u, bad u la shim ïa ka Rebekka, bad ka la long ka tnga jong u; bad u la ieit eh ïa ka: bad ïa u Isaak la pynsngewtngen shaphang ka kmie jong u."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Abraham u la shim sa kawei pat ka tnga, bad ka kyrteng jong ka, ka la long “ka Keturah”.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ïa u ka la kha ïa u Simran, bad ïa u Jokshan, bad ïa u Medan, bad ïa u Midian, bad ïa u Ishbak, bad ïa u Shuah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Jokshan u la pynkha ïa u Sheba, bad ïa u Dedan. Bad ki khun shynrang u Dedan ki la long ki Asshurim, bad ki Letushim, bad ki Leummim.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Midian ki la long u Ephah, bad u Epher, bad u Hanokh, bad u Abidah, bad u Eldaah. Te kine baroh ki la long ki khun shynrang ka Keturah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Abraham u la ai baroh katba u don ha u Isaak.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, ïa kita ki khun shynrang ba u Abraham u la ïoh na ki tnga ba kham poh jong u, u Abraham u la ai ïa ki jingai, bad u la phah noh ïa ki na u Isaak u khun jong u, mynba u dang im, shaphang mihngi, sha ka ri mihngi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kine mynta ki long ki sngi ki snem ka jingim baroh kawei jong u Abraham ïa kiba u la im, shispah hynñiewphew san snem.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Abraham u la ïap noh, u la ïap ruh ha ka jinglong tymmen ba la ïaw bha keiñ, bad u la hun tymmen ruh, ba u la dap da ki snem; bad la ïalum ïa u sha u paidlang jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Isaak bad u Ishmael ki khun jong u, ki la ïatep ïa u ha ka krem Makhpelah, ha ka lyngkha u Ephron u khun u Sohar u khun u Heth, kaba marpyrshah ïa ka Mamre;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> kaba long kata ka lyngkha ïa kaba u Abraham u la thied na ki khun shynrang u Heth: hangta la tep ïa u Abraham, bad ïa ka Sara ka tnga jong u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ynda la ïap u Abraham, U Blei u la kyrkhu ïa u Isaak u khun jong u; bad u Isaak u la shong sah hajan ka pukri Lahai-roi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad kine ki long ki jinghiar pateng bynriew jong u Ishmael, u khun u Abraham, ïa uba ka Hagar kaba ka kynja Ijipt, ka shakri ka Sara, ka la kha ïa u Abraham.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad kine ki long ki kyrteng jong ki khun shynrang u Ishmael, ha la ka kyrteng kyrteng, kat kumba la kha pateng ïa ki: u Nebaioth u khun nyngkong u Ishmael, bad u Kedar, bad u Abdeel, bad u Mibsam,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad u Mishma, bad u Dumah, bad u Massa,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> u Hadar, bad u Tema, u Jetur, u Naphish, bad u Kedemah.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Ishmael, bad kine keiñ ki long ki kyrteng jong ki, ha la ka shnong ka shnong, bad ha la ki kut; khat-ar ki syiem ha la ka jaid ka jaid bynriew.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad kine ki long ki snem ka jingim jong u Ishmael, shispah laiphew hynñiew snem: te u la kut noh ka mynsiem bad u la ïap noh; bad la lum ïa u ruh sha u paidlang jong u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki khun jong u ki la ïashong sah naduh ka ri Habilah haduh ka ri Shur, kaba ha khmat ka ri Ijipt, haba me ïaid ha ka lynti shaphang ka ri Assyria: namar la hap ban shongneh u Ishmael ha khmat ki para jong u baroh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad kine ki long ki jinghiar pateng u Isaak, u khun u Abraham: u Abraham u la pynkha ïa u Isaak,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad u Isaak u la long sawphew snem mynba u la shim ïa ka Rebekka ka khun u Bethuel, u kynja Syria na ka ri Padan-Aram, ka para u Laban u kynja Syria, ïa ka ban long ka tnga jong u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Isaak u la ïai-duwai ha U Trai na ka bynta ka tnga jong u, namar ba ka long kaba lyngki: bad U Trai u la shahshkor ïa u, te ka Rebekka ka tnga jong u ka la punkhun.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ki khun ki la khih ïaleh lem ha ka kpoh jong ka; ka te ka la ong, “Lada ka long kumta, hato balei ba nga long kumne?” Te ka la leit kylli ïa U Trai.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha ka, “Don ha ka kpoh jong pha ar ki jaid bynriew, bad ar ki paidbah keiñ kin sa ïakhlad noh ïa lade hi ha ka kpoh jong pha; bad uwei u paidlang un kham don bor ïa uta uwei pat; bad uta uba shuwa un shakri ïa uba hadien.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ynda la dap ki sngi jong ka, ïa ka ban kha, ha khmih, ar ngut bashong synrop ha ka kpoh jong ka.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad uba nyngkong u la mih noh uba saw baroh shimet kum ka jaiñkup ba shñiuh; bad ki la khot kyrteng “u Iso” ïa u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te hadien kata, la mih noh u para jong u, bad ka kti jong u ka da bat ïa u Iso na ka khongdong'jat jong u; nangta la khot kyrteng “u Jakob” ïa u: bad u Isaak u la long uba hynriewphew snem ka rta mynba ka la kha ïa ki.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad kita ki khynnah ki la nang san: bad u Iso u la long uba nang beh mrad, u briew uba ju ïaidwir eh ha madan; hynrei, u Jakob u la long u briew uba jemnud, uba shong ha la ki ïingtrep.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u Isaak u la ieit ïa u Iso, namar ka doh skei jong u ba u la ju bam: hynrei, ka Rebekka ka la ieit ïa u Jakob.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u Jakob u la shet ïa ka jingshet syrwa: hadien kata, u Iso u la wan na lyngkha, bad u la sngewthait lwait ruh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Iso u la ong ha u Jakob, “To shah ïa nga ban bam, nga kyrpad ïa me, na kata kaba saw saw, naba nga sngewjrem eh:” namar kata la khot “u Edom” ïa u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te u Jakob u la ong, “To die noh ha nga ha kane ka sngi ïa ka hok ka jinglong hynmen jong me.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u Iso u la ong, “Ha khmih, ngan sa ïap noh: bad kan myntoi aïu ïa nga kane ka hok ka jinglong hynmen?”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u Jakob u la ong, “To smai ha nga mynta ka sngi;” u te u la smai ha u: bad u la die noh ïa ka hok ka jinglong hynmen jong u ha u Jakob.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u Jakob u la ai ha u Iso ïa u kpu bad ïa ka jingshet syrwa da u kynja ri; u ruh u la bam bad u la dih, bad u la ïeng joit, bad u la leit noh ruh: kumta, u Iso u la ibeiñ ïa ka hok ka jinglong hynmen jong u."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ka la don ka 'nemsniew ha kata ka ri nalor kata ka 'nemsniew kaba la don mynshuwa ha ki sngi jong u Abraham. Bad u Isaak u la leit sha u Abimelekh u syiem ki Philistia sha Gerar.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad U Trai u la paw ha u, bad u la ong, “Wat leit hiar sha ka ri Ijipt; to shong sah ha kata ka ri ïa kaba ngan ong ha me.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> To shong nongwei katto katne ha kane ka ri, bad nga te ngan long lem bad me, bad ngan kyrkhu ïa me; namar ha me, bad ha u symbai jong me, ngan ai ïa kine ki ri baroh, bad ngan pyndep skhem ïa la ka jingsmai ïa kaba nga la smai ha u Abraham u kpa jong me.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ngan pynbun ïa u symbai jong me kum ki khlur bneng, bad ngan ai ha u symbai jong me ïa kine ki ri baroh; bad ïa ki jaid bynriew baroh ka pyrthei yn kyrkhu ha u symbai jong me;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> namar ba u Abraham u la shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong nga, bad ba u la sumar ïa kaba nga la hukum ïa u ban sumar ïa ki hukum jong nga, ïa ki rukom jong nga, bad ïa ki tynrai ka jingsneng jong nga.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Isaak u la shong sah ha Gerar.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki briew jong kata ka jaka ki la kylli shaphang ka tnga jong u; u te u la ïathuh, “Ka long ka para jong nga keiñ:” naba u la sheptieng ban phla, “Ka long ka tnga jong nga;” u ong “ba ïoh ki briew jong kata ka jaka kin da pynïap noh ïa nga namar ka Rebekka; namar ka la long kaba ibhabriew.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ynda u la don kham bun sngi hangta, ba u Abimelekh u syiem jong ki Philistia u la khmih na ka jingkhang ïit, bad u la ïohi ruh, bad ha khmih, u Isaak u da lehkai bad ka Rebekka ka tnga jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Abimelekh u la khot ïa u Isaak, bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, shisha ka long ka tnga jong me: hato kumno te me la ong, ‘Ka long ka para jong nga?’ ” Te u Isaak u la ïathuh ha u, “Namar nga la ong ha lade, ‘Ba ïoh nga ïap namar jong ka.’ ”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Abimelekh u la ong, “Hato kaei kane ba me la leh ïa ngi? da kaba jem uwei na u paidlang un da lah thiah lem bad ka tnga jong me, bad kumta keiñ, me men da la pynngat ka jingrem halor jong ngi.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Abimelekh, namar kata, u la hukum ïa uta u paidlang baroh, u da ong, “Uta uba ktah ïa une u briew lane ïa ka tnga jong u, yn pynïap noh shisha ïa u.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Isaak u la bet ha kata ka khyndew, bad u la ïoh kynshew ha kata ka snem ïa kaba shispah shah. Bad U Trai u la kyrkhu ïa u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad uta u briew u la man bha, bad u la nang kham khraw kham khraw, bad u la nang roi ruh ha ban da u la jia long uba khraw eh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Namar u la don ruh ka spah da ki kynhun langbrot, bad ka spah da ki kynhun masi, bad ki shakri shynrang batrei lyngkha babun eh; katba ki Philistia ki la ïabishni ïa u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Namar kita ki pukri baroh ïa kiba ki shakri u kpa jong u ki la lah ïatih myn ha ki sngi u Abraham u kpa jong u, kita ki Philistia ki la ïaset noh ïa ki, bad ki la ïa-pyndap ïa ki da ka khyndew keiñ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Abimelekh u la ong ha u Isaak, “To khie kynriah noh na ngi; naba me la nang long uba kham don bor shibun ïa ngi.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, u Isaak u la kynriah noh nangta, bad u la pynïeng ïa la ka ïingtrep ha ka pynthor Gerar, bad u la shong sah shato.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Isaak u la phah tih biang ïa kita ki pukri um, ïa kiba ki la lah ïatih myn ha ki sngi u Abraham u kpa jong u; naba kita ki Philistia ki la lah set noh ïa ki, ynda la ïap u Abraham: bad u la buh ïa kijuh ki kyrteng ha ki da kiba u kpa jong u, u la lah khot ïa ki.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad kumta, ki shakri u Isaak ki la ïatih ha kata ka pynthor, bad ki la ïashem hangta ka pukri ka um bakyrsoi im.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki nongap jingri ka Gerar ki la ïakajia bad ki nongap jingri u Isaak, ki da ong, “Ka um ka dei ka jong ngi:” namar kata, u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka pukri “ka Esek”; naba ki la ïakajia bad u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki la ïatih sa ïa kawei pat ka pukri, bad shaphang kata ruh ki la ïakajia: namar kata, u la khot kyrteng ïa ka, “ka Sitnah”.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, te u la kynriah noh nangta, bad u la tih ïa kawei pat ka pukri; hynrei, kim shym la ïakajia shaphang kata: te u la khot kyrteng “ka Rehoboth” ïa ka; bad u la ong, “Naba mynta ba U Trai u la pynkylluid ïa ngi, ngin ïa nang roi ruh ha kane ka khyndew.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la leit kiew nangta sha Beer-sheba.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad U Trai u la mihpaw ha u ha kata ka miet, bad u la ong, “Nga long U Blei u Abraham u kpa jong me: to wat sheptieng, naba ma nga, nga long ryngkat bad me bad ngan kyrkhu ïa me, bad ngan pynroi ïa u symbai jong me na ka bynta u Abraham u shakri jong nga.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u la tei ïa ka duwan hangta, bad u la khot kyrpad ïa ka kyrteng U Trai, bad u la pynïeng ïa la ka ïingtrep ruh hangta: bad hangta ki shakri jong u Isaak ki la ïatih ïa ka pukri.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u Abimelekh u la leit sha u na Gerar, bad u Ahussath u lok jong u, bad u Phikhol u nongïalam barangbah u paidïapom jong u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u Isaak u la ong ha ki, “Hato balei phi wan ha nga, haba phi la isih ïa nga, bad haba phi la beh noh ïa nga na phi?”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ki te ki la ïathuh, “Shisha ngi la ïohi ba U Trai u long ryngkat bad me: te ngi la ïa-ong, ‘Mynta to ai ba kan long ka jingsmai hapdeng jong ngi, hapdeng jong ngi bad me keiñ, to ïa ngin ïathaw ka jutang bad me,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ba men ym leh sniew ïa ngi, kumba ma ngi ngim shym la ktah ïa me, bad kumba ngi ngim shym la leh ei ei ruh em, hynrei, tang ïa ka babha ïa me, bad ngi la phah noh ïa me ruh ha ka jingsuk: me long mynta ïa uba la kyrkhu da U Trai.’ ”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka jingkhawai ïa ki, bad ki la ïabam ki la ïadih ruh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïakhie joit dang step eh, bad ki la ïasmai biang paralok hi: bad u Isaak u la phah noh ïa ki, bad ki la ïaleit noh ruh na u ha kaba suk.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha kata kajuh ka sngi, ba ki shakri u Isaak ki la wan ïathuh ha u shaphang ka pukri ïa kaba ki la lah ïatih, bad ki la ong ruh ha u, “Ngi la shem ïa ka um.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u la khot “ka Sheba” ïa ka: namar kata, ka kyrteng kata ka shnong ka long “ka Beer-sheba” haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u Iso u la long uba sawphew snem, bad u la shim tnga ïa ka Judith ka khun u Beeri u kynja Hit, bad ïa ka Bashemath ka khun u Elon u kynja Hit:",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> te kita ki la long kaba kthang mynsiem ïa u Isaak bad ïa ka Rebekka."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ba haba la tymmen u Isaak, bad ba ki khmat jong u ki la byrngut, katba um imat shynna shuh, ba u la khot ïa u Iso u khun u banyngkong jong u, bad u la ong ha u, “Ko khun”; u te u la ong ha u, “Ha khmih, ma nga.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la ong, “Ha khmih mynta, nga la tymmen, bad ïa ka sngi ka jingïap jong nga ngam tip.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad mynta te, to shim, nga kyrpad ïa me, ïa la ki atiar, ïa la ka ryngkap bad ïa la ka ryntieh keiñ, bad to khie leit sha ka lyngkha, bad to kem ka doh skei ïa nga,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad to shet ïa nga ïa ka jingbam ka babang, katba nga sngewbrai hi ban bam, bad to wallam ruh ha nga, ba ngan ïoh bam ba ka mynsiem jong nga kan ïoh kyrkhu ïa me mynshuwa ba ngan ïap noh.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ka Rebekka ka la ïohsngew mynba u Isaak u la kren ha u Iso u khun jong u. Bad u Iso u la leit noh sha ka lyngkha ïa ka ban beh skei, ba un ïoh wallam.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, ka Rebekka ka la ong ha u Jakob u khun jong ka, ka da ong, “Ha khmih, nga la ïohsngew ïa u kpa jong me ba u da kren ha u Iso u hynmen jong me, u da ong,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ‘To wallam ha nga ïa ka doh mrad, bad to shet ïa nga ïa ka jingbam ka babang, ba ngan ïoh bam, bad ba ngan ïoh kyrkhu ïa me ha khmat U Trai shuwa ba ngan ïap noh.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te mynta, ko khun, to sngew ïa ka ktien jong nga shaphang kata ïa kaba ngan sa hukum ïa me.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> To khie leit mynta sha ka kynhun blang, bad to wallam nangta ha nga ïa ar tylli ki khun blang shynrang ki basngaid bha; bad nga ruh ngan shet ïa ka jingbam ka babang da ki, ïa u kpa jong me, katba u sngewbha eh hi keiñ;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad me men leit ai ïa ka ha u kpa jong me, ba un ïoh bam, bad ba un ïoh kyrkhu ïa me mynshuwa ba u ïap noh.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Jakob u la ong ha ka Rebekka ka kmie jong u, “Ha khmih, u Iso u hynmen jong nga u long u briew ba-mih shñiuh eh ha u, haba ma nga, nga long u briew u bajlih:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> u kpa jong nga lehse un tba ïa nga, te ngan long kum u nongshukor ha khmat jong u; kumta, ngan pynwan hiar halor jong nga hi ïa ka jingtim, bad ym ïa ka jingkyrkhu.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, ka kmie jong u ka la ong ha u, “To ai ba ka jingtim jong me kan long halor jong nga ko khun: tang ba men shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong nga, bad to khie leit wallam ïa ki ha nga.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U te u la leit, bad u la shim ïa ki khun blang, bad u la wallam ïa ki sha la ka kmie: bad ka kmie jong u ka la shet ïa ka jingbam ka babang, katba u sngewbha eh hi u kpa jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ka Rebekka ka la shim ïa ki jaiñkup kiba itynnad eh ki jong u Iso u khun banyngkong jong ka kiba la don bad ka ha ïing, bad ka la pynkup ïa ki ha u Jakob u khun bakhatduh jong ka;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ha ki kti jong u, bad ha ka bajlih ka ryndang jong u, ka la buh ïa ki snieh jong kita ki khun blang;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad ka la ai ïa kata ka jingbam ka babang bad ïa u kpu ïa kiba ka la lah shet lypa, ha ka kti u Jakob u khun jong ka.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u la leit bsut sha la u kpa, bad u la ong, “Ko kpa”: u te u la ong, “Ha khmih ma nga; me long uei, ko khun?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Jakob u la ong ha la u kpa, “Nga long u Iso u khun uba la kha nyngkong jong me; nga la leh keiñ kumba me la bthah ha nga: to da khie, nga kyrpad ïa me, to shong to bam ruh na ka doh beh mrad jong nga, ba ka mynsiem jong me kan ïoh kyrkhu ïa nga.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Isaak u la ong ha la u khun, “Kumno ko khun, ba me la shem ïa ka shen katta katta?” U te u la ong, “Namar ba U Trai uba U Blei jong me u la pynwan ïa ka ha khmat jong nga.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Isaak u la ong ha u Jakob, “To ale kham hajan mynta, ba ngan ïoh tba ïa me ko khun, la shisha me long u Iso u khun jong nga ne em.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Jakob u la leit kham hajan u Isaak u kpa jong u; u te u la tba ïa u, bad u la ong, “Ka ktien ka long ka ktien u Jakob, hynrei, ki kti ki long ki kti u Iso keiñ.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te um shym lah ithuh ïa u, namar ba ki kti jong u ki la long kiba shñiuh, kum ki kti u Iso: namar kata, u la kyrkhu ïa u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U la ong ruh, “Shisha me long u Iso u khun jong nga hi?” U ruh u la ïathuh, “Nga long keiñ.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong, “To wallam hajan jong nga bad to ai ba ngan bam na ka doh skei u khun jong nga, ba ka mynsiem jong nga kan ïoh kyrkhu ïa me.” Te u la wallam hajan jong u bad u la bam: bad u la wallam ïa ka umsoh Waiñ ha u bad u la dih.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ynda kumta, u Isaak u kpa jong u, u la ong ha u, “To ale hajan mynta, bad to doh ïa nga ko khun.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u la wan hajan, bad u la doh ïa u: bad u la iw ïa ka jingiw ki jaiñkup jong u, bad u la kyrkhu ruh ïa u, bad u da ong, “Ha khmih, ka jingiw u khun jong nga ka long kum ka jingiw ka lyngkha ïa kaba U Trai u la kyrkhu!",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, to long ba U Blei un da ai ha me na ka umjer bneng, bad na ka jingsngaid ka khyndew, bad ka bun byrhien na u Kew bad ka umsoh Waiñ:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> to long ba ki paidlang kin ïashakri ïa me, bad ki jaid bynriew kin ïadem khrup ha me: to long u trai halor la ki para, bad to long ba ki khun shynrang ka kmie jong me kin dem khrup ha me: uta uba tim ïa me un long uba la shah tim hi, bad uta uba kyrkhu ïa me un long uba la shah kyrkhu hi.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ynda u Isaak u la lah wai noh ban kyrkhu ïa u Jakob, bad tang shu lah mih noh shabar u Jakob na khmat u Isaak u kpa jong u, ba u Iso ruh, u hynmen jong u, u la wan na la kaba beh mrad.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u ruh de u la lah shet ïa ka jingbam ka babang bad u la wallam ïa ka ha la u kpa, bad u la ong ha la u kpa, “To ai ba un khie u kpa jong nga, ba un bam ruh na ka doh skei u khun jong u, ba ka mynsiem jong me kan ïoh kyrkhu ïa nga.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u Isaak u kpa jong u, u la ong ha u, “Me uei?” U te u la ïathuh, “Nga long u khun jong me, uba la kha nyngkong jong me keiñ, u Iso.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u Isaak u la sngewkhynñiuh da ka jingkhynñiuh bakhraw eh, bad u la kylli, “Uei? Ha-ei uta uba la beh ïa ka doh skei, bad ba la wallam ha nga, ma nga te nga la bam na ka baroh mynshuwa ba la poi ma me, bad nga la kyrkhu ïa u? shisha keiñ, un long ruh uta ïa uba la kyrkhu.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u Iso ynda u la ïohsngew ïa ki ktien jong u kpa, u la kyang da ka jingkyang kaba khraw bad ka bakthang eh, bad u la ong ha la u kpa, “To kyrkhu ïa nga, ho-oid keiñ ïa nga ruh, ko kpa.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te u la ïathuh, “U para jong me u la wan da ka jingshukor, bad u la shim noh ïa ka jingkyrkhu jong me.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> U Iso te u la ïathuh, “Kam long kaba dei eh ba la khot kyrteng ïa u, ‘u Jakob’ mo? Naba u la shukor ïa nga mynta la ar sien: ïa ka hok ka jinglong hynmen jong nga u la lah shim noh; bad ha khmih, mynta pat, u la knieh noh ïa ka jingkyrkhu jong nga.” Bad u la ong, “Mem shym la buh kyrpang ïa nga ruh ïa ka jingkyrkhu?”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad u Isaak u la ïathuh, u da ong ha u Iso, “Ha khmih, nga la pynlong u trai ïa u halor jong me, bad nga la ai ha u ïa ki hynmen hynbew baroh jong u ba kin long ki shakri jong u; bad da u Kew bad ka umsoh Waiñ nga la kyrshan ïa u: te ha me mynta, ngan leh aïu pat ko khun?”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad u Iso u la kylli ha la u kpa, “Me don tang kawei ka jingkyrkhu, ko kpa? To kyrkhu ïa nga, ho-oid keiñ ïa nga ruh de, ko kpa.” Bad u Iso u la kyang eh, bad u la ïam ruh.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te u Isaak u kpa jong u, u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha u, “Ha khmih, ka jaka shong sah jong me kan long na ka jingsngaid ka khyndew bad na kaba hap ka umjer ki bneng na jrong;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> bad da la ka waitlam men im, bad ïa la u para men shakri; kan jia ruh haba la ïoh jop ma me, ba men pynkheiñ ïa ka lyngkor jong u na la ka ryndang.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te u Iso u la isih ïa u Jakob namar kata ka jingkyrkhu da kaba u kpa jong u, u lah kyrkhu ïa u: bad u Iso u la ong ha la ka dohnud, “Ki sngi ban ïambriew ïa i pa ki la jan; hadien kata, nga, ngan da pynïap noh ïa u Jakob u para jong nga.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ynda kumta, la ïathuh ha ka Rebekka ïa kine ki ktien u Iso u khun banyngkong jong ka: te ka la phah khot ïa u Jakob u khun bakhatduh jong ka, bad ka la ong ha u, “Ha khmih, u Iso u hynmen jong me, u pynshngain ïa lade shaphang jong me, ha ka jingkyrmen ba un ïoh pynïap noh ïa me.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te mynta, ko khun, to sngew ïa ka ktien jong nga; to da mih noh, to da phet rieh sha u Laban u hynmen jong nga, sha Haran",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> bad to da shong lem bad u khyndiat sngi tad ynda ka phai noh ka jingkhih bitar u hynmen jong me;",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> tad ynda ka jingbitar u hynmen jong me ka phai noh keiñ na me, bad ba u la klet noh ïa kata ïa kaba me la leh ïa u: hadien kata, ngan phah shaw pat ïa me nangta shane: hato balei yn shim noh na nga ïa phi baroh ar ngut ruh ha kawei ka sngi?”",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Bad ka Rebekka ka la ong ha u Isaak, “Nga pynkhuslai ïa la ka jingim namar kita ki khun kynthei u Heth: lada u Jakob un shim ka tnga ïa lade na ki khun kynthei u Heth, kumba long kine ki khun kynthei jong kane ka ri, nga dang donkam aïu shuh ïa la ka jingim?”"
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Isaak u la khot ha lade ïa u Jakob, bad u la kyrkhu ïa u, bad u la adong ruh ïa u, bad u la ong ha u, “Wat shim ka tnga ha lade na ki khun kynthei ki kynja Kanaan.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> To khie da leit noh sha ka ri Padan-Aram sha ka ïing u Bethuel u kpa ka kmie jong me; bad to shim ka tnga ïa lade nangta na ki khun kynthei u Laban u hynmen ka kmie jong me.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad U Blei U Badonbor Baroh un da kyrkhu ïa me, bad un da pynkharoi ïa me, bad un da pynlong bun ruh ïa me, ba men ïoh long ka jingïalang ki paidbah.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad un ai ha me ïa ka jingkyrkhu u Abraham: ha me bad ha u symbai jong me lem bad me; ba men ïoh pateng ïa ka ri ka jingwan hap jong me, ïa kaba U Blei u la ai duh ha u Abraham.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, u Isaak u la phah noh ïa u Jakob: bad u la leit sha Padan-Aram, sha u Laban u khun u Bethuel u kynja Syria, u hynmen ka Rebekka, ka kmie u Jakob bad u Iso.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba u Iso u la ïohi ba u Isaak u la lah kyrkhu ïa u Jakob, bad ba u la phah noh ïa u sha Padan-Aram, ba un shim tnga ïa lade nangta; bad ba u la adong ïa u, haba u dang kyrkhu ïa u, u da ong, “Men ym shim ka tnga na ki khun kynthei ki kynja Kanaan,”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad ba u Jakob u la sngew ïa u kpa jong u bad ïa ka kmie jong u, bad ba u la leit noh sha Padan-Aram.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Iso ba u da ïohi ba kita ki khun kynthei ki kynja Kanaan ki long ki basniew ha khmat u Isaak u kpa jong u,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> te u Iso u la leit sha ïing u Ishmael, bad u la shim ïa ka Mahalath ka khun u Ishmael, u khun u Abraham, kaba long ka para jong u Nebaioth, sha kita ki tnga ïa kiba u don lypa keiñ ba kan long ka tnga jong u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jakob u la leit noh na Beer-sheba, bad u leit shaphang ka shnong Haran.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u lap ba poi ha kata kawei ka jaka, bad u la sah miet hangta naba la sep ka sngi; bad u la shim na ki maw jong kata ka jaka ïa ka ban pynlong ïa la ka syngkhlieh, bad u la ïohthiah ha kata ka jaka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u la phohsniew ruh, bad ha khmih ka jingkieng ba la thung ha ka khyndew, kaba ka khlieh jong ka, ka da kot haduh ka bneng: bad ha khmih ruh ki angel U Blei ki da ïakiew bad ïahiar ha ka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ha khmih, U Trai u la ïeng haneng jong ka, bad u la ong, “Nga long U Trai uba U Blei u Abraham u kpa jong me, bad U Blei u Isaak: kane ka khyndew ha kaba me thiah, ha me ngan ai duh ïa ka, bad ha u symbai jong me;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad u symbai jong me un long kum ka 'dewmet ka khyndew, bad men sapait saphriang noh sha sepngi, bad sha mihngi, bad sha shatei, bad sha shathie: bad ha me yn long ba la kyrkhu ïa ki jaid bynriew baroh ka pyrthei bad ha u symbai jong me.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ha khmih, ma nga, nga don lem bad me, bad ngan ri bha ïa me hangno hangno ruh kat shaba me leit, bad ngan ïalam biang ïa me sha kane ka ri; naba ngan ym iehnoh ïa me, tad ynda nga la lah pyndep ïa kaba nga la ong ha me.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Jakob u la kyndit thiah, bad u la ong, “Shisha U Trai u don ha kane ka jaka; bad ma nga ngam shym la tip ïa kata.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u la sngewsheptieng, bad u la ong, “A katno kaba shyrkhei kane ka jaka! ym don hangne, hynrei, tang ka ïing U Blei hi, bad kane ka long ka khyrdop ka bneng.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Jakob u la khie dang step phyrngab, bad u la shim ïa uta u maw da uba u la lah pynlong syngkhlieh ïa lade, bad u la thung mawbynna ruh ïa u bad u la theh ka umphniang ha kliar jong u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “ka Bethel”: hynrei, “ka Lus” ka la ju long ka kyrteng kata ka nongbah mynnyngkong.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jakob u la kular skhem ïa ka kular, u da ong, “Lada U Blei un long ryngkat bad nga, bad un sumar ïa nga ha kane ka lynti ha kaba nga nang leit, bad un ai ha nga ïa u kpu ban bam, bad ïa ki jaiñkup ban kup,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad ba ngan ïoh wan poi pat da kaba suk sha ïing u kpa jong nga, U Trai un long U Blei jong nga,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> ynda kumta keiñ, une u maw, ïa uba nga la thung mawbynna ïa u, un long ka ïing U Blei: bad na kiei kiei baroh ba men ai ha nga, nga ruh ngan ai shisha ha me ïa kaba shiphew bynta.”"
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Jakob u la nang leit la ka jingleit, bad u la leit poi sha ka ri ki khun ka ri mihngi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la khmih, te ha khmih kawei ka pukri ha ka lyngkha, bad ha khmih, la don lai ki kynhun langbrot kiba dem hajan jong ka; naba na kata ka pukri ki la ju ai um ïa kita ki kynhun langbrot: bad la don u maw bakhraw ha ka shyntur kata ka pukri.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad hangta la ïalang kita ki kynhun langbrot baroh: bad ki la ïa-pyntyllun noh ïa uta u maw na ka shyntur kata ka pukri, ïa ka ban ai um ïa kita ki langbrot, bad ynda kumta, ki la ïabuh biang pat ïa uta u maw ha la ka jaka ha ka shyntur kata ka pukri.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u Jakob u la ong ha ki, “Ko ki para, phi kiba na-ei?” Ki te ki la ïathuh, “Ngi long na Haran.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u la kylli ha ki, “Phi ithuh ïa u Laban u khun u Nahor?” Ki te ki la ïathuh, “Ngi ithuh keiñ ïa u.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la kylli ha ki, “U koit?” Ki ruh ki la ïathuh, “U koit: bad ha khmih, ka Rakhel ka khun jong u ka wan bad kita ki langbrot.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la ong pat, “Ha khmih, ka dang don bun ka sngi, lymne ym pat biang ka por ïa ka ban pynïalang ïa ki jingri: to phin ai um ïa ki langbrot, bad to phin khie leit ap ïa ki.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ki te ki la ong, “Ngim lah, tad ynda la pynïalang ïa ki kynhun langbrot baroh, bad ba ki la ïa-pyntyllun ïa uta u maw na ka shyntur ka pukri; ynda kumta, ngin sa ai um ïa kita ki langbrot.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Katba u dang kren bad ki, ka Rakhel ruh ka la wan bad ki langbrot u kpa jong ka: naba ka la ju sharai ïa ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba u Jakob u la ïohi ïa ka Rakhel ka khun u Laban u hynmen ka kmie jong u, bad ïa ki langbrot u Laban u hynmen ka kmie jong u, ba u Jakob u la shur hajan, bad u la pyntyllun noh ïa uta u maw na ka shyntur ka pukri, bad u la ai um ruh de ïa ka kynhun langbrot jong u Laban u hynmen ka kmie jong u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Jakob u la doh ïa ka Rakhel, bad u la kyang bad u la ïam de.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Jakob u la ïathuh ha ka Rakhel ba u long u para u kpa jong ka, bad ba u long u khun ka Rebekka: ka te ka la phet soit ïa ka ban ïathuh ha la u kpa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba u Laban u la bna shaphang u Jakob u khun ka para jong u, ba u la phet soit ban tan ïa u, bad u la kdup ïa u, bad u la doh ïa u, bad u la ïalam ïa u sha la ïing. Bad u Jakob u la ïathuhkhana ha u Laban ïa kine kiei kiei baroh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Laban u la ong ha u, “Shisha me long ka shyieng bad ka doh jong nga.” Te u la shong bad u shi bnai.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Laban u la ong ha u Jakob, “Hato namar ba me long u para jong nga, namar kata, ka dei ba men shakri ïa nga khlem da ïoh bainong ei ei? To ïathuh ha nga, kaei kan long ka bainong jong me?”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u Laban u la don ar ngut ki khun kynthei: ka kyrteng kaba kham san ka la long “ka Leah” bad ka kyrteng kaba hadien “ka Rakhel”.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ka Leah ka la long ka bapang jawaid khmat; hynrei, ka Rakhel ka la long kaba ibhabriew, bad kaba itynnad.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Jakob u la ieit eh ïa ka Rakhel, bad u la ong, “Ngan shakri ïa me hynñiew snem na ka bynta ka Rakhel ka khun bakhatduh jong me.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Laban u la ïathuh, “Ka kham bha ban ai ïa ka ha me, ban ïa kaba ngan da ai ïa ka ha uwei pat u briew: to shong sah bad nga.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumta, u Jakob u la shakri na ka bynta ka Rakhel hynñiew snem; hynrei, ki la imat ha u tang kum kiba khyndiat sngi namar ka jingieit eh jong u ïa ka keiñ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Jakob u la ong ha u Laban, “To ai ha nga ïa ka tnga jong nga, naba la dep ki sngi jong nga, ba ngan ïoh leit sha ka.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Laban u la ïalum ïa ki rangbah baroh jong kata ka jaka, bad u la thaw ïa ka jingkhawai.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, ka la jia ynda miet ba u la shim ïa ka Leah ka khun jong u bad u la wallam ïa ka sha u; te u la leit bsut sha ka.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Laban u la ai ha ka ïa ka Silpah ka shakri jong u ban long ka shakri ka Leah ka khun jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, ka la jia, ba la step, ha khmih, ka la long ka Leah: u te u la kylli ha u Laban, “Hato kaei kane ba me la leh ïa nga? Ngam shym la shakri ïa me na ka bynta ka Rakhel mo? Te balei ba me la leh phon ïa nga?”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Laban u la ïathuh, “Kam bit keiñ ban leh kumta ha ka ri jong nga, ban ai ïa kaba kham poh mynshuwa ïa ka hynmen.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> To pyndep noh ïa ka shi taïew jong kane ka Leah, bad ngin ïa-ai ha me ïa kane ruh, namar kata ka jingshakri ïa kaba men shakri biang bad nga sa hynñiew snem kiwei pat.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u Jakob u la leh kumta, bad u la pyndep noh ïa ka shi taïew jong ka: bad u Laban u la ai ha u ïa ka Rakhel ka khun jong u ïa ka ban long ka tnga jong u ruh.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U Laban ruh u la ai ïa ka Bilhah ka shakri jong u ha ka Rakhel ïa ka ban long ka shakri jong ka hi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u la leit bsut ruh sha ka Rakhel, bad u la ieit ruh ïa ka Rakhel kham tam ïa ka Leah, te u la shong shakri bad u sa hynñiew snem kiwei pat.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te U Trai ynda u la ïohi ba la isih ïa ka Leah, u la plie ïa ka kpoh jong ka: hynrei, ka Rakhel ka la long kaba lyngki.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ka Leah ka la punkhun bad ka la kha ïa u khun, bad ka la khot kyrteng “u Reuben” ïa u: naba ka la ong, “Shisha U Trai u la khmih ïa ka jingsngewshitom jong nga; namar kata, mynta u tnga jong nga un ieit ïa nga.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad ka la punkhun biang pat, bad ka la kha ïa u khun, bad ka la ong, “Naba U Trai u la ïohsngew ba la isih ïa nga, namar kata, u la ai pat ïa une ruh;” te ka la khot kyrteng “u Simeon” ïa u.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad ka la punkhun pat, bad ka la kha ïa u khun, bad ka la ong, “Mynta shisha u tnga jong nga un da ïasoh ieit ha nga, naba nga la kha ïa lai ngut ki khun shynrang ïa u:” namar kata, ka la khot kyrteng “u Lebi” ïa u.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ka la punkhun pat sa shi sien, bad ka la kha ïa u khun, bad ka la ong, “Mynta shi sien ngan ïaroh ïa U Trai”: namar kata, ka la khot kyrteng “u Judah” ïa u; bad ka la sangeh teng na ka ban kha khun."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ka Rakhel haba ka la ïohi ba kam kha khun ïa u Jakob, ka la bishni ïa la ka hynmen; ka la ong ruh ha u Jakob, “To ai khun ïa nga, ba ïoh ngan ïap noh.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Jakob u la khih bitar lep pyrshah ïa ka Rakhel bad u la kylli, “Nga shong ha ka jaka U Blei mo, uba la khang noh na pha ïa u soh ka kpoh?”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ka te ka la ong, “Ha khmih ka Bilhah ka shakri jong nga, to khie leit bsut sha ka; ba kan ïoh kha ma ka halor ki khohsiew jong nga, bad ïa nga ruh yn sa kha khun na ka.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kumta, ka la ai ïa ka Bilhah ka shakri jong ka ha u kum ka tnga; te u Jakob u la leit bsut sha ka.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ka Bilhah ka la punkhun, bad ka la kha u khun ïa u Jakob.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ka Rakhel ka la ong, “U Blei u la bishar ïa nga, bad u la ïohsngew ruh ïa ka ktien jong nga, bad u la ai ha nga ïa u khun:” namar kata, ka la khot kyrteng “u Dan” ïa u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ka Bilhah ka shakri jong ka Rakhel ka la punkhun biang pat, bad ka la kha sa uwei pat u khun ïa u Jakob.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ka Rakhel ka la ong, “Da ki jingïaleh jong U Blei keiñ nga la ïaleh bad ka hynmen jong nga, bad nga la lah ruh:” te ka la khot kyrteng “u Naphtali” ïa u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ka Leah, ynda ka la ïohi ba ka la lah wai noh ban kha, ka la shim ïa ka Silpah ka shakri jong ka bad ka la ai ïa ka ha u Jakob kum ka tnga.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ka Silpah ka shakri jong ka Leah ka la kha u khun ïa u Jakob.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ka Leah ka la ong, “Ka kynhun kan sa wan:” kumta, ka la khot kyrteng “u Gad” ïa u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ka Silpah ka shakri jong ka Leah ka la kha ïa uwei pat u khun ïa u Jakob.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ka Leah ka la ong, “Kaba suk long ma nga naba ki kynthei kin ïakhot kaba suk ïa nga:” te ka la khot kyrteng “u Asher” ïa u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Reuben u la leit ha ki sngi ka aïom ot Kew, bad u la shem ïa ki kynja soh Mandrakore, bad u la wallam ïa ki sha ka Leah ka kmie jong u. Te ka Rakhel ka la ong ha ka Leah, “To ai ha nga, nga kyrpad ïa pha, na ki soh Mandrakore u khun jong pha.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ka Leah ka la kylli ha ka Rakhel, “Hato ka long kaba sting ba pha la knieh noh ïa u tnga jong nga? bad phan mon knieh noh ruh ïa ki soh Mandrakore u khun jong nga?” Bad ka Rakhel ka la ïathuh, “To ai namar kata ba u Jakob un ïoh thiah bad pha ha kane ka miet na ka bynta ki soh Mandrakore u khun jong pha.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba u Jakob u la wan noh na ka lyngkha la janmiet, ka Leah ka la leit shaw ïa u, bad ka la ong, “To men wan bsut sha nga mynta; naba shisha keiñ nga la shim wai ïa me da ki soh Mandrakore u khun jong nga.” Kumta, u la ïoh thiah bad ka ha kata ka miet.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad U Blei u la shahshkor ïa ka Leah, bad ka la punkhun, bad ka la kha ïa u khun u basan ïa u Jakob.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ka Leah ka la ong, “U Blei u la ai ha nga ïa ka bainong jong nga, namar ba nga la ai ïa la ka shakri ha u tnga jong nga:” kumta te, ka la khot kyrteng “u Issakhar” ïa u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ka Leah ka la punkhun biang pat, bad ka la kha ïa u khun u bahynriew ïa u Jakob.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ka Leah ka la ong, “U Blei u la ai ha nga ïa ka jingai ka babha; mynta u tnga jong nga un da shongneh bad nga, naba nga la kha hynriew ngut ki khun shynrang ïa u.” Te ka la khot kyrteng “u Sabulon” ïa u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad hadien kata, ka la kha ïa ka khun, bad ka la khot kyrteng “ka Dinah” ïa ka.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te U Blei u la kynmaw ïa ka Rakhel ruh, bad U Blei u la shahshkor ïa ka bad u la plie ïa ka kpoh jong ka.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ka la punkhun, bad ka la kha ïa u khun; te ka la ong, “U Blei u la law noh ïa ka jinglongbeiñ jong nga:”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad ka la khot kyrteng “u Joseph” ïa u; namar ka la ong, “U Trai un ai shuh ha nga sa uwei pat u khun.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ynda ka Rakhel ka la kha ïa u Joseph, ba u Jakob u la ong ha u Laban, “To phah noh ïa nga, khnang ba ngan ïoh leit sha la ka jaka, bad sha la ka ri.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> To ai noh ha nga ïa ki tnga jong nga bad ïa ki khun jong nga, kiba nga la shakri ïa me na ka bynta jong ki, bad to pyllait noh ïa nga: naba me tip hi ïa ka jingshakri jong nga ïa kaba nga la shakri ïa me.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u Laban u la ong ha u, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, lada nga la shem ïa ka jingsbun ha khmat jong me, to wat leit noh: namar nga la shem ba U Trai u la kyrkhu ïa nga na ka bynta jong me.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u la ong ruh, “To buh biang ha nga ïa ka bainong jong me, nga te ngan ai ïa ka ha me.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U te u la ong ha u Laban, “Me tip hi kumno nga la shakri ïa me, bad kumno ki jingri jong me ki la long bad nga.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Namar ka la long khyndiat kaba me don mynshuwa ba la poi ma nga, hynrei, mynta, ka la nang roi sha kaba bun byrhien eh; bad U Trai u la kyrkhu ïa me ha ki sla'jat jong nga: te mynta hato lano ngan ïoh kamai ïa la ka ïing hi?”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u Laban u la ong, “Ngan ai aïu ha me?” Bad u Jakob u la ïathuh, “Men ym ai ei ei ruh ha nga: hynrei, lada men leh ïa kane ïa nga, ngan da sumar bad ngan ri biang pat ïa ki kynhun langbrot jong me.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ngan ïaid lyngba ïa ki kynhun langbrot jong me mynta ka sngi, bad ngan pynkhlad noh nangta ïa ki bathoh bria bad ïa ki bathoh bruiñ baroh na ki langbrot, bad ïa kita kiba lam saw baroh napdeng ki khun langbrot, bad ïa ki bathoh bria bad ïa ki bathoh bruiñ napdeng ki blang: te na kum kita hi kan long keiñ ka bainong jong nga.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kumta, ka hok jong nga kan ïoh kheiñ na ka bynta jong nga ha kaba lashai lashisngi, haba kan sa wan wad ïa ka bainong ha khmat jong me: bad baroh kat ki bymlong bathoh bria bad bathoh bruiñ hapdeng ki blang, bad ki bym lam saw hapdeng ki langbrot, kata kan long ba ñiew kum kaba la tuh bad nga.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u Laban u la ong, “Ha khmih, to ai ba kan long kat kum ka ktien jong me.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ha kata ka sngi, u la pynkyrpang noh ïa ki bathoh shuid bad ïa ki bathoh pan na ki blang shynrang, bad ïa ki bathoh bruiñ bad ïa ki bathoh bria baroh na ki blang kynthei, bad baroh kat kiba don khyndiat ka balieh ha ki, bad ïa kiba lam saw baroh hapdeng ki langbrot ruh de, bad u la aiti ïa ki ban ap ha ki khun shynrang jong u.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad u la buh lai sngi lynti hapdeng ki jong ki bad ki jong u Jakob: bad u Jakob u la bsa ïa kiba dang sah na ki kynhun jong u Laban.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jakob u la shim ïa ki tnat im u dieng Libneh, bad ïa ki jong u dieng soh Khyllam bad ïa ki jong u dieng soh Ot; bad u la khoh ïa ki thoh syngkha balieh ha ki, da kaba pynpaw ïa ka met lieh ka jong kita ki tnat.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad u la buh ïa kita ki tnat dieng ïa kiba u la khoh ha khmat kita ki kynhun, ha ki nur ha ki jingseng um, ha kaba kita ki kynhun ki ïawan dih um, ba kin ïoh ïashit seng khun haba ki ïawan ban dih um.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad kita ki kynhun ki la ïashit seng khun ha khmat kita ki tnat dieng, te ki kynhun ki la kha khun da ki bathoh shuid thoh pan, bad da ki bathoh bruiñ bad ki bathoh bria.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad u Jakob u la pynkhlad noh ïa ki khun langbrot, bad u la pynphai ïa ki khmat ki kynhun u Laban shaphang kita ki bathoh syngkha, bad sha kita kiba lam saw baroh ha ki kynhun u Laban; te ïa la ki jong ki kynhun u la buh kyrpang hi bad um shym la buh ïa ki ryngkat bad ki kynhun u Laban.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ka la jia ruh, kat haba kita ki jingri kiba kham khlaiñ ki ïashit seng khun, ba u Jakob u la nang buh nang buh ïa kita ki tnat dieng ha khmat kita ki kynhun ha ki nur ki jingseng um, ba kin ïoh seng khun ha khmat kita ki tnat dieng.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Hynrei, haba ki langbrot ki long kiba tlot, um ju buh keiñ: kumta, kita kiba kham tlot ki la long ki jong u Laban, bad kita kiba kham khlaiñ ki jong u Jakob.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Kumta, uta u briew u la roi shikatdei eh, bad u la don shibun ki jingri, bad ki shakri kynthei, bad ki shakri shynrang, bad ki ut, bad ki kadda ruh de."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Jakob u la ïohsngew ïa ki ktien ki khun shynrang u Laban ba ki ïa-ong, “U Jakob u la shim noh baroh kat kaba la dei ka jong u kpa jong ngi; bad ïa kane ka burom baroh u la ïoh da kata kaba la dei ïa u kpa jong ngi.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Jakob putet u la ïohi ïa ka khmat u Laban, bad ha khmih, kam shym long sha u kum mynshuwa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Jakob, “To leit phai noh sha ka ri ki kpa jong me, bad sha la ki kur; ma nga ruh ngan long ryngkat bad me.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Jakob te u la phah khot ïa ka Rakhel bad ïa ka Leah sha lyngkha sha ki kynhun jong u,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad u la ong ha ki, “Nga ïohi ïa ka khmat u kpa jong phi ba kam long sha nga kum mynshuwa; hynrei, U Blei u kpa jong nga u la don lem bad nga.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Phi ruh phi tip ba nga la shakri ïa u kpa jong phi katba shong ka bor ha nga.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u kpa jong phi u la shukor ïa nga, bad u la pynkylla ïa ka bainong jong nga la shiphew sien; la kumta ruh, U Blei um shym la shah ïa u ban pynsniew ïa nga.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Lada u la ong kumne, ‘Ki kynja ki bathoh bria kin long ka bainong jong me;’ te kumta, kita ki kynhun baroh ki la kha da ki bathoh bria: bad lada u la ong pat kumne, ‘Ki kynja ki bathoh syngkha kin long ka bainong jong me;’ kumta te, kita ki kynhun baroh ki la kha da ki bathoh syngkha.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kumta, U Blei u la shim noh ïa ki jingri u kpa jong phi, bad u la ai ïa ki ha nga.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ka la jia ruh hamar ba ki ïashit seng khun kita ki kynhun langbrot, ba nga la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad nga la ïohi ha ka jingphohsniew, bad ha khmih, ki langbrot shynrang kiba la beh pakor ïa ki langbrot ki la long ki bathoh syngkha, ki bathoh bruiñ bad ki bathoh bria.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u angel U Blei u la ong ha nga ha ka jingphohsniew, ‘Ko Jakob,’ nga te nga la ong, ‘Ha khmih ma nga.’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U te u la ong, ‘To khmied mynta ïa la ki khmat, to khmih ruh, ki langbrot shynrang baroh kiba beh pakor ïa ki langbrot ki long ki bathoh syngkha, ki bathoh bruiñ, bad ki bathoh bria: naba nga la ïohi baroh kat kaba u Laban u la leh ïa me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ma nga, nga long U Blei jong ka Bethel ha kaba me la pynsleh ïa uta u mawbynna, mynba me la kular skhem ha nga hangta ïa ka jingkular baskhem: to khie te mynta, to da leit noh na kane ka ri bad to leit phai pat sha ka ri ki kur jong me hi.’ ”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ka Rakhel bad ka Leah ki la ïathuh bad ki da ong ha u, “Ka dang sah ka bynta lane ka jingïoh pateng ei ei ruh mo ïa ngi ha ïing u kpa jong ngi?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hato um shym la ñiew ïa ngi kum ki nongwei mo? Naba u la die noh ïa ngi bad ïa ka dor jong ngi u la bam duh khoit hi keiñ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Namar kata, ka spah baroh ïa kaba U Blei u la shim noh na u kpa jong ngi, kata ka long ka jong ngi, bad ka jong ki khun jong ngi: te mynta, ïa kaei kaei ruh baroh katba U Blei u la ong ha me to da leh keiñ.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jakob u la khie joit, bad u la pynshong ïa la ki khun shynrang bad ïa la ki tnga halor ki ut;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad u la shim noh ïa la ki jingri baroh, bad ïa la ka spah baroh ïa kaba u la ïoh ïalum, ïa ki jingri keiñ ba u la ïoh hi, ïa kiba u la lah kamai hi ha Padan-Aram ïa ka ban leit noh sha u Isaak u kpa jong u sha ka ri Kanaan.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Laban u la leit ban khap shñiuh ïa la ki langbrot: bad ka Rakhel ka la tuh ïa ki durblei ki jong u kpa jong ka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Jakob u la phet noh jar jar khlem da tip u Laban u kynja Syria, naba um shym la ïathuh ha u ba un sa phet noh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta, u la phet noh bad baroh katba u don; bad u la mih noh joit, bad u la leit sha shiliang kata ka wah, bad u la thew beit ïa la ka khmat shaphang u lum Gilead.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ki la ïathuh ha u Laban ha ka balai sngi ba u Jakob u la lah phet noh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U ruh u la shim ïa la ki para lem bad u bad u la beh nadien jong u haduh hynñiew sngi lynti bad u la lap ïa u ha u lum Gilead.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad U Blei u la wan ha u Laban u kynja Syria mynmiet ha ka jingphohsniew, bad u la ong ha u, “To sumar ba men ym kren ei ei ruh ha u Jakob ka babha ne ka basniew.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ynda kumta, u Laban u la lap ïa u Jakob. Bad u Jakob u la lah pynïeng ïa la ka ïingtrep ha uta u lum: bad u Laban u la pynïeng ruh ïa la ka jong bad ki para jong u ha u lum Gilead.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Laban u la kren ha u Jakob, “Hato me la leh aïu, haba kumne ba me la phet noh buhrieh na nga, bad me la ïalam noh ïa ki khun kynthei jong nga kumba ïa ki mraw da ka waitlam?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ka balei ba me la phet noh ha kaba rieh bad ba me la phet noh kumba leh tuh na nga; bad ba mem shym la ïathuh ha nga, ba ngan da ïoh leit on keiñ ïa me da kaba leh kmen, bad da ki jingrwai, bad da kaba tem jingtem, bad ka kanjari, bad da ka duitara?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ba mem shym la ai ba ngan ïoh ïadoh ïa la ki khun shynrang bad kynthei? Mynta te, me la leh bieit da kaba leh kumne.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ka long ha ka kti jong nga ban pynsniew ïa phi: hynrei, U Blei u kpa jong phi u la kren ha nga mynhynne mynmiet, u da ong, ‘To sumar ïa lade ba men ym kren ei ei ruh ha u Jakob ka babha ne ka basniew.’",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Mynta shisha la me la donkam ban leit wan noh naba me kynmaw eh hir hir ïa ka ïing u kpa jong me, hato balei ba me la tuh ïa ki blei jong nga?”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te u Jakob u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha u Laban, “Nga la phet rieh namar ba nga la sheptieng: naba nga la ong, ‘Ba ïoh men da knieh noh na nga ïa ki khun kynthei jong me.’",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Jar ha uba men shem ïa ki blei jong me, to ai un ïap noh keiñ: ha khmat ki para shynrang jong ngi, to men khmih thuh ïa kaei na kaba dei ka jong me ka don bad nga bad to shim sha me.” Naba u Jakob um shym tip ba ka Rakhel ka la lah tuh ïa ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u Laban u la leit bsut shapoh ka ïingtrep u Jakob, bad sha ka ïingtrep ka Leah, bad sha ki ïingtrep ki jong ki shakri kynthei baroh ar ngut; hynrei, um shem shuh ïa ki. Ynda kumta, u la wan noh na ka ïingtrep jong ka Leah bad u la leit bsut sha ka ïingtrep jong ka Rakhel.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad ka Rakhel ka la lah shim ïa kita ki bleithaw, bad ka la lah thep ruh ïa ki ha ka jin ka ut, bad ka la shong halor jong ki ruh. Bad u Laban u la wad ïa kata ka ïingtrep baroh kawei, hynrei, um shem.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ka la ong ha la u kpa, “U kynrad jong nga un ym sngewsih ba ngam sngewlah khih ha khmat jong me; naba ka la jia ha nga mynta ka rukom ki kynthei.” Kumta, u la twad, hynrei, um shym la shem keiñ ïa kita ki bleithaw.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te u Jakob u la sngewbitar, bad u la kren pynrem ïa u Laban: bad u Jakob u da ïathuh u la ong ha u Laban, “Hato kaei ka jingryngkang jong nga? Bad kaei ka pop jong nga ba me la wan beh shit eh katta nadien jong nga?",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Haba me la khyllie ïa ki jingbuh jingsat jong nga baroh, hato me la shem aïu na ki jingbuh jingsat baroh ka ïing jong me? to buh ïa kata hangne ha khmat ki hynmen hynbew jong nga bad ki jong me, ba kin ïoh bishar hapdeng jong ngi baroh ar ngut.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> La arphew snem mynta ba nga la shong bad me, ki langbrot kmie jong me bad ki blang kynthei jong me kim shym la liat khun, bad ïa ki 'lang shynrang na ka kynhun langbrot jong me ngam shym la bam keiñ.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ïa kata kaba la tar da ki mrad khlaw ngam shym la wallam ha me: nga hi nga la pynburia ïa ka; na ka kti jong nga me la pan ïa kata, la kaba la tuh mynsngi, lane kaba la tuh mynmiet.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kumne ka la jia ïa nga; mynsngi ka jingshit ryngkhiang ka la bam duh ïa nga, bad u thah mynmiet; te ka jingïohthiah jong nga ka la kynriah noh na ki khmat jong nga.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Kumne keiñ, nga la don arphew snem ha ka ïing jong me; nga la shakri ïa me haduh khatsaw snem na ka bynta ki khun kynthei jong me ar ngut, bad hynriew snem na ka bynta ki jingri jong me: bad ïa ka bainong jong nga me la pynkylla jin shiphew sien.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Lymda U Blei jong u kpa jong nga, uba U Blei jong u Abraham bad uba ka jingsheptieng burom jong u Isaak u la don lem bad nga, shisha men da la lah phah noh suda ïa nga mynta. Ïa ka jingkhuslai jong nga bad ïa ka jingleh minot ki kti jong nga U Blei u la ïohi, te u la sneng pynrem ïa me mynhynne mynmiet.”",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad u Laban u la ïathuh ha u Jakob, u la ong, “Kine ki khun kynthei ki long ki khun kynthei jong nga, bad kine ki khynnah ki long ki khynnah jong nga, bad kine ki jingri ki long ki jingri jong nga, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh katba me ïohi ki long ki jong nga keiñ: bad nga lah ban leh aïu mynta ka sngi ïa kine ki khun kynthei jong nga, lane ïa ki khun jong ki, ïa kiba ki la kha?",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Te ale mynta, to ngin ïathaw ïa ka jutang, ma nga bad ma me; bad to ai ba kan long ka sakhi hapdeng jong nga bad jong me.”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te u Jakob u la shim ïa u maw, bad u la pynïeng mawbynna ïa u.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> U Jakob u la ong ruh ha ki para shynrang jong u, “To ïalum ïa ki maw;” bad ki la ïashim ïa ki maw, bad ki da ïa-pynlong ka kynton ïa ki: bad ki la ïabam hangta de halor kata ka kynton.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Bad u Laban u la khot kyrteng ïa ka, “ka Jegar-sahadutha”: hynrei, u Jakob u la khot “ka Galeed” ïa ka.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Bad u Laban u la ong, “Kane ka kynton ka long ka jingsakhi hapdeng jong nga bad me ha kane ka sngi.” Namar kata, la khot “ka Galeed” ïa ka;",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> bad “Mispah” ruh; naba u la ong, “U Trai un da khmih thuh hapdeng jong nga bad jong me, haba ngim ïadon shuh markhmat paralok hi.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Lada men pynshitom ïa ki khun kynthei jong nga, lane lada men shim da kiwei pat ki tnga nalor ki khun kynthei jong nga, ym don mano mano ruh bad ngi ban long sakhi ïa kata; to khmih, U Blei u long u sakhi hapdeng jong nga bad jong me.”",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> U Laban u la ong ruh ha u Jakob, “Ha khmih ïa kane ka kynton, bad ha khmih ïa une u mawbynna ïa kiba nga la pynïeng hapdeng jong nga bad jong me.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Kan long ka sakhi kane ka kynton, bad un long u sakhi une u mawbynna ruh de, ba ma nga ngan ym ïaid palat ïa kane ka kynton maw sha me, bad ba ma me ruh men ym ïaid palat ïa kane ka kynton maw bad ïa une u mawbynna sha nga, ïa ka ban pynsniew keiñ.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> U Blei jong u Abraham bad U Blei jong u Nahor, U Blei jong u kpa jong ki, un bishar hapdeng jong ngi.” Bad u Jakob u la smai da ka jingsheptieng burom jong u Isaak u kpa jong u.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jakob u la pynïap doh halor uta u lum, bad u la khot ïa la ki para shynrang ïa ka ban ïabam ïa kata ka jingbam: bad kumta ki la ïabam bad ki la ïasah baroh shi miet ha uta u lum.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Bad u Laban u la khie dang step eh, bad u la doh ïa la ki khun shynrang, bad ïa la ki khun kynthei, bad u la kyrkhu ïa ki: kumta, u Laban u la leit wan noh, bad u la leit phai pat sha la ka jaka."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Jakob u la nang ïaid noh ha la ka lynti, bad ki angel U Blei ki la ïashem bad u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Jakob u la ong ynda u la ïohi ïa ki, “Kane ka long ka kynhun bah U Blei:” bad u la khot kyrteng “ka Mahanaim” ïa kata ka jaka.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Jakob u la lah phah ïa ki nonglam khubor ha shuwa jong u ha u Iso u hynmen jong u sha ka ri Seir, ka khyndew jong u Edom.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la hukum ïa ki, u da ong, “Kumne phin ong ha u Iso u kynrad jong nga: ‘Kumne u ong u Jakob u shakri u jong me, bad u Laban nga la shong nongwei noh, bad nga la sah haduh mynta:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad nga don ki masi, bad ki kadda, bad ki kynhun langbrot, bad ki blang, bad ki shakri shynrang, bad ki shakri kynthei de: bad nga la phah ïathuh ha la u kynrad khnang ïa ka ban shem ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong me.’ ”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad kita ki nonglam khubor ki la ïawan phai pat sha u Jakob, ki da ong, “Ngi la leit ha u Iso u hynmen jong me bad u wan ban tan ruh ïa me, bad sawspah ki rangbah lem bad u.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jakob u la sheptieng shikatdei eh bad u la sngewjynjar: bad u la pynbynta ïa kita ki briew kiba la don lem bad u, bad ïa ki kynhun langbrot, bad ïa ki masi, bad ïa ki ut, ha ki ar kynhun;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad u la ong, “Lada u Iso un wan ïakynduh ïa kawei ka kynhun, bad u da shoh ïa ka, te kata kawei pat ka kynhun kan ïohlait im.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Jakob u la ong, “A Blei u Abraham u kpa jong nga, bad U Blei u Isaak u kpa jong nga, U Trai uba la ong ha nga, ‘To leit phai pat sha la ka ri, bad sha la ki kur, bad ngan leh bha ïa me;’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ngam shym don ka jingdawa ïa iba khyndiat tam eh ruh na kita ki jingleh isynei jong me baroh, lymne na kata ka jingleh shisha baroh ba me la leh ha la u shakri; naba tang bad la u diengduh nga la wan sha shiliang kane ka Jordan; bad mynta nga la wan long ar kynhun.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> To pyllait im ïa nga mynta, nga kyrpad ïa me, na ka kti u hynmen jong nga, na ka kti u Iso: naba nga sheptieng ïa u, ba ïoh un wan bad shoh ïap ïa nga, ïa ka kmie ruh lem bad ki khun.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, me la ong, ‘Shisha ngan leh bha ïa me, bad ngan pynlong ïa u symbai jong me kum u shyiap ka duriaw, ïa uba ym lah ñiew shuh na ka jingbun bah jong u.’ ”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad hangta u la sah ha kata ka miet; bad u la shim na kata kaba la don ha ka kti jong u ïa ka ban ai ka jingai ha u Iso u hynmen jong u;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ïa ki blang kynthei, arspah, bad ïa ki blang shynrang, arphew, ïa ki langbrot kmie, arspah, bad ïa ki langbrot shynrang, arphew,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ïa ki ut ba ai buiñ bad ki khun, laiphew, ïa ki masi kynthei, sawphew, bad ïa ki masi kyrtong, shiphew, ïa ki kadda kynthei, arphew, bad ki khun, shiphew.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la aiti ïa ki ha ka kti ki shakri jong u, ha la ka shi kynhun shi kynhun kyrpang kyrpang; bad u la ong ha la ki shakri, “To ïaid sha shiliang ha shuwa jong nga, bad to buh katto katne ka jingjngai hapdeng ki kynhun kawei pa kawei.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u la hukum ïa uba ha shuwa eh, u da ong, “Haba u Iso u hynmen jong nga u ïashem bad me, bad haba u da kylli ïa me, da kaba ong, ‘Me dei u jongno? Bad shaei men leit? Bad ki jongno kine kiba ha shuwa jong me?’",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, men sa ïathuh, ‘Ki long ki jong u Jakob u shakri jong me; kane ka long ka jingai burom ba la phah ha u Iso u kynrad jong nga: bad ha khmih, u ruh u don hadien jong ngi.’ ”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kumjuh ruh u la bthah ïa u ba-ar bad ïa u balai bad ïa kita baroh kiba la bud ïa kita ki kynhun, u da ong, “Kum ha kane ka rukom keiñ, phin kren ha u Iso, haba phi ïashem bad u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Phin ong ruh putet, ‘Ha khmih, u Jakob u shakri jong me u don hadien jong ngi.’ ” Naba u la ong, “Ngan pynïasuk ïa u da kata ka jingai burom kaba leit sha shuwa jong nga; bad hadien kata, ngan da khmih ïa ka khmat jong u; lehse u ruh un pdiang sngewbha ïa ka khmat jong nga.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta, kata ka jingai burom u Jakob ka la leit sha shiliang ha shuwa jong u: ma u hi te u la sah ha kata ka miet ha la ka jingïalang briew la ka jong.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u la khie joit ha kata ka miet, bad u la shim ïa la ki tnga baroh ar ngut, bad ïa la ki shakri kynthei ar ngut, bad ïa la ki khun shynrang khatwei ngut ruh de, bad u la nang ïaid noh sha shiliang ka khriang i wah duid Jabbok.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la ïalam ïa ki, bad u la pynphah ïa ki sha shiliang ita i wah duid; kumta, u la phah sha shiliang ïa kiei kiei kat kiba u la don.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ïa u Jakob la iehnoh marwei; bad uwei u briew u la ïaleh bad u haduh ban da shai byrngut.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ynda u la ïohi ba um lah jop ïa u Jakob, u la ktah ïa u tlong mat shyieng ka skhep jong u; kumta la kheiñ khylliah u tlong ka mat shyieng ka skhep ka jong u Jakob da kaba u ïaleh bad u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad uta u la ong, “To pyllait noh ïa nga, naba kan sa shai byrngut.” Hynrei, u la ïathuh, “Ngan ym pyllait ïa me lymda me da kyrkhu keiñ ïa nga.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U ruh u la ong ha u Jakob, “Kaei ka kyrteng jong me?” Bad u Jakob u la ïathuh, “U Jakob.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U Angel pat u la ong, “Yn ym khot shuh ïa ka kyrteng jong me, ‘u Jakob’, hynrei ‘u Israel’: naba kum u syiem me la ïoh bor bad U Blei bad ki briew, te me la jop ruh.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u Jakob u la kylli ïa u, bad u la ong, “To ïathuh, nga kyrpad ïa me, ïa ka kyrteng jong me.” U te u la ong, “Balei ba me kylli ïa kane shaphang ka kyrteng jong nga?” Bad hangta hi u la kyrkhu ïa u.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Jakob u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “ ‘ka Peniel’: naba nga la ïohi ïa U Blei markhmat, bad ïa ka mynsiem jong nga la pyllait im putet.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te katta, ka sngi ka la lah mih halor jong u mynba u dang ïaid lait noh ïa ka Peniel, bad u la dkoh na ka skhep jong u.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Namar kata, ki khun Israel kim ju bam ïa u thied heh ba la lait ran, uba ha u tlong ka skhep, haduh kane ka sngi: naba u la ktah ïa u tlong mat shyieng ka skhep u Jakob ha uta u thied heh ba la ran."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Jakob u la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad u la khmih, ha khmih ruh, u Iso u wan bad sawspah ki rangbah lem bad u. Te u Jakob u la sam ïa ki khun ha la ki jong ki jong ha ka Leah, bad ha ka Rakhel, bad ha kita ki shakri kynthei ar ngut.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la buh ïa kita ki shakri kynthei bad la ki khun sha shuwa eh, bad ïa ka Leah bad la ki khun hadien, bad ïa ka Rakhel bad ïa u Joseph ha khatduh eh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Jakob u la nang ïaid sha shuwa jong ki, bad u la nguh dem haduh ka khyndew hynñiew sien, tad ynda u la poi hajan ïa la u hynmen.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Iso u la phet ban ïashem bad u, bad u la kdup ïa u bad u la noh ha ka ryndang jong u bad u la doh ïa u de: ki la ïam ruh de.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad u la ïohi ïa ki kynthei bad ïa ki khynnah, bad u la kylli, “Kiei kine ba me don?” Bad u Jakob u la ïathuh, “Ki long ki khun ïa kiba U Blei na ka jingsbun jong u, u la ai ha u shakri jong me.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te kita ki shakri kynthei ki la ïapoi hajan; ma ki bad ki khun jong ki, ki ruh ki la ïanguh de.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ka Leah ruh ka la poi hajan bad la ki khun, bad ki la ïanguh ngon de: hadien kata, la poi hajan sa u Joseph bad ka Rakhel, ki ruh ki la ïanguh ngon.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u la kylli, “Ïa ka ban lei kane ka kynhun bah jong me baroh ïa kaba nga la ïashem?” Bad u Jakob u la ïathuh, “Ïa ka ban ïoh ïa ka jingmonbha keiñ ha khmat u kynrad jong nga.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Iso u la ong, “Nga don kynrei ko hep; to long sha me kaba dei ka jong me.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Jakob u la ong, “Em, nga kyrpad ïa me, lada shisha nga la shem ïa ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong me mynta, to pdiang te ïa ka jingai sngewbha jong nga na ka kti jong nga: naba na kaba nga ïohi ïa ka khmat jong me, ka long kumba nga la ïohi ïa ka khmat U Blei hi, haba me la sngewbha bad nga.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> To pdiang, nga kyrpad ïa me, ïa ka jingkyrkhu jong nga, ïa kaba la wallam ha me; naba U Blei u la leh sbun ïa nga, bad namar ba nga don ïa kiei kiei baroh.” Kumta, u la kyrpad eh ïa u, u te u la pdiang ïa ka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u la ong, “Ïa ngin ïaleit, to ngin ïa nang ïaid noh, ma nga ruh ngan leit ha shuwa jong me.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Jakob u la ong, “U kynrad jong nga u tip ba kine ki khun ki dang jem met bad ba ki kynhun bad ki jingri kiba dang ai buiñ ki don bad nga: te lada ñiah pynthait eh ïa ki tang shi sngi ruh, kin ïap noh baroh ki kynhun.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> To ai ba u kynrad jong nga, nga kyrpad ïa me, un nang ïaid sha shuwa u shakri jong u: ma nga ruh ngan wan suki, ryngkat bad ka jingïaid ki jingri kiba ha shuwa jong nga, bad ryngkat bad ka jong ki khun ruh, ha ban da ngan poi sha u kynrad jong nga ha Seir.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Iso u la ong, “To shah ba ngan iehnoh bad me ïa kiba na kine ki briew kiba don bad nga.” Te u Jakob u la ïathuh, “Yn lei kata? to shah ba ngan shem ïa ka jingsngewbha ha khmat u kynrad jong nga.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, u Iso u la kylla dien ha kata ka sngi ha la ka lynti sha Seir.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Jakob u la nang ïaid sha Sukkoth, bad u la thaw ka ïing ïa lade, bad u la thaw sem ïa la ki jingri: namar kata, u la khot “ka Sukkoth” ïa kata ka jaka.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Jakob u la poi suk bha sha ka nongbah Shekhem kaba ha ka ri Kanaan mynba u la wan na Padan-Aram; bad u la pynïeng ïa la ka ïingtrep ha khmat kata ka nongbah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u la thied ka bynta na kata ka khyndew ha kaba u la pyiar ïa la ka ïingjaiñ, na ka kti ki khun shynrang u Hamor, u kpa u Shekhem ha ka dor shispah ki sbai kesitah.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u la pynïeng ïa ka duwan hangta, bad u la khot kyrteng ïa ka, “ka El-Elohe-Israel.”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ka Dinah ka khun ka Leah, ïa kaba ka la kha ïa u Jakob, ka la leit shabar ïa ka ban khmih ïa ki khun kynthei jong kata ka ri.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad haba u Shekhem u khun u Hamor u kynja Hib, u syiem jong kata ka ri, u la ïohi ïa ka, u la shim ïa ka bad u la thiah lem bad ka, bad u la pynkheiñ burom ïa ka.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ka mynsiem jong u ka la ïasoh ha ka Dinah ka khun u Jakob, bad u la ieit ïa kata ka samla, bad u la kren pynsngewbha ha ka dohnud jong kata ka samla.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Shekhem u la ong ha u Hamor u kpa jong u, u da ong, “To pynïoh ka tnga ïa nga ïa kane ka samla.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Jakob u la ïohsngew ba u Shekhem u la lah pynkheiñ burom ïa ka Dinah ka khun jong u: te ki khun jong u ki la don ha ka lyngkha bad ki jingri jong u: bad u Jakob, namar kata, u la shu sngap haduh ba kin da la wan hi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Hamor u kpa u Shekhem u la leit shabar ha u Jakob ban ïakren bad u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Jakob ki la ïawan noh na kata ka lyngkha ynda ki la ïohsngew ïa kata: bad kita ki rangbah ki la ïasngewsih, bad ki la ïasngewbitar eh naba u Shekhem u la leh ïa kaba bieit sniew pyrshah ïa u Israel da kaba u ïoh thiah bad ka khun u Jakob; ïa kaba ym shym dei ban leh keiñ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Hamor u la kren bad ki, u da ong, “Ka mynsiem u Shekhem u khun jong nga ka ïasoh ieit eh ha ka khun jong phi: to ai noh mynta ïa ka ha u, nga kyrpad ïa phi, ban long ka tnga jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad to ngin ai shongkurim ma phi bad ma ngi, ïa ki khun kynthei jong phi to ai ha ngi, bad ïa ki khun kynthei jong ngi to shim sha phi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Phi ruh phin ïoh shong sah bad ngi, bad ka khyndew baroh kan long ha khmat jong phi; to da ïashong sah ha ka bad to da ïakhaïi ha ka bad to da shim ïa la ki bynta trai ha ka.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Shekhem ruh u la ong ha u kpa jong ka bad ha ki hynmen hynbew jong ka, “To shah ba ngan shem ïa ka jingmonbha ha khmat jong phi, bad katba phin ong ha nga ngan ai keiñ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> To buh ïa ka dor jingmynrain ka bakhraw katno katno ruh na ka bynta jong ka, bad to pan ïa ka jingai ruh, ma nga ruh ngan ai kat kumba phin ong ha nga: hynrei, to phin ai ïa kata ka samla ban long ka tnga jong nga.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, kita ki khun shynrang u Jakob ki la ïaphai ktien ha u Shekhem bad ha u Hamor u kpa jong u da ka buit sian phon, bad ki la ïa-ong, naba u la pynkheiñ burom ïa ka Dinah ka para jong ki,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad ki la ïathuh ha ki, “Ngim lah ban leh ïa kane, ban ai ïa la ka para ha u briew u bym shym la otsher ïa u; naba kata kan long kaba kheiñ burom ïa ngi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, tang ha kane, ngin ïakohnguh ïa phi: lada phin long kum ma ngi, ba la otsher ïa u shynrang baroh na phi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, ngin ai noh ïa la ki khun kynthei ha phi, ngi ruh ngin shim ïa ki khun kynthei jong phi sha ngi, bad ngin ïashongneh ryngkat bad phi, bad ngin ïalong uwei u paidbah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, lada phim shahshkor ïa ngi, ban shah otsher ïa phi; te ngi ruh ngin shim noh ïa la ka khun, bad ngin ïaleit noh.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki ktien jong ki, ki la pynsngewbha ïa u Hamor, bad ïa u Shekhem u khun u Hamor.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad uta u samla um shym la pynslem ban leh ïa kata, naba u la ibha eh ïa ka khun u Jakob: bad u la long ma u keiñ uba kham donburom tam ban ïa ka ïing u kpa jong u baroh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, u Hamor bad u Shekhem u khun jong u, ki la ïaleit sha ka khyrdop ka nongbah jong ki, bad ki la ïakren bad ki briew ka nongbah jong ki, ki da ong,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Kine ki briew ki ïasuk bad ngi; namar kata, to ai ba kin ïashong sah ha ka khyndew bad ba kin ïoh ïakhaïi ha ka ruh; namar ha khmih ruh, ka ri ka kylluid biang ïa ki de; ïa ki khun kynthei jong ki ngin shim sha ngi ban long ki tnga jong ngi, bad ïa ki khun kynthei jong ngi ruh ngin ïa-ai noh ha ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, tang ha kane, kine ki briew kin ïakohnguh ïa ngi ban shongneh ryngkat bad ngi ïa ka ban ïalong uwei u paidlang, lada u shynrang baroh hapdeng jong ngi un long ba la otsher ïa u, kumba ki long ma ki ba la otsher ïa ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, ki jingri jong ki bad ka spah jong ki bad ki mrad jong ki baroh kin ym long ki jong ngi mo? Tang ba ngin ïakohnguh ïa ki, ma ki ruh kin ïashong duh ryngkat bad ngi.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ïa u Hamor bad ïa u Shekhem u khun jong u kat kiba la wan mih noh na ka khyrdop ka nongbah jong u, ki la ïashahshkor baroh; bad ïa u shynrang baroh la otsher, ïa baroh keiñ kat kiba la wan mih noh na kata ka khyrdop ka nongbah jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha ka balai sngi, haba ki dang ïasat syllang eh, ba ar ngut na ki khun shynrang u Jakob: u Simeon bad u Lebi, ki hynmen jong ka Dinah, ki la ïashim ïa la ka waitlam mar kawei, bad ki la ïawan hiar kynsan halor kata ka nongbah, bad ki la ïa-pynïap noh ruh ïa ki shynrang baroh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad ïa u Hamor bad ïa u Shekhem u khun jong u ki la pynïap noh da ka banep ka waitlam, bad ki la shim noh ïa ka Dinah na ka ïing u Shekhem bad hadien kata ki la ïaleit wan noh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kita ki khun shynrang u Jakob ki la ïawan hiar ha kita ïa kiba la shoh ïap, bad ki la ïalute ïa kata ka nongbah, namar ba ki la lah pynkheiñ burom ïa ka para jong ki.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ïa ki langbrot jong ki bad ïa ki masi jong ki, bad ïa ki kadda jong ki, bad ïa kaei kaei ruh katba la don hapoh kata ka nongbah, bad ïa kaei kaei ruh katba la don ha ka lyngkha, ki la ïashim noh,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad ïa ka spah jong ki baroh, bad ïa ki khun khynnah jong ki baroh, bad ïa ki tnga jong ki, ki la ïalam mraw, bad ki la ïalute ïa baroh keiñ katba la don ha ki ïing.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jakob u la ong ha u Simeon bad ha u Lebi, “Phi la pynshitom ïa nga da kaba phi la pynlong ïa nga uba ijli hapdeng ki trai-shnong jong kane ka ri, hapdeng ki kynja Kanaan bad ki kynja Peris keiñ: bad haba nga ruh nga long uba khyndiat briew, kin ïalang lem ban ïaleh ïa nga, bad kin pynïap noh ïa nga; kumta ïa nga yn sa pynjot noh; ma nga bad ka ïing jong nga.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ki te ki la ïathuh, “Hato ka la dei ïa u ban leh ïa ka para jong ngi kum ïa ka nuti?”"
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, U Blei u la ong ha u Jakob, “To mih noh, to leit kiew sha Bethel, bad to shong sah hangta: bad to da thaw ïa ka duwan hangta ïa uta U Blei uba la paw ha me mynba me dang phet ïap na khmat u Iso u hynmen jong me.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jakob u la ong ha la ka ïing, bad ha kita baroh kat kiba don bad u, “To buh noh ïa kita ki blei bakhyllah kiba don hapdeng jong phi bad to pynkhuid ïa lade, bad to pli ïa la ki jaiñ;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad to ïa ngin ïamih noh, bad ngin ïaleit kiew sha Bethel; ba hangta ngan thaw ïa ka duwan ïa uta U Blei uba la shahshkor ïa nga ha ka sngi ka jingsngewjynjar jong nga, bad uba la long ryngkat bad nga ha kata ka lynti baroh ha kaba nga la ïaid.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïa-ai noh ha u Jakob ïa kita ki blei bakhyllah baroh katba ki la don ha la ka kti, bad ïa la ki sohshkor kiba la don ha ki shkor jong ki; bad u Jakob u la tep rieh ïa ki hapoh u dieng Sning uba hajan ka Shekhem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki la ïa nang leit noh: bad ka jingsheptieng ïa U Blei ka la ngat ha kita ki nongbah kiba la don baroh sawdong ïa ki, katba kim shym la ïabeh nadien ki khun shynrang u Jakob.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, u Jakob u la poi ha ka Lus, kaba ha ka ri Kanaan, kata kaba long ka Bethel, ma u bad kita ki briew baroh kat kiba la don bad u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la tei ïa ka duwan hangta, bad u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “ka El-Bethel”: namar ba hangta U Blei u la paw ha u, mynba u la phet ïap na khmat u hynmen jong u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, ka Deborah ka aïa jong ka Rebekka ka la ïap noh, bad la tep ïa ka ruh harum ka Bethel hapoh uwei u dieng Sning: te la khot kyrteng ïa ka, “ka Allon-bakhuth”.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad U Blei u la paw pat sa shi sien ha u Jakob, haba u la wan noh na Padan-Aram bad u la kyrkhu ïa u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad U Blei u la ong ha u, “Ka kyrteng jong me ka long ‘u Jakob’: te yn ym khot kyrteng shuh ‘u Jakob’ ïa me, hynrei, ‘u Israel’ kan long ka kyrteng jong me”: kumta, u la khot kyrteng ïa u, “u Israel”.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Blei u la ong ruh ha u, “Nga long U Blei U Badonbor Baroh: to da nang kharoi, bad to da nang man bun ruh; ka jaid bynriew bad ka jingïalang ki jaid bynriew kin ïamih noh na me bad ki syiem ruh kin mih na ki syngkai jong me.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ka ri ïa kaba nga la ai ha u Abraham bad ha u Isaak, ha me keiñ ngan ai ïa ka, bad ha u symbai jong me hadien jong me ngan ai ïa kata ka ri.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad U Blei u la leit kiew noh na u na kata ka jaka hi ha kaba U la lah ïakren bad u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Jakob u la pynïeng ïa u mot pynkynmaw ha kata ka jaka ha kaba u la lah ïakren bad U, da u mawbynna keiñ: bad u la theh halor jong u ïa ka jingainguh dih, bad u la theh ïa ka umphniang ruh halor jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Jakob u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka ha kaba U Blei u la lah ïakren bad u, “ka Bethel”.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïaleit noh na Bethel; bad la don tang kumba shikyntien kwai lynti ban ïaid haduh Ephrath: bad ka Rakhel ka la suhkhun bad ka jingsuh khun jong ka, ka la long kaba jur eh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba ka dang suhkhun eh ba ka nongbat khun ka la ong ha ka, “To wat sheptieng; naba ine ruh i long i khun shynrang ïa pha.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ka la jia, hamar ba kan sa jah noh ka mynsiem jong ka, (naba ka la ïap noh keiñ,) ba ka la jer kyrteng “u Ben-oni” ïa u: hynrei, u kpa jong u, u la jer kyrteng “u Benjamin” ïa u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ka Rakhel ka la ïap noh, bad la tep ïa ka ha ka lynti sha Ephrath, kaba long ka Bethlehem.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Jakob u la pynïeng ïa u mawbynna halor ka jingtep jong ka: bad uta u long u mawbynna ka jingtep ka Rakhel haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Israel u la nang ïaid noh, bad u la pyiar ïa la ka ïingjaiñ sha lyndet ka kut Edar.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ka la jia ruh, mynba u Israel u dang shong sah ha kata ka ri, ba u Reuben u la leit thiah bad ka Bilhah, ka tnga ba kham poh ka jong u kpa jong u: bad u Israel u la ïohsngew ïa kata. Te u Jakob u la don khat-ar ngut ki khun shynrang:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ki khun shynrang jong ka Leah: u Reuben, u khun nyngkong u Jakob, bad u Simeon, bad u Lebi, bad u Judah, bad u Issakhar, bad u Sabulon.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ki khun shynrang ki jong ka Rakhel: u Joseph, bad u Benjamin.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang ki jong ka Bilhah, ka shakri ka Rakhel: u Dan, bad u Naphtali.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang ki jong ka Silpah, ka shakri ka Leah: u Gad, bad u Asher. Kine ki long ki khun shynrang ki jong u Jakob, ïa kiba la kha ïa u ha Padan-Aram.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u Jakob u la poi ha u Isaak u kpa jong u sha Mamre, sha ka nongbah Arbah, kaba long ka Hebron, ha kaba u Abraham bad u Isaak ki la ïashong sohshnong.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ki sngi ka rta ki jong u Isaak ki la long shispah bad phraphew snem.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u Isaak u la ai noh ïa la ka mynsiem bad u la ïap noh, bad la lum ïa u sha la ki briew, uba la tymmen bad uba la dap ki sngi jong u: bad ki khun shynrang jong u, u Iso bad u Jakob ki la ïatep ïa u."
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad kine ki long ki jinghiar pateng jong u Iso, u kynja Edom.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Iso u la shim ïa la ki tnga na ki khun kynthei ki kynja Kanaan: ka Adah ka khun u Elon u kynja Hit, bad ka Aholibamah ka khun ka Anah ka khun u Sibeon u kynja Hib,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ka Bashemath ka khun u Ishmael, ka para u Nebaioth.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ka Adah ka la kha ïa u Eliphas ha u Iso; bad ka Bashemath ka la kha ïa u Reuel;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ka Aholibamah ka la kha ïa u Jeush, bad ïa u Jaalam, bad ïa u Korah: kine ki long ki khun shynrang ki jong u Iso, ïa kiba la kha ha u ha ka ri Kanaan.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Iso u la shim ïa la ki tnga, bad ïa la ki khun, ki kynthei bad ki shynrang, bad ïa ki mynsiem baroh kiba la dei ïa ka ïing jong u, bad ïa la ki jingri, bad ïa la ki mrad baroh, bad ïa la ka spah baroh, ïa kaba u la ïoh ha ka ri Kanaan; bad u la leit noh sha ka ri kaba kyrpang na khmat u Jakob u para jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Naba ka spah jong ki ka la bun katta katba kim lah shuh ban ïashong ryngkat; bad kata ka ri ha kaba ki la ïalong sohshnong kam lah bsa ïa ki baroh namar ki jingri jong ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, u Iso u la shong duh ha u lum Seir: u Iso u long u Edom.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad kine ki long ki jinghiar pateng ki jong u Iso u kpa ki kynja Edom ha u lum Seir.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kine ki long ki kyrteng ki khun shynrang u Iso: u Eliphas u khun ka Adah ka tnga u Iso, u Reuel u khun ka Bashemath ka tnga u Iso.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Eliphas ki la long: u Teman, u Omar, u Sepho, bad u Gatam, bad u Kenas.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ka Timna ka la long ka tnga ba kham poh ka jong u Eliphas u khun u Iso; bad ka la kha ïa u Amalek ha u Eliphas: kine ki la long ki khun shynrang ka Adah ka tnga u Iso.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Reuel: u Nahath, bad u Serah, u Shammah, bad u Missah; kine ki la long ki khun shynrang ki jong ka Bashemath ka tnga u Iso.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad kine ki la long ki khun shynrang ka Aholibamah, ka khun ka Anah ka khun u Sibeon, ka tnga u Iso: bad ka la kha ha u Iso ïa u Jeush, bad ïa u Jaalam, bad ïa u Korah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kine ki long ki syiem jong ki khun shynrang u Iso: kiba ki khun shynrang u Eliphas, u khun banyngkong u Iso: u Teman syiem, u Omar syiem, u Sepho syiem, u Kenas syiem.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U Korah syiem, u Gatam syiem, u Amalek syiem: kine ki long ki syiem kiba la mih na u Eliphas ha ka ri Edom: bad kine ki long ki khun shynrang ka Adah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Reuel u khun u Iso: u Nahath syiem, u Serah syiem, u Shammah syiem, u Missah syiem: kine ki long ki syiem na u Reuel ha ka ri Edom; kine ki long ki khun shynrang ka Bashemath ka tnga u Iso.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad kine ki long ki khun shynrang ka Aholibamah ka tnga u Iso: u Jeush syiem, u Jaalam syiem, u Korah syiem: kine ki long ki syiem kiba la mih na ka Aholibamah kaba ka khun ka Anah ka tnga u Iso.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Iso, uba long u Edom, bad kine ki long ki syiem jong ki.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Seir u kynja Hor, kiba la ju shong sah ha kata ka ri: u Lotan, bad u Shobal, bad u Sibeon, bad u Anah,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad u Dishon, bad u Eser, bad u Dishan: kine ki long ki syiem jong ki kynja Hor, kiba ki khun shynrang u Seir ha ka ri Edom.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Lotan ki la long: u Hori bad u Hemam; bad ka para u Lotan ka la long ka Timna.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Shobal: u Alban, bad u Manahath, bad u Ebal, bad u Shepho, bad u Onam.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Sibeon: u Aïah bad u Anah: une u long uta u Anah uba la shem ïa kita ki pukri um mihpohliew bashit, mynba u pynbam phlang ïa ki kadda jong u Sibeon u kpa jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad kine ki long ki khun u Anah: u Dishon, bad ka Aholibamah, ka khun u Anah.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Dishon: u Hemdan, bad u Eshban, bad u Ithran, bad u Kheran.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad kine ki long ki khun shynrang u Eser: u Bilhan, bad u Saaban, bad u Akan.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kine ki long ki khun u Dishan: u Us, bad u Aran.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kine ki long ki syiem kiba la mih na ki kynja Hor: u Lotan syiem, u Shobal syiem, u Sibeon syiem, bad u Anah syiem,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> u Dishon syiem, u Eser syiem, u Dishan syiem: kine ki long ki syiem kiba la mih na ki kynja Hor; kumba shong ka jinglong syiem jong ki ha ka ri Seir.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad kine ki long kita ki syiem kiba la synshar ha ka ri Edom, mynshuwa ba la synshar da u syiem halor ki khun Israel.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u Bela u khun u Beor u la synshar ha ka ri Edom: bad ka kyrteng ka nongbah jong u ka la long “ka Dinhabah”.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u Bela u la ïap, bad u Jobab u khun u Serah na Bosrah, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u Jobab u la ïap, bad u Husham na ka ri ki kynja Teman, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad u Husham u la ïap, bad ha ka jaka jong u, u la synshar u Hadad, u khun u Bedad, uba la shoh ïa u Midian ha ka lyngkha u Moab; bad ka kyrteng ka nongbah jong u ka la long “ka Abith”.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad u Hadad u la ïap, bad u Samlah na Masrekah u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad u Samlah u la ïap, bad ha ka jaka jong u la synshar u Saul uba na Rehoboth kaba harud ka wah.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad u Saul u la ïap, bad u Baal-hanan u khun u Akhbor u la synshar ïa ka jaka jong u.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad u Baal-hanan u khun u Akhbor u la ïap, bad u Hadar u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u: bad ka kyrteng ka nongbah jong u ka la long “ka Pau”; bad ka kyrteng ka tnga jong u ka la long “ka Mehetabel”, ka khun ka Matred, bad ka khun u Mesahab.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kumta, kine ki long ki kyrteng ki syiem kiba la mih na u Iso, ha la ka ïing ka ïing, ha la ka jaka jaka, da la ki kyrteng hi: u Timna syiem, u Albah syiem, u Jetheth syiem,",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> u Aholibamah syiem, u Elah syiem, u Pinon syiem,",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> u Kenas syiem, u Teman syiem, u Mibsar syiem,",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> u Magdiel syiem, u Iram syiem: kine ki long ki syiem ka ri Edom, kumba ki ïashong sah ha la ka shnong ka shnong, ha la ka ri la ka jong ka jong: une u long u Iso u kpa ki kynja Edom."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hynrei, u Jakob u la shong sah ha ka ri ha kaba la shong sohshnong u kpa jong u, ha ka ri Kanaan keiñ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kane ka long ka jingïathuhkhana shaphang u Jakob. U Joseph, haba u la khathynñiew snem ka rta, u la ju ap ïa ki kynhun lem bad ki hynmen jong u; bad uta u khynnah u la don bad ki khun shynrang ka Bilhah, lem ruh bad ki khun shynrang ka Silpah, ki tnga u kpa jong u: bad u Joseph u la wan ïalap ïa ka ktien bymbha shaphang jong ki ha u kpa jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Israel u la ieit ïa u Joseph nalor ki khun shynrang jong u baroh, naba u long u khun ka jinglong tymmen jong u: te u la thaw ïa ka sopti bathoh broin ïa u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad haba ki hynmen jong u ki la ïohi ba u kpa jong ki u la ieit ïa u nalor ki hynmen jong u baroh, ki la ïashun ïa u, bad kim lah kren suk sngewbha shuh ïa u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Joseph u la phohsniew ïa ka jingphohsniew, bad u la ïathuh ïa ka ha la ki hynmen: te ki la nang kham isih ïa u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “To sngew mynta, nga kyrpad ïa phi, ïa kane ka jingphohsniew ïa kaba nga la phohsniew;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> namar, ha khmih, ngi dang ïateh song ïa ki thup kba ha ka lyngkha, bad ha khmih, ka song jong nga ka la khie joit bad ka la ïeng beit ruh; bad ha khmih, ki song jong phi ki da ïeng lyngwiar bad ki da ïanguh ruh ïa ka song jong nga.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, ki hynmen jong u ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Shisha men synshar halor jong ngi? ne me shisha men ïoh long trai halor jong ngi?” Bad ki la nang kham isih shuh ïa u namar kita ki jingphohsniew jong u, bad namar ki ktien jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u la phohsniew pat sa kawei ka jingphohsniew, bad u la ïathuh ïa ka ha la ki hynmen, u la ong ruh, “Ha khmih, nga la phohsniew sa kawei pat ka jingphohsniew; bad ha khmih, ka sngi bad u bnai bad khatwei ki khlur ki la ïanguh ïa nga.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u la ïathuh ïa ka ha la u kpa, bad ha la ki hynmen: bad u kpa jong u, u la sneng pyrshah ïa u, bad u la ong ha u, “Hato kaei kane ka jingphohsniew ïa kaba me la phohsniew? Ma nga bad ka kmie jong me, bad ki hynmen jong me, shisha ngin ïawan ban ïanguh ngon ma ngi ha khmat jong me haduh khyndew?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki hynmen jong u ki la ïabishni ïa u; hynrei, u kpa jong u, u la kynshew ïa kata ka jingong ha la ka dohnud.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ki hynmen jong u ki la ïaleit ban ïasharai ïa ki kynhun u kpa jong ki ha Shekhem.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Israel u la ong ha u Joseph, “Ki hynmen jong me kim ïasharai ïa ki kynhun ha Shekhem? To ale, bad ngan phah ïa me sha ki.” U ruh u la ong, “To, ha khmih ma nga.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la ong ha u, “To khie leit, nga kyrpad ïa me, to khmih la ka suk bha ne em bad ki hynmen jong me, bad ka bha bad ki kynhun; bad to wallam ktien pat ïa nga.” Kumta, u la phah ïa u na ka pynthor Hebron, bad u la leit poi haduh Shekhem.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te, ha khmih, uwei u briew u la ïakynduh bad u haba u dang ïaid sakma ha ka lyngkha: bad uta u briew u la kylli ïa u, u da ong, “Me wad aïu?”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la ïathuh, “Nga wad ïa ki hynmen jong nga keiñ: to ïathuh ïa nga, nga kyrpad ïa me, ha-ei ki ïasharai?”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad uta u briew u la ïathuh, “Ki la kynriah noh nangne; naba nga la ïohsngew ba ki ïa-ong, ‘To ngin ïaleit sha Dothan.’ ” Ynda kumta, u Joseph u sa leit beh ïa la ki hynmen, bad u la shem ïa ki ha Dothan.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki la ïohi ïa u na jngai; te haba um pat poi hajan jong ki, ki la ïasylla lem ban pynïap noh ïa u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki la ïa-ong paralok hi, “Ha khmih u wan une u trai ki jingphohsniew.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> To ïa mynta, namar kata ngin ïa-pynïap noh ïa u, bad ngin ïabred ïa u ha kawei ka thliew um bad ngin ïathuh, uwei u mrad u basniew u la bam duh ïa u: ynda kumta, ngin ïakhmih yn long aïu na ki jingphohsniew jong u.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Reuben u la ïohsngew bad u la pyllait noh ïa u na ki kti jong ki; u la ong ruh artad, “Wat ai ba ngin pynïap ïa u.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Reuben u la ong pat ha ki, “Wat theh ïa ka snam, to pynhiar ïa u sha kane ka thliew um kaba ha khlaw, hynrei, wat buh ïa ka kti ha u;” ïa kane u la ong ba un ïoh pyllait ïa u na ki kti jong ki, ban ïalam pat ïa u sha la u kpa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba u Joseph u la wan poi sha la ki hynmen, ba ki la law noh ïa ka sopti jong u na u Joseph, ïa kata ka sopti bathoh broin keiñ ïa kaba u phong;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad ki la ïashim ïa u, bad ki la ïa-pynhiar ïa u sha ka thliew um: hynrei, kata ka thliew um ka la rngad noh, bad ym don um ha ka.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki la ïashong ha khyndew ban bam jingbam: bad ki la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad ki la ïakhmih ruh, te ha khmih, shi kynhun ki kynja Ishmael ki ïawan na Gilead bad ki ut jong ki, kiba kit ïa ki kynja masla bad ïa ka umphniang baiwbih bakordor bad ïa ka mirr, bad ki leit kit ïa ki, shathie sha ka ri Ijipt.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Judah u la ong ha la ki para, “Kan myntoi aïu lada ngin pynïap ïa la u para, bad buhrieh ïa ka snam jong u?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ale, ïa ngin ïadie noh ïa u ha kine ki kynja Ishmael bad wat ai ba ka kti jong ngi kan long ha u; naba u long u para jong ngi na ka doh jong ngi.” Bad ki para jong u ki la ïa-pynshahshkor.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, haba kita ki nongkhaïi ki kynja Midian ki la ïaid lait ïa ki, ki la khring, bad ki la kyntiew ïa u Joseph na kata ka thliew um, bad ki la die noh ïa u Joseph ha kita ki kynja Ishmael, arphew ki sbai rupa: bad ki ruh ki la wallam ïa u Joseph sha ka ri Ijipt.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Reuben u la wan kylla pat sha kata ka thliew um; bad ha khmih, u Joseph um don ha kata ka thliew um; te u la kad ïa la ki jaiñkup.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u la wan phai sha la ki para, bad u la ong, “Uta u khynnah um don; ma nga te shaei ngan leit?”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad ki la shim ïa ka sopti u Joseph, bad ki la pynïap ïa iwei i khun blang bad ki la wieh ïa kata ka sopti ha kata ka snam;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> bad ki la phah ïa kata ka sopti bathoh broin, bad ki la leit lam ïa ka sha la u kpa; ki la ong ruh, “Ïa kane ngi la shem: to da khmih thuh mynta la ka long ne em ka sopti u khun jong me.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u la ithuh ïa ka, bad u la ong, “Ka long keiñ ka sopti u khun jong nga; u mrad u basniew u la bam duh ïa u; shisha la tar ïa u Joseph.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u Jakob u la kad ïa la ki jaiñkup, bad u la buh da ka jaiñ khain ha la ka syngkai, bad u la ïam leh sngewsih ïa la u khun bun sngi.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ynda kumta, ki khun jong u baroh ki shynrang bad ki kynthei ki la ïamih ïa ka ban pyntngen ïa u; hynrei, um shah ba kin pyntngen ïa u; bad u la ong, “Naba shisha ngan leit hiar sha la u khun da kaba ïambriew haduh ka jingtep.” Kumta, u kpa jong u, u la ïam na ka bynta jong u.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad kita ki kynja Midian ki la ïadie ïa u ha ka ri Ijipt, ha u Potiphar, u nongkam u Pharaoh, bad u nongsumar barangbah ka ïing jong u."
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha kata ka aïom, ba u Judah u la leit hiar na la ki parakha, bad u la phai sha uwei u kynja Adullam, uba kyrteng “u Hirah”.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad hangta u Judah u la ïohi ïa ka khun uwei u kynja Kanaan, uba kyrteng “u Shua”; bad u la shim ïa ka, bad u la leit sha ka.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ka la punkhun, bad ka la kha ïa u khun; bad u la khot kyrteng “u Er” ïa u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ka la punkhun biang, bad ka la kha ïa u khun; bad u la khot kyrteng “u Onan” ïa u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ka la punkhun, bad ka la kha ïa u khun pat sa shi sien; bad u la khot kyrteng “u Shelah” ïa u: te u la don ha Khesib mynba ka la kha ïa une.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Judah u la shim ka tnga ïa u Er u khun nyngkong jong u, bad ka kyrteng jong ka, ka la long “ka Tamar”.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Er, u khun nyngkong u Judah, u la long u basniew eh ha khmat U Trai; te U Trai u la pynïap noh ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Judah u la ong ha u Onan, “To khie leit sha ka tnga u hynmen jong me, bad to bia ïa ka, bad to pynmih symbai ïa la u hynmen.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Onan u la tip ba u symbai un ym long ïa u hi kumta haba u la leit sha ka tnga u hynmen jong u, u la ju pynjah duh ïa la u symbai ha tbian, ba ïoh un pynmih symbai ïa la u hynmen.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad kata ïa kaba u la leh ka la long ka basniew eh ha khmat U Trai: bad namar kata, U la pynïap noh ïa u ruh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Judah u la ong ha ka Tamar ka pyrsa kurim jong u, “To sah riewkynthei noh ha ïing u kpa jong pha, haduh ba un da la san u Shelah u khun jong nga:” naba u la ong, “ba ïoh u ruh un ïap noh kum ki hynmen jong u.” Kumta ka Tamar ka la leit bad ka la shong sah ha ïing u kpa jong ka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ynda la bun sngi ka la ïap noh ka khun u Shua, ka tnga u Judah; bad u Judah u la pyntngen ïa lade, bad u la leit kiew sha Timnath, sha ki nongkhap shñiuh ki langbrot jong u: ma u bad u Hirah u kynja Adullam u lok jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ïa ka Tamar ruh la bna, da kaba ong, “Ha khmih, u kthaw kurim jong pha u leit kiew sha Timnath ban khap shñiuh ïa ki langbrot jong u.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ka te ka la law noh na lade ïa ki jaiñkup riewkynthei jong ka, bad ka la tap ïa lade da ka jingkah khmat, bad ka la pynkup ïa lade, bad ka la shong ha ka khyrdop ka Enaim, kaba ha ka lynti sha Timnath; naba ka la ïohi ba u Shelah u la san, bad ba ym shym la ai ïa ka ban long ka tnga jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Judah u la ïohi ïa ka, bad u la tharai ba ka long ka nuti; naba ka la kah ïa la ka khmat.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la phai sha ka ha kata ka lynti, bad u la ong, “Ale, to shah ba ngan wan sha pha;” (naba um tip ba ka long ka pyrsa kurim jong u hi.) Ka ruh ka la ong, “Men ai aïu ha nga, ba men ïoh wan ha nga?”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U te u la ong, “Ngan phah ha pha da i khun blang iwei na ka kynhun.” Te ka la ong, “Men ai da ka synjat ha nga ha ban da men phah ïa ita?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U te u la ong, “Ka synjat aïu ngan ai ha pha?” Ka ruh ka la ïathuh, “Ïa i 'sah shab jong me, bad ïa ka rumar jong me, bad ïa u diengduh jong me ba me don ha la ka kti.” Bad u la ai ïa ki ha ka, bad u la leit sha ka, bad ka la punkhun na u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ka la khie joit, bad ka la leit noh, bad ka la law noh na lade ïa la ka jingkah, bad ka la kup biang ïa ki jaiñkup riewkynthei jong ka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Judah u la phah lam ïa ita i khun blang da ka kti u lok jong u, uta u kynja Adullam, ba un ïoh shim pat ïa la ka synjat na ka kti jong kata ka briew: hynrei, um shem ïa ka.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u la kylli ïa ki briew jong kata ka jaka, u da ong, “Shaei kata ka nuti kaba la don ha Enaim harud lynti?” Bad ki la ïathuh, “Ym shym don nuti shane.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumta, u la leit phai pat sha u Judah, bad u la ong, “Ngam shem ïa ka; bad kita ki briew jong kata ka jaka ruh ki la ïa-ong, ‘Ym don nuti hangne.’ ”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u Judah u la ong, “To ai kan shim hi ha lade ïa kita, ba ïoh ngin shem ïa ka jinglehrain: ha khmih, nga la phah lam ïa ine i khun blang bad mem shym la shem ïa ka pynban.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ka la jia ruh ynda la lai bnai, ba la ïathuh ha u Judah, da kaba ong, “Ka Tamar ka pyrsa kurim jong me ka la kam nuti; bad ha khmih, ka la punkhun ruh da kaba klim.” Ynda kumta, u Judah u la ong, “To pynmih noh ïa ka, bad to ai ba yn thang noh ïa ka.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Haba la pynmih noh ïa ka, ka la phah sha la u kthaw kurim, ka da ong, “Na uta u briew uba long u trai kine kiei kiei ruh, nga la punkhun keiñ:” bad ka la ong, “To khmih thuh mynta ki jongno kine: ka 'sah shab, bad ka rumar, bad u diengduh.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Judah u la phla ïa ki kum la ka jong, bad u la ong, “Ka kham hok ma ka ban ïa nga; namar ngam shym la ai ïa ka ha u Shelah u khun jong nga.” Bad um shym la ithuh shuh ïa ka.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ka la jia ruh haba ka la suhkhun, ba ha khmih, la don ar ngut ha ka kpoh jong ka.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba ka dang kha, ba uwei u la pynmih ïa la ka kti: bad ka nongbat khun ka la shim da u ksai basaw bad ka la teh ïa u ha ka kti jong u, ka da ong, “Une u la mih noh shuwa.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Hynrei, ka la jia, ynda u la ring pat shapoh ïa la ka kti, ba ha khmih, u para jong u, u la mih noh: bad ka la ong, “Kumno ba me la pynlong ïa kane ka jingpra da ka bor? To ai ba kane ka jingpra kan long halor jong me:” namar kata, la khot kyrteng “u Phares” ïa u.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hadien kata ruh, la mih noh sa u para jong u, uba la don u ksai basaw ha la ka kti: bad la khot kyrteng “u Serah” ïa u."
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kumta, la ïalam arsut ïa u Joseph sha ka ri Ijipt; u nongkam u Pharaoh, bad u nongsumar barangbah ka ïing jong u, u la thied ïa u na ki kti ki kynja Ishmael, kiba la ïalam arsut shata ïa u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad U Trai u la don ryngkat bad u Joseph, bad u la long u briew ba man bha eh; bad u la shong ha ïing uta u kynja Ijipt u kynrad jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u kynrad jong u, u la ïohi ba U Trai u la don ryngkat bad u, bad U Trai u la pynman bha ïa kiei kiei baroh ha ki kti jong u ïa kiba u la leh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Joseph u la shem ïa ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong u, bad u la nang shakri ïa u: bad u la buh ïa u halor ka ïing jong u, bad u la aiti ïa kiei kiei baroh katba u la don hapoh ka kti jong u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ka la jia ruh naduh ka por ba u la buh ïa u halor la ka ïing, bad halor kiei kiei baroh katba u la don, ba U Trai u la kyrkhu ïa ka ïing jong uta u kynja Ijipt na ka bynta u Joseph; bad ka jingkyrkhu U Trai ka la long halor kiei kiei baroh katba u don ha ka ïing, bad ha ka lyngkha.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u la iehnoh ïa kiei kiei baroh katba u la don hapoh ka kti u Joseph; bad um shym la tip shaphang kaei kaei ruh ba u la don, hynrei, tang ïa ka jingbam ïa kaba u la ju bam. U Joseph u la long ruh uba ibhabriew eh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ka la jia hadien kine kiei kiei ruh, ba ka tnga u kynrad jong u ka la shat ïa la ki khmat ha u Joseph; bad ka la ong, “To thiah lem bad nga.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, u la kyrngah, bad u la ong ruh ha ka tnga u kynrad jong u, “Ha khmih, u kynrad jong nga um tip shaphang kaei kaei ruh kaba don bad nga ha ïing, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh u la buh ha ka kti jong nga;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> uba kham halor ïa nga ha kane ka ïing ym don; bad um shym la khang ei ei ruh na nga, hynrei, tang ïa pha keiñ, naba pha long ka tnga jong u: kumno te nga lah ban leh ïa kane kaba bymman eh, bad ban leh pop pyrshah ïa U Blei?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ka la jia ruh, ba katba ka dem kren ha u Joseph ha la ka sngi, um pynshahshkor satia ïa ka ban thiah lem bad ka, lane ban long lem bad ka.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka la jia ruh, hamar kata ka por, ba u la leit sha ïing ban kam ïa la ka jingkam ïing; bad ym shym la don mano mano ruh em ha ïing na ki briew jong kata ka ïing.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ka la kem bat ïa u na ka jaiñkup jong u, ka da ong, “To thiah lem bad nga:” u te u la iehnoh ïa la ka jaiñkup ha ka kti jong ka, bad u la phet noh soit, bad u la mih noh sha khyndew.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ka la jia ruh, ynda ka la ïohi ba u la iehnoh ïa la ka jaiñkup ha ka kti jong ka, bad ba u la phet noh soit na ïing,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ba ka la khot ïa ki rangbah ka ïing jong ka, bad ka la ïathuh ha ki, ka da ong, “To khmih, u la wallam hapoh ïa u kynja Hebru ha ngi ïa ka ban pynjahburom ïa ngi; u la wan bsut sha nga ïa ka ban thiah lem bad nga, nga te nga la kyang jam:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ka la jia ruh, ynda u la ïohsngew ba nga la kyang jam bad ba nga la pyrta jam, ba u la iehnoh ïa la ka jaiñkup ha nga, bad u la phet soit, bad u la mih noh na ïing.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ka la buh ïa ka jaiñkup jong u ha lade, ha ban da la wan u kynrad jong u sha la ïing.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ka la kren ha u kum da kine ki ktien, ka da ong, “Uta u shakri uba kynja Hebru ïa uba me la wallam sha ngi, u la wan bsut sha nga ïa ka ban pynkheiñ burom ïa nga:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ka la jia ruh, katba nga la kyang eh bad ba nga la pyrta jam, ba u la iehnoh ïa la ka jaiñkup bad nga, bad u la phet noh na ïing.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ka la jia ruh, haba u kynrad jong u, u la ïohsngew ïa kine ki ktien ka tnga jong u ïa kiba ka la kren ha u, ba ka da ong, “Kum ha kane ka rukom u shakri jong me u la leh ïa nga;” ba ka jingbitar jong u ka la meh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u kynrad u Joseph u la shim ïa u, bad u la buh ïa u ha ka ïing byndi, ka jaka ha kaba la khum ïa ki nongsah byndi jong u syiem; kumta, u la don hangta ha kata ka ïing byndi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, U Trai u la don ryngkat bad u Joseph, bad u la pyni ïa ka jingisynei ïa u, bad u la ai ha u ka jingmonbha ha khmat u nongap ïing byndi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te uta u nongap ka ïing byndi u la buh ha ka kti u Joseph ïa ki nongsah byndi baroh, katba la don ha kata ka ïing byndi; bad ïa kaei kaei ruh ba ki la leh hangta, u la long ma u keiñ uba la leh ïa kata.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U nongap ïa ka ïing byndi um shym khmih ïa kaei kaei ruh em kaba u la don ha ka kti jong u; naba U Trai u la don ryngkat bad u, te kaei kaei ruh ïa kaba u la leh, U Trai u la pynman bha ïa ka."
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ka la jia hadien kine kiei kiei ruh, ba u rangbah ki nongrah khuri jong u syiem ka ri Ijipt bad u rangbah ki nongshet kpu ki la leh pop pyrshah ïa u kynrad jong ki u syiem ka ri Ijipt.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la bitar eh ïa ki nongkam jong u baroh ar ngut, ïa u rangbah ki nongrah khuri, bad ïa u rangbah ki nongshet kpu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la set byndi ïa ki ha ka ïing u rangbah ki nongphasi, ha kata ka ïing byndi, ha kaba la sah byndi u Joseph ruh de.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad uta u rangbah ki nongphasi u la buh ïa u Joseph u nongsumar bad ki, bad ïa ka ban shakri ïa ki: bad ki la ïashong byndi katto katne sngi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki la phohsniew ïa ka jingphohsniew baroh ar ngut, ïa la ka jong ka jong ka jingphohsniew ha kajuh ka miet, uwei uwei ruh kat kumba shong ka jingpynsngewthuh ïa ka jingmut ka jingphohsniew jong u hi, u nongrah khuri bad u nongshet kpu jong u syiem ka ri Ijipt keiñ, ïa kiba la khum ha ka ïing byndi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Joseph u la leit bsut sha ki mynstep, u la khmih ruh ïa ki, bad ha khmih, ki la sngewsih.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la kylli ïa ki nongkam jong u Pharaoh kiba la don bad u ha ka byndi ka ïing u kynrad jong u, u da ong, “Balei ba ki khmat jong phi ki i 'matsngewsih mynta?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki la ïathuh ha u, “Ngi la phohsniew ïa ka jingphohsniew, hynrei, ym don u ban batai ïa ka.” Bad u Joseph u la ong ha ki, “Ki jingbatai kim dei ki jong U Blei mo? To ïathuh ha nga ïa ki mynta, nga kyrpad ïa phi.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad uta u rangbah ki nongrah khuri u la ïathuh ïa la ka jingphohsniew ha u Joseph, bad u la ong ha u, “Nga la long ha ka jingphohsniew jong nga, bad ha khmih, u dieng soh Waiñ ha khmat jong nga,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ha uta u dieng soh Waiñ la don lai ki tnat: bad u i kumba dang kan shylluit, u dang lah phuh syntiew; bad ki rynjup soh jong u ki la sei da ki soh Waiñ ba la ih:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad ka khuri jong u Pharaoh ka la don ha ka kti jong nga: bad nga la shim ïa ki soh Waiñ, bad nga la khem ïa ki ha ka khuri jong u Pharaoh, bad nga la ai ïa ka khuri ha ka kti u Pharaoh.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ong ha u, “Kane ka long ka jingbatai jong ka: Kita ki lai tnat ki long lai sngi;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> sa lai sngi u Pharaoh un kyntiew ïa ka khlieh jong me, bad un pynshong biang ïa me ha la ka kam bad men ïoh ai ïa ka khuri jong u Pharaoh ha ka kti jong u, ha ka rukom kum kaba mynno mynno ruh mynba me la long u nongrah khuri jong u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, to kynmaw me ïa nga ynda ka la bha bad me, bad to leh sbun ïa nga, nga kyrpad ïa me, bad to pynkynmaw ïa nga ha u Pharaoh, bad to ïalam noh ïa nga na kane ka ïing:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> naba shisha la tuh ïa nga kum ka jingtuh na ka ri ki kynja Hebru: bad shane pat ngam shym leh ei ei ruh em ba kin set noh ïa nga hapoh kane ka ïing byndi.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Uta u rangbah ki nongshet kpu ynda u la ïohi ba kata ka jingbatai ka la long ka babha, u la ong ha u Joseph, “Nga la long ma nga ruh kumjuh ha la ka jingphohsniew, bad ha khmih, lai tylli ki kriah kpu halor ka khlieh jong nga,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad ha ka kriah kaba kham hajrong la don na ki jaid jingbam baroh ïa u Pharaoh kiba dei jong ka kam u nongshet kpu; bad ki sim ki la bam na kata ka kriah kaba halor ka khlieh jong nga.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Kane ka long ka jingbatai jong ka: Kita lai tylli ki kriah kpu ki long lai sngi;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> te sa lai sngi u Pharaoh un kyntiew ïa ka khlieh jong me nalor jong me, bad un sdien ïa me halor u dieng; bad ki sim kin bam ïa ka doh jong me na me.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ha ka balai sngi ka la jia lyngkhuh ka sngi kha jong u Pharaoh, bad u la thaw ïa ka jingkhawai ïa la ki shakri baroh: bad u la kyntiew ïa ka khlieh ka jong u rangbah ki nongrah khuri, bad ïa ka jong u rangbah ki nongshet kpu hapdeng ki shakri jong u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u la khot pat ïa uta u rangbah ki nongrah khuri sha ka kam rah khuri jong u; u ruh u la ai ïa ka khuri ha ka kti u Pharaoh:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> hynrei, ïa uta u rangbah ki nongshet kpu u la sdien: kumba u Joseph u la lah batai ïa ki keiñ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, uta u rangbah ki nongrah khuri um shym la kynmaw ïa u Joseph, hynrei, u la klet noh ïa u."
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia te ynda la dap ar snem, ba u Pharaoh u la phohsniew: bad ha khmih, u da ïeng harud ka wah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ha khmih, la mih na kata ka wah hynñiew ki masi kynthei kiba ibha bad basngaid; bad ki la bam phlang ha ka 'dew'lang ni.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ha khmih, hynñiew kiwei pat ki masi kynthei ki la ïawan kiew hadien jong ki na kata ka wah, kiba isih ban khmih bad ki baraikhoh; bad ki la ïaïeng hajan ïa kita kiwei ki masi harud kata ka wah.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad kita ki masi kynthei kiba isih bad ki baraikhoh ki la bam ïa kita ki masi kynthei kiba ibha bad basngaid. Ynda kumta, u Pharaoh u la kyndit thiah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la thiah biang bad u la phohsniew pat sa shi wat: bad ha khmih, hynñiew tylli ki rynjup soh Kew ki mih na uwei u jyntang, kiba la met bad ki babha.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ha khmih, sa hynñiew tylli ki rynjup soh Kew ki baswai bad kiba la thangïong da ka lyer mihngi, kiba mih shluiñ hadien jong ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad kita ki rynjup soh Kew ki baswai ki la nguid noh ïa kita ki hynñiew tylli ki soh Kew kiba la met bad ki babha. Te u Pharaoh u la kyndit thiah, bad ha khmih, ka la long ka jingphohsniew.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te mynstep ka la jia ba ka mynsiem jong u ka la khih khuslai; bad u la phah khot ïa ki kynja nongkren byrtong baroh ka ri Ijipt, bad ïa ki riewstad baroh jong ka: bad u Pharaoh u la ïathuh ha ki la ki jingphohsniew; hynrei, ym don ba lah ban batai ïa ki ha u Pharaoh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, uta u rangbah ki nongrah khuri u la kren ha u Pharaoh, u da ong, “Mynta shisha nga kynmaw ïa la ki jingleh duna.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Pharaoh u la bitar ïa la ki shakri bad u la set ïa nga ha ka ïing byndi, ha ïing u rangbah ki nongphasi, ïa nga keiñ bad ïa u rangbah ki nongshet kpu,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ngi la ïaphohsniew ïa ka jingphohsniew ruh ha kajuh ka miet: ma nga bad ma u; ngi la ïaphohsniew uwei uwei ruh kat kumba shong ka jingbatai la ka jong ka jong ka jingphohsniew.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te la don hangta ryngkat bad ngi u samla, u kynja Hebru, u shakri jong u rangbah ki nongphasi; bad ngi la ïathuh ha u, u ruh u la batai ïa ngi ïa ki jingphohsniew jong ngi; ïa uwei uwei ruh kat kumba la long la ka jingphohsniew u la batai ma u keiñ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ba kumba u la batai ïa ngi, kumta hi ka la long; ïa nga la kyntiew pat sha la ka kam, bad ïa uta uwei la sdien.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Pharaoh, namar kata, u la phah khot ïa u Joseph, ki te ki la ïaphet ban wallam ïa u na kata ka ïing byndi; bad u ruh u la khi ïa lade, bad u la pli ïa la ki jaiñkup bad u la wan sha u Pharaoh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la ong ha u Joseph, “Nga la phohsniew ïa ka jingphohsniew, bad ym don ba lah ban batai ïa ka; te nga la bna shaphang jong me, ba me lah ban sngap ïa ka jingphohsniew ïa ka ban batai ïa ka.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ïathuh ha u Pharaoh, “Ym ma nga: hynrei, U Blei un ai jubab shaphang ka jingsuk jong u Pharaoh.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Pharaoh u la ong ha u Joseph, “Ha khmih, ha ka jingphohsniew jong nga, nga la ïeng harud kata ka wah:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ha khmih, ki ïamih na kata ka wah hynñiew ki masi kynthei, ki basngaid, bad ba-ibha; bad ha ka 'dew'lang ni ki ïabam phlang:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad ha khmih ruh, hynñiew kiwei pat ki masi kynthei ki ïawan kiew nadien jong ki, ki baswai bad ki basniew eh ban khmih bad ki baraikhoh ruh de: ki basniew kat kine ngam shym la ïohi mynno mynno ruh em ha ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te kita ki masi kynthei ki baraikhoh bad basniew, ki la bam ïa kita ki hynñiew ki masi kynthei ki basngaid kiba la kiew shuwa:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad la ki la lah nguid sha ka kpoh jong ki, ym shym lah ithuh ba ki la leit sha ka kpoh jong ki; hynrei, haba khmih ïa ki, ki la sniew kumba mynshuwa. Ynda kumta, nga la kyndit thiah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nga la ïohi ruh ha ka jingphohsniew jong nga, bad ha khmih, hynñiew tylli ki rynjup soh Kew ba la met bad babha, ki mih shluiñ ha uwei u jyntang:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad ha khmih, sa hynñiew tylli ki rynjup soh Kew ba la tyrkhong bad ki ba-iswai, bad ba la thangïong da ka lyer mihngi, ki la mih shluiñ hadien jong ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad kita ki rynjup soh Kew ki baswai ki la nguid noh ïa kita ki hynñiew tylli ki rynjup soh Kew ki babha: bad ïa kane nga la ïathuh ha ki nongkren shwar; hynrei, ym don ba lah ban batai ïa ka ha nga.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joseph u la ïathuh ha u Pharaoh, “Ka jingphohsniew u Pharaoh ka long kawei; ïa kaba U Blei un sa leh, ïa kata keiñ u la ïathuh ha u Pharaoh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kita ki hynñiew ki masi kynthei basngaid ki long hynñiew snem bad kita ki hynñiew tylli ki rynjup soh Kew ruh ki long hynñiew snem: ka jingphohsniew ka long kawei keiñ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Pat kita ki hynñiew ki masi kynthei ki baraikhoh bad basniew ruh, kiba la ïawan kiew hadien jong ki, ki long hynñiew snem; bad kita ki hynñiew tylli ki rynjup soh Kew kiba khlem met ba la thangïong da ka lyer mihngi, kin long hynñiew snem ka 'nemsniew keiñ.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Kane ka long kata ka ktien ïa kaba nga la ong ha u Pharaoh: ‘Ïa kaba U Blei un sa leh, ïa kata keiñ u la pyni ha u Pharaoh.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ha khmih, ki hynñiew snem kin wan bad kaba dap kyrhai lyngba ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, hadien jong ki, kin mih ki hynñiew snem da ka 'nemsniew; kumta, yn sa klet noh ïa kata ka jingdap kyrhai baroh lyngba ka ri Ijipt; bad kata ka 'nemsniew kan pynjot noh ïa ka ri;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad yn ym ithuh shuh ïa kata ka jingdap kyrhai ha ka ri namar kata ka 'nemsniew ban sa jia hadien; naba kan long kaba jur eh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Pat shaphang kaba pynlong ar kyntien ïa kata ka jingphohsniew ïa u Pharaoh; ka long kumta ïa ka ban pynskhem ïa kata ka jinglong da U Blei, bad namar ba U Blei un sa pynkloi ban leh ïa kata.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Mynta te, to ai ba u Pharaoh un wad da u briew u bashemphang bad u bastad, bad to ai ba un buh ïa u halor ka ri Ijipt.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> To ai ba u Pharaoh un leh ïa kane bad to ai ba un buh da ki nongkhmih halor ka ri, bad to ai ba un shim ïa kaba san bynta na ki jingmih jong ka ri Ijipt hapdeng kita ki hynñiew snem kiba dap kyrhai.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad to ai kin ïalum ïa ka jingbam baroh hapdeng kita ki hynñiew snem ki babha ki ban sa wan, bad kin kynshew ïa u Kew hapoh ka kti jong u Pharaoh, ïa ka ban sumar biang ïa ka jingbam ha ki nongbah.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kumta, kata ka jingbam kan long ka jingkynshew lypa ïa ka ri ha kita ki hynñiew snem jong ka 'nemsniew ka ban jia ha ka ri Ijipt; ba yn ym pynjot noh ïa ka ri da kata ka 'nemsniew.’ ”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad kane ka ktien ka bha ha khmat u Pharaoh, bad ha khmat ki shakri jong u baroh.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te u Pharaoh u la ong ha la ki shakri, “Ngi lah ban shem ïa u briew kat une, uba shong U Mynsiem U Blei ha u?”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> U Pharaoh u la ong ruh ha u Joseph, “Naba U Blei u la pyni ha me ïa kane baroh, ym don shuh u bashemphang bad u bastad kum ma me:",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> ma me, men long halor ka ïing jong nga, bad da ka ktien jong me yn synshar ïa ki briew jong nga baroh: hynrei, tang ha ka khet syiem ma nga ngan long uba kham khraw halor jong me.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ynda kumta, u Pharaoh u la ong ha u Joseph, “To khmih, nga la buh ïa me halor ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la law noh ïa ka sa'ti na la ka kti, bad u la buh ïa ka ha ka kti u Joseph, bad u la pynkup ïa u da ki jaiñ 'sai ryndia bani, bad u la buh ïa u kynjri ksiar ha ka ryndang jong u;",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> bad u la pynshong ïa u ha ka kali ka ba-ar ka jong u; bad ki la ïapyrta noh ha shuwa jong u, “To dem ka khohsiew”: kumta, u la buh ïa u halor ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> U Pharaoh u la ong ruh ha u Joseph, “Ma nga, u Pharaoh, bad khlem ma me ym don uwei u briew ruh ban rah ïa la ka kti lane ïa la ka sla'jat ha ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei.”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la khot kyrteng “u Saphnath-Paaneah” ïa u Joseph; bad u la ai ha u ïa ka Asenath ka khun u Potipherah, u lyngdoh ka shnong On, ban long ka tnga jong u. Ynda kumta, u Joseph u la leit noh lyngba ka ri Ijipt.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Bad u Joseph u la laiphew snem ka rta mynba u la ïeng ha khmat u Pharaoh u syiem ka ri Ijipt. Bad u Joseph u la mih noh na khmat u Pharaoh, bad u la ïaid kylleng ïa ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Bad ka khyndew ka la sei soh kyrhai eh shi kham shi kham hapdeng kita ki hynñiew snem ba-dap kyrhai.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> U te u la ïalum lang ïa ki jingbam baroh ha kita ki hynñiew snem, kiba la long ha ka ri Ijipt, bad u la buh kynshew ïa ka jingbam ha ki nongbah: ïa ka jingbam ka lyngkha keiñ, kaba long sawdong ha la ka nongbah hi, u la kynshew ha kajuh.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Kumta, u Joseph u la ïalum lang ïa u Kew shikatdei eh, kat u shyiap ka duriaw, tad ynda u la iehnoh ban ñiew; naba ym lah ñiew shuh.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Hynrei, mynshuwa ba ki la jia kita ki snem jong ka 'nemsniew la kha ïa u Joseph ar ngut ki khun shynrang, ïa kiba ka Asenath ka khun u Potipherah u lyngdoh ka shnong On ka la kha ïa u.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Bad u Joseph u la khot kyrteng “u Manasseh” ïa uba la kha nyngkong: “Naba U Blei u la pynklet ïa nga ïa ka jingleh shitom jong nga baroh, bad ïa ka ïing u kpa jong nga baroh.”",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Bad ïa u ba-ar u la khot kyrteng “ ‘u Ephraim’: “Naba U Blei u la pynman ïa nga ha ka ri ba la ban shitom ïa nga.”",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Ynda kumta, la wai noh kita ki hynñiew snem ka jingdap kyrhai, ba la long ha ka ri Ijipt.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Bad kita ki hynñiew snem jong ka 'nemsniew ki la sdang ban mih, kat kumba u Joseph u la lah ïathuh: bad kata ka 'nemsniew ka la long ha ki ri baroh; hynrei, la don ka jingbam ha ka ri Ijipt baroh.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Bad haba ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei ka la shah 'nemsniew, ki paidlang ki la ïakyang ha u Pharaoh ban ïoh kpu; bad u Pharaoh u la ong ha ki Ijipt baroh, “To khie leit sha u Joseph; to leh katba u ong ha phi.”",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Bad ka 'nemsniew ka la kem ïa kata ka ri baroh kawei: ynda kumta, u Joseph u la plie ïa kita ki ïing jingkynshew baroh, bad u la die ha ki Ijipt; naba kata ka 'nemsniew ka la jur eh ha ka ri Ijipt.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Bad ki ri baroh ki la ïawan sha ka ri Ijipt ha u Joseph ïa ka ban thied Kew; naba ka 'nemsniew ka la jur eh ha ki ri baroh."
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Jakob haba u la ïoh tip ba don u Kew ha ka ri Ijipt, u Jakob u la ong ha la ki khun shynrang, “Balei ba phi ïa-peit khmat paralok hi?”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, nga la ïohsngew ba don u Kew ha ka ri Ijipt: to khie leit hiar shata, bad to thied ïa ngi nangta; ba ngin ïoh im, bad ba ngin ym ïap noh.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kumta, ki hynmen u Joseph shiphew ngut ki la ïaleit hiar sha ka ri Ijipt ïa ka ban thied Kew.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, u Jakob um shym pyllait ïa u Benjamin, u para u Joseph, ban leit ryngkat bad la ki hynmen; namar u la ong, “Ba ïoh yn jia ka basniew ïa u.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, kita ki khun shynrang u Israel ruh ki la ïawan ban thied Kew hapdeng kita kiba la ïawan: naba la long kata ka 'nemsniew ha ka ri Kanaan ruh de.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Joseph u la long u nongsynshar halor kata ka ri, bad u la long ma u keiñ uba la die ha ki briew baroh jong kata ka ri; bad ki hynmen u Joseph ki la ïawan, bad ki la ïanguh ngon ïa u da la ki khmat haduh ka khyndew.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ïohi ïa la ki hynmen, bad u la ithuh ïa ki, hynrei, u la leh jngai ïa lade bad ki, bad u la kren eh khar khar ha ki; u la ong ruh ha ki, “Na-ei phi ïawan?” Ki ruh ki la ïathuh, “Na ka ri Kanaan ïa ka ban thied jingbam.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Joseph u da ithuh ïa la ki hynmen, hynrei, ki, kim shym la ithuh ïa u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Joseph u la kynmaw ïa la ki jingphohsniew ba u la lah phohsniew shaphang jong ki, bad u la ong ha ki, “Phi long kiba ïawan syntiat; ïa ka ban khmih na-ei ka lait jingda ka ri phi la wan.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ki te ki la ïathuh ha u, “Em, ko kynrad, hynrei, ki shakri jong me ki la ïawan ban thied jingbam.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngi baroh ngi long ki khun shynrang tang uwei u briew; ngi long ki briew kiba shisha, ki shakri jong me kim long ki nongsyntiat satia.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U te u la ong ha ki, “Em, hynrei, phi la wan ban khmih na-ei ka lait jingda ka ri.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki pat ki la ïathuh, “Ki shakri jong me ngi long khat-ar ngut shipara, ki khun shynrang tang uwei u briew ha ka ri Kanaan; bad ha khmih, u bakhatduh eh u don mynta lem bad u kpa jong ngi, bad uwei pat um don shuh.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ong ha ki, “Ka long kata keiñ ïa kaba nga la kren ha phi, ‘Phi long ki nongsyntiat.’",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Da kane yn sa tynjuh ïa phi: Katba u im u Pharaoh phin ym ïoh mih noh nangne, lymda wan shane u para bakhatduh eh jong phi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> To phah noh ïa uwei na phi ban leit shaw ïa u para jong phi, bad ïa phi yn sa khum, khnang ba yn pynshisha ïa ka ktien jong phi la ka don ne em ka jingshisha ha phi: lada ym don, katba u im u Pharaoh phi long ki nongsyntiat shisha.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u la buh ha byndi ïa ki baroh lang haduh lai sngi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ong ha ki ha ka balai sngi, “To phin leh ïa kane, ba phin ïoh im; nga tieng burom ïa U Blei.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Lada phi long ki briew kiba shisha, to ai ba ïa uwei na phi shipara yn khum ha ka ïing byndi jong phi: te ma phi to khie leit, pynkit noh da u Kew na ka bynta ka 'nemsniew ka ïing jong phi:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad ïa u para bakhatduh eh jong phi phin wallam ryngkat bad phi ha nga; kumta, yn pynshisha ïa ki ktien jong phi, phi ruh phin ym ïap.” Ki te ki la leh kumta.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki la ïa-ong paralok hi, “Shisha ngi la rem shaphang uta u para jong ngi, naba ngi la ïohi ïa ka jingjynjar ka mynsiem jong u, mynba u la kyrpad ïa ngi, te ma ngi ngim shym sngew satia ïa u; namar kata keiñ, ka la jia kane ka jingjynjar ha ngi.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Reuben u la phai ktien ïa ki, u da ong, “Nga ngam shym la ong ha phi, haba nga la kren, ‘Wat leh pop ïa une u samla;’ te phim sngap satia? Bad namar kata te, ha khmih, yn sa pan ïa ka snam jong u.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad kim shym tip ba u Joseph u la ïohsngew ïa ki; namar la don u nongbatai ktien hapdeng jong ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U te u la phai noh lyndet na ki, bad u la ïam; bad u la wan pat sa shi sien sha ki bad u la kren ha ki, bad u la shim ïa u Simeon na ki bad u la phah khum ïa u ha khmat jong ki.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joseph u la hukum ban pyndap ïa ki byrni jong ki da u Kew, bad ban buh pat ïa ki sbai jong ki uwei pa uwei ha la ka jong ka jong ka byrni, bad ban ai jingbam ïa ki ban bam ha lynti: kumta, u la leh ruh ïa ki.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki te ki la kyntiew ïa la u Kew halor ki kadda jong ki, bad ki la ïaleit noh nangta.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad uwei u la plie ïa la ka byrni ban sa ai jingbam ïa la ka kadda ha ka ïingbasa, bad u la ïohi ïa la ki sbai; namar ha khmih, ki la don ha ka shyntur ka byrni jong u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u la ong ha la ki para, “Ïa ki sbai jong nga la ai pat; bad ha khmih, ki don ruh ha ka byrni jong nga:” ynda kumta, la tyllep noh ïa ka dohnud jong ki, bad ki la ïakyiuh, ki da ïa-ong paralok hi, “Kaei kane ba U Blei u la leh ïa ngi?”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ki la ïapoi sha u Jakob u kpa jong ki sha ka ri Kanaan bad ki la ïathuhkhana ha u baroh ba la lah jia ïa ki, ki da ong,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> “Uta u briew, uba long u trai ha kata ka ri, u la kren khar khar eh ha ngi, bad u la ñiew ïa ngi kum ki nongsyntiat ïa kata ka ri.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, ngi la ong ha u, ‘Ngi long ki briew kiba shisha; ngim long satia ki nongsyntiat;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ngi la long khat-ar ngut shipara, ki khun shynrang u kpa jong ngi; uwei um don shuh, bad u bakhatduh eh u don mynta bad u kpa jong ngi ha ka ri Kanaan.’",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad uta u briew, uba long u trai ha kata ka ri, u la ong ha ngi, ‘Da kane keiñ ngan ïoh tip la phi long kiba shisha ne em; ïa uwei u para to phin iehnoh bad nga, bad na ka bynta ka 'nemsniew ki ïing jong phi to shim jingbam, bad to leit wan noh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad to wallam noh ïa u para bakhatduh eh jong phi sha nga: kumta, ngan sa ïoh tip ba phim long satia ki nongsyntiat, hynrei, ba phi long ki briew kiba shisha: ynda kumta, ngan ai noh ha phi ïa u para jong phi, bad phin ïoh khaïi ha kane ka ri.’ ”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ka la jia katba ki la ïatheh pynsuda ïa la ki byrni, ba ha khmih, ka jingsong sbai jong ki uwei pa uwei ka la don ha la ka jong ka jong ka byrni: bad ki la ïohi ïa ki jingsong sbai jong ki, ma ki bad u kpa jong ki de, bad ki la ïasheptieng.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad u Jakob u kpa jong ki u la ong ha ki, “Ïa nga phi la pynduh khun: u Joseph um don shuh, bad u Simeon u ruh um don shuh, bad ïa u Benjamin pat phin shim noh: kine kiei kiei baroh ki ïaleh pyrshah ïa nga.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ynda kumta, u Reuben u la ïathuh ha la u kpa, u da ong, “To pynïap noh ïa ki khun shynrang jong nga baroh ar ngut, lada ngam wallam biang pat ïa u sha me: to buh ïa u ha ka kti jong nga, bad ngan wallam biang ïa u pat sha me.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> U te u la ong, “Un ym ïoh leit u khun jong nga ryngkat bad phi; naba u hynmen jong u, u la ïap noh bad ïa u la pynsah marwei: lada jia ka basniew ei ei ruh ïa u ha ka lynti ha kaba phin leit, te phin pynhiar ïa ki 'ñiuhlieh jong nga sha ka jingtep da ka jingsngewsih.”"
		},
		"43": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad kata ka 'nemsniew ka la nang kham jur ha kata ka ri.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ynda ki la ïabam ïa u Kew ïa uba ki la lah wallam na ka ri Ijipt, ba u kpa jong ki u la ong ha ki, “To khie leit sa shi sien, to thied biang khyndiat ka jingbam ïa ngi.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Judah u la ïathuh ha u, u la ong, “Ïa kaba maham u la maham uta u briew ïa ngi, u da ong, ‘Phin ym ïohi shuh ïa ka khmat jong nga, lymda phi don bad la u para ryngkat bad phi.’",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Lada men phah ïa u para jong ngi ryngkat bad ngi, ngin ïaleit hiar bad ngin thied jingbam ïa me;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> hynrei, lada men ym phah ïa u, ngin ym leit hiar: naba uta u briew u la ong ha ngi, ‘Phin ym ïohi shuh ïa ka khmat jong nga, lymda phi don bad la u para ryngkat bad phi.’ ”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Israel u la ong, “Na ka balei phi la leh sniew ïa nga, da kaba ïathuh ha uta u briew ba phi dang don para shuh?”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki ruh ki la ïathuh, “Uta u briew u la kylli bniah eh shaphang jong ngi, bad shaphang ka ïing jong ngi, u da ong, ‘U dang im u kpa jong phi? Phi dang don para shuh?’ Ngi ruh ngi la ïathuh ha u kum ha kine ki ktien: shisha ngi lah ban tip ba un ong, ‘To phin wanlam arsut shane ïa u para jong phi?’ ”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Judah ruh u la ong ha u Israel u kpa jong u, “To pyllait noh ïa une u samla bad nga, ngi ruh ngin ïamih bad ngin ïaleit noh; ba ngin ïoh im, bad ba ngin ym ïap noh, ma ngi, bad ma me ruh, bad ki khun khynnah jong ngi de.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngan long ma nga u nongbahkhlieh na ka bynta jong u; na ka kti jong nga men pan ïa u: lada ngam da wallam pat ïa u sha me, bad lada ngam buh ïa u ha khmat jong me, nangta nga la kit rem, nga la pop pyrshah ïa me baroh shi rta:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> shisha lada ngim shym la pyntud kumne, shisha ngi la ïawan katta kat ar kyrwat.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, u Israel u kpa jong ki u la ïathuh ha ki, “Lada ka dei ban long kumta te, to leh ïa kane; to shim na kiei kiei ruh ki babha tam jong kane ka ri ha ki jingdiang jong phi, bad to ïaleit lam arsut sha uta u briew da ka jingai sngewbha, ïa khyndiat ka umkseh baiwbih bakordor, bad khyndiat ka ngap, ïa ki masla, bad ïa ka mirr, ïa ki kwai, bad ki soh Khyllam.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> To shim ruh ar shah da ki sbai bad phi; bad to leit lam noh pat bad phi ïa kito ki sbai ba la buh pat ha ka shyntur ki byrni jong phi; lehse kata ka la long tang ka jingklet pynban.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> To phin ïalam ruh bad u para jong phi, to da ïamih noh, bad to da ïaleit phai pat sha uta u rangbah:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad to ai ba U Blei U Badonbor Baroh un ai ka jingisynei ïa phi ha khmat uta u rangbah, bad un phah pyllait noh ha phi ïa uta uwei pat u para jong phi, bad ïa u Benjamin de. Bad ma nga, lada yn pynduh khun ïa nga to yn pynduh khun keiñ.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad kita ki briew ki la shim ïa kata ka jingai, bad ki la shim ïa ki sbai ar shah ha la ka kti, bad ïa u Benjamin de; bad ki la ïamih noh, bad ki la ïaleit hiar sha ka ri Ijipt, bad ki la ïeng ruh ha khmat u Joseph.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ïohi ïa u Benjamin lem bad ki, bad u la ong ha uba halor ka ïing jong u, “To ïalam ïa kine ki briew shapoh ïing, bad to shohdoh ruh, bad to pynkhreh ruh de; naba kine ki briew kin ïoh bam ryngkat bad nga ha kaba shiteng sngi.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad uta u briew u la leh kumba u Joseph u la bthah; bad uta u briew u la ïalam ïa kita ki briew ha ka ïing u Joseph.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te kita ki briew ki la kyiuh haba la ïalam ïa ki shapoh ka ïing u Joseph; ki la ïa-ong ruh, “Namar kita ki sbai ba la buh pat ha ki byrni jong ngi ha kata kaba shi sien wan, la ïalam ïa ngi shapoh shane; ïa ka ban ïoh ban ïa ngi, bad ïa ka ban pynhap ïa ngi, bad ïa ka ban buh mraw ïa ngi, bad ban shim ïa ki kadda jong ngi ruh de.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki la ïakham kynshur hajan ïa uta u briew uba halor ka ïing u Joseph, bad ki la ïakren bad u hajan ka jingkhang ka ïing,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad ki la ïa-ong, “A ko kynrad, shisha ngi la ïawan hiar shane mynnyngkong ïa ka ban thied jingbam:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ka la jia te, ynda ngi la ïapoi ha ka ïingbasa, bad ba ngi la ïa-plie ïa ki byrni jong ngi, ha khmih ruh, ki sbai jong uwei uwei ruh ki la don ha ka shyntur ka byrni jong u, ki sbai jong ngi kiba biang keiñ ha ka jingthew: hynrei, ngi la wallam pat ïa ki ha la ka kti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ngi la wallam arsut ruh da kiwei pat ki sbai ha la ki kti ïa ka ban thied jingbam: te ngim tip mano ba la buh ïa ki sbai jong ngi ha ki byrni jong ngi.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U te u la ong, “Ka jingsuk ïa phi, to wat sheptieng shuh: U Blei jong phi, bad U Blei u kpa jong phi, u la ai ïa ka jingkynshew ha ki byrni jong phi: ki sbai jong phi ki la wan ha nga.” Bad u la wallam shabar ïa u Simeon sha ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad uta u briew u la ïalam ïa kita ki briew shapoh ïing u Joseph, bad u la ai um ha ki, bad ki la sait ïa la ki sla'jat; bad u la ai jingbam ïa ki kadda jong ki.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ki te ki la ïa-pynkhreh ïa la ka jingai ïa ka jingwan u Joseph ha kaba shiteng sngi: naba ki la ïohsngew ba kin sa ïoh bam jingbam hangta.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te ynda la poi u Joseph sha la ïing, ki la wallam ïa la ka jingai ïa kaba ki la don ha la ka kti shapoh ïing, bad ki la ïanguh ïa u haduh ka khyndew.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u la kylli ïa ki shaphang la ka jingbha jingsuk, bad u la ong, “U koit bha u tymmen, u kpa jong phi uba phi la kren shaphang jong u? U dang im?”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ki ruh ki ïathuh, “U koit bha u shakri jong me, u kpa jong ngi, u dang im haduh mynta.” Ynda kumta, ki la ïanguh khlieh bad ki la ïadem.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U ruh u la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad u la ïohi ïa la u para, u Benjamin, u khun ka kmie jong u hi, bad u la ong, “Une u long u para bakhatduh eh jong phi, uba phi la ong shaphang jong u ha nga?” Ynda kumta, u la ong, “U Blei un isynei ïa me, ko khun.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Joseph u la leh kyrkieh eh; naba ka dohnud jong u ka la ing hir hir shaphang u para jong u, bad u la wad jaka ha kyndong ba un ïoh ïam; bad u la leit shapoh la ka kamra, bad u la ïam hangta.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda kumta, u la bta ïa la ka khmat, bad u la wan noh, bad u la kan ïa la ka mynsiem, bad u la ong, “To buh ïa ka jingbam.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kumta, ki la buh ïa ka jingbam ïa u kyrpang, bad ïa ki ruh kyrpang, bad ïa ki Ijipt kiba la ju bam ryngkat bad u ruh de, kyrpang; namar ki kynja Ijipt kim lah bam jingbam lem bad ki kynja Hebru; namar kata ka long kaba ijli da ki kynja Ijipt.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïashong ha khmat jong u ter ter, ïa uba la kha nyngkong katba kum ka jinglong hynmen jong u, bad u bakhatduh eh katba kum ka jinglong hynbew jong u: te kita ki briew ki la ïasngew lyngngoh paralok hi keiñ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> U ruh u la phah hi ïa ki pliang jingbam na khmat jong u sha ki: hynrei, ka pliang jingbam jong u Benjamin ka la tam san shah ïa kano kano na ki jong ki baroh. Kumta, ki la ïadih, bad ki la ïakhawai sngewbha bad u."
		},
		"44": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u la hukum ïa uba halor ka ïing jong u, u da ong, “To pyndap ïa ki byrni jong kine ki briew da ka jingbam, katba ki lah ban ngiam, bad to buh pat ruh ïa ki sbai ki jong uwei uwei ruh ha ka shyntur ka byrni jong u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad to thep ruh ïa u luta jong nga hi, ïa u luta rupa keiñ, ha ka byrni jong uta u bakhatduh na ki, ryngkat bad ki sbai u Kew jong u.” U ruh u la leh katba long ka ktien u Joseph ïa kaba u la lah kren.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ka la shai byrngut, bad ïa kita ki briew la pyllait noh, ma ki bad ki kadda jong ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Haba ki la poi shabar ka nongbah, te haba kim pat la jngai, u Joseph u la ong ha uba halor ka ïing jong u, “To ïeng, bad to khie leit beh hadien ïa kita ki briew; bad ynda me la lap ïa ki, to ong ha ki, ‘Hato balei ba phi la siew kylliang da ka basniew na ka bynta ka babha?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Une um long uta u luta na uba u kynrad jong nga u ju dih, bad da uba u lah ban khan shisha? Phi la leh sniew keiñ da kaba leh kumta.’ ”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U ruh u la lap ïa ki, bad u la kren ha ki ïa kine kijuh ki ktien.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Na ka balei ba u trai kynrad jong ngi u kren kum ïa kine ki ktien? Ban leh kum ïa kane ka kam, to ai ba kan long jngai na ki shakri jong me haba da lei lei ruh:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ha khmih, ïa ki sbai ba ngi la shem ha ki shyntur ki byrni jong ngi, ngi la wallam pat sha me naduh ka ri Kanaan: kumno te ngin da tuh ïa ka ksiar lane ïa ka rupa na ka ïing u kynrad jong me?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Uta na ki shakri jong me ha uba yn shem ïa uta u luta, to ai ba un ïap noh; ma ngi ruh ngin ïalong ki mraw ïa u trai kynrad jong nga.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “To ai ba kan long mynta kumba phi la ong: uta keiñ ha uba yn shem ïa uta u luta un long u shakri jong nga; hynrei, ma phi phin ïalong ba khlem jingrem.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïa-pynkloi noh bad ki la ïa-pynhiar noh uwei uwei ruh ïa la ka byrni byrni ha tbian, bad uwei uwei ruh u la plie ïa la ka byrni.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u la wad, da kaba sdang ha u banyngkong eh, bad u la wai ha u bakhatduh eh: bad u shem ïa uta u luta ha ka byrni jong u Benjamin.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la kad ïa la ki jaiñkup, bad ki la ïateh biang uwei uwei ruh ïa la ka jingkit halor ka kadda jong u, bad ki la ïaleit kylla noh pat sha kata ka nongbah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Judah u la wan bad ki para jong u sha ka ïing u Joseph; naba u dang sah hi hangta; bad ki la dem ha khmat jong u haduh ka khyndew.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ong ha ki, “Kaei kane ka jingleh ba phi la leh? Phim tip ba u briew kat ma nga u lah ban khan shisha?”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, u Judah u la ong, “Ngin ïa-ong aïu ha u trai kynrad jong nga? Hato ngin ïakren aïu? Bad kumno shisha ngin ïa-pynksan ïa lade? U Blei u la shem ïa ka kam bymhok ki shakri jong me: ha khmih, ngi long ki mraw ïa u kynrad jong nga, toi ma ngi ruh, bad uta ruh ha uba la shem ïa uta u luta.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U te u la ong, “Wat ai ba ngan leh ïa kata haba da lei lei ruh: uta u briew ha uba la shem ïa uta u luta, uta un long keiñ u mraw jong nga; hynrei, shaphang jong phi, to phin leit kiew ha ka jingsuk sha u kpa jong phi.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, u Judah u la kynshur hajan jong u, bad u la ong, “Ko kynrad, to shah, nga kyrpad ïa me, ïa u shakri jong me ban kren kawei ka ktien ha ki shkor u kynrad jong nga, bad to wat sngewbitar ïa la u shakri: naba me long kum u Pharaoh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U kynrad jong nga u la kylli ïa ki shakri jong u, u da ong, ‘Phi don u kpa, lane u para?’",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ngi ruh ngi la ïathuh ha u kynrad jong nga, ‘Ngi don u kpa uba la tymmen, bad u khun ka jinglong tymmen jong u, u bakhatduh eh; bad u hynmen jong u, u la ïap, bad la iehnoh marwei ïa u na ka kmie jong u, te u kpa jong u, u ieit eh ïa u.’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Me ruh me la ong ha ki shakri jong me, ‘To wallam arsut ïa u sha nga, ba ngan ïoh buh ïa ki khmat jong nga ha u.’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ngi la ïathuh ha u kynrad jong nga, ‘Uta u samla um lah iehnoh ïa la u kpa: naba lada un iehnoh ïa la u kpa, un da ïap noh u kpa jong u.’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ma me ruh me la ong ha ki shakri jong me, ‘Lymda wan hiar u para bakhatduh eh jong phi ryngkat bad phi, phin ym ïohi shuh ïa ka khmat jong nga.’",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ka la jia ruh ynda ngi la leit kiew sha u kpa jong nga u shakri jong me, ba ngi la ïathuh ha u ïa ki ktien u kynrad jong nga.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u kpa jong ngi u la ong, ‘To khie leit sa shi sien pat, to thied ïa ngi khyndiat ka jingbam.’",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, ngi la ong ma ngi, ‘Ngi ngim lah ban leit hiar: lada u para u bakhatduh eh u da don ryngkat bad ngi, te ngin ïaleit hiar keiñ; naba ngim lah ïoh khmih ïa ka khmat uta u rangbah, lymda don u para bakhatduh eh lem bad ngi.’",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u kpa jong nga, u shakri jong me, u la ong ha ngi, ‘Phi tip ba ka tnga jong nga ka la kha tang ar ngut ïa nga;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad uwei u la mih noh na nga, bad nga la ong, “Shisha shisha keiñ la patar lyngkhot lyngkhai ïa u; bad haduh mynta ruh ngam shym la ïohi shuh ïa u.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Mynta, lada phin shim noh ïa une de na khmat jong nga, bad lada kan jia ka basniew ei ei ruh ïa u, kumta phin ïa-pynhiar ïa ki 'ñiuhlieh jong nga sha ka jingtep da ka jingsngewsih.’",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Mynta te, haba nga poi ha u kpa jong nga, u shakri jong me, khlem da don une u samla bad ngi: haba la khum ïa ka mynsiem jong u lem bad une;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> kan sa jia haba u ïohi ba um shym wan une u samla ba un ïap noh shisha: bad ki shakri jong me kin ïa-pynhiar ïa ki 'ñiuhlieh u shakri jong me, u kpa jong ngi sha ka jingtep da ka jingsngewsih.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Naba u shakri jong me u la bahkhlieh na ka bynta une u samla ïa u kpa jong nga, nga da ong, ‘Lada ngam wallam ïa u sha me, nga la rem noh junom ha khmat u kpa jong nga.’",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Namar kata, mynta, nga kyrpad ïa me, ba u shakri jong me un ïoh shong mraw ïa u kynrad jong nga na ka bynta une u samla; to shah te ïa une u samla ban leit kiew noh ryngkat bad la ki hynmen.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Naba kumno ngan leit kiew ma nga sha la u kpa, lada une u samla um don lem bad nga? Ba ïoh ngan ïohi ïa ka jingsniew ka ban jia ha u kpa jong nga.”"
		},
		"45": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joseph um lah shah shuh ha khmat kita baroh kiba ïeng bad u; bad u la kyang, “To ai ba ki briew baroh kin mih noh na khmat jong nga.” Bad ym shym la don mano mano ruh hajan jong u, mynba u Joseph u la pynithuh ïa lade ha la ki hynmen hynbew.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la kyang da kaba ïam: bad ki Ijipt ki la ïohsngew, bad ka ïing u Pharaoh ruh ki la ïohsngew.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ong ha la ki hynmen hynbew, “Ma nga, nga long u Joseph; shisha u dang im u kpa jong nga?” Te ki hynmen jong u kim lah phai ktien shuh ïa u; naba ki la kyiuh eh ha khmat jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ong ha ki hynmen jong u, “To ïawan hajan ïa nga, nga kyrpad ïa phi.” Bad ki la ïawan hajan. Bad u la ong, “Ma nga, nga long u Joseph u para jong phi, ïa uba phi la die noh sha ka ri Ijipt.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, mynta, wat ïasngewsih shuh, bad wat ïasngewbitar ïa lade ruh, namar ba phi la die noh ïa nga shane: naba ïa ka ban pynim ïa ki mynsiem, U Blei u la phah ïa nga sha shuwa jong phi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Namar la lah don ar snem lypa na ka 'nemsniew hapoh kane ka ri: bad ki dang sah sa san snem, ha kiba yn ym don balur lane ba-ot.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad U Blei u la ïalam ïa nga keiñ ha shuwa jong phi ïa ka ban pynsah ïa kiba na phi ha ka khyndew, bad ïa ka ban pynim ïa phi da ka jingpyllait im bakhraw.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Mynta te, ym shym long ma phi ba la phah ïa nga shane, hynrei, U Blei hi keiñ: bad u la pynlong ïa nga kum u kpa ïa u Pharaoh, bad u trai halor ka ïing jong u baroh, bad u nongsynshar ha ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> To pynkloi noh, bad to khie leit kiew sha u kpa jong nga, bad to ïathuh ruh ha u, ‘Kumne u ong u khun jong me u Joseph, U Blei u la pynlong ïa nga u trai halor ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei: to wan hiar noh sha nga, to wat pynslem:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad men ïoh shong ha ka ri Goshen, bad men ïoh long hajan jong nga: ma me, bad ki khun jong me, bad ki khun ki khun jong me, bad ki kynhun jong me, bad ki masi jong me, bad baroh katba me don:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad hangta ngan bsa ïa me; naba ka 'nemsniew kan dang sah sa san snem; ba ïoh lap ka jingkyrduh ïa me, bad ïa ka ïing jong me, bad ïa baroh katba me don.’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ha khmih, ki khmat jong phi ki ïohi, bad ki khmat u para jong nga u Benjamin, ba ka shyntur jong nga hi ka long kaba kren ha phi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> To ïathuh ruh ha u kpa jong nga ïa ka burom jong nga baroh ha ka ri Ijipt, bad shaphang kiei kiei baroh katba phi la ïohi; to pynkloi noh ruh ïa ka ban ïalam arsut ïa u kpa jong nga shane.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la noh ïa lade ha ka ryndang u Benjamin u para jong u, bad u la ïam; bad u Benjamin ruh u la ïam ha ka ryndang jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la doh de ïa la ki hynmen baroh, bad u la ïam ruh halor jong ki: bad ynda kumta, ki hynmen jong u ki la ïakren bad u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad la bna ïa kata ha ïing u Pharaoh, ba la ong, “Ki hynmen u Joseph ki la wan.” Bad kata ka la bha ha khmat u Pharaoh, bad ha khmat ki shakri jong u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la ong ha u Joseph, “To ong ha la ki hynmen, ‘Ïa kane to phin leh; to pynkit ïa ki mrad jong phi, bad to khie leit noh ruh sha ka ri Kanaan:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad to ïalam ïa u kpa jong phi bad ïa kiba ha ki ïing jong phi de, bad to wan pat sha nga: bad ngan ai ha phi na ka jingbha ka ri Ijipt, bad phin ïoh bam ruh na ka khleiñ jong kane ka ri.’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Mynta me la lah ïoh ka hukum, ‘To leh ïa kane; to shim bad phi ïa ki kali na ka ri Ijipt ïa ki khun rit jong phi, bad ïa ki tnga jong phi, bad to wallam ïa la u kpa, bad to ïawan hiar noh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Wat ai ruh ba ki khmat jong phi kin ñiew ei ei ruh ïa la ki jingbuh jingsat; naba ka jingbha ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei ka long ïa phi keiñ.’ ”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Israel ki la leh kumta: bad u Joseph u la ai ha ki ïa ki kali, kumba u la hukum u Pharaoh, bad u la ai ïa ka jingbam ïa ki ha lynti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u la ai ha uwei uwei baroh da ki jaiñkup, shi kup shi kup ban ïapli; hynrei, ha u Benjamin u la ai laispah da ki sbai rupa, bad san riam da ki jaiñkup.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ïa la u kpa ruh u la phah lam kumne; ïa shiphew ki kadda ba la pynkit da kiei kiei kiba kham bha tam jong ka ri Ijipt, bad ïa shiphew ki kadda kynthei ba la pynkit da u Kew, bad u kpu, bad ka jingbam ba la khreh bang de ïa la u kpa hi baroh shi lynti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ynda kumta, u la pyllait noh ïa la ki hynmen hynbew, ki ruh ki la ïaleit noh: bad u la ong ha ki, “To wat ïamai ho ha kata ka lynti.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kumta, ki la ïaleit kiew noh na ka ri Ijipt, bad ki la wan sha ka ri Kanaan sha u Jakob u kpa jong ki.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad ki la ïathuh ha u, ki da ong, “U Joseph u dang im, bad u synshar halor ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei.” Bad ka dohnud jong u ka la jlep noh, naba um shym la ngeit shuh ïa ki.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ki la ïathuhkhana ha u ïa ki ktien baroh u Joseph, ïa kiba u la lah ong ha ki: bad haba u la ïohi ïa ki kali ïa kiba u Joseph u la lah phah lam ban kit ïa u, ynda kumta, ka mynsiem u Jakob u kpa jong ki ka la nang shait pat:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad u Israel u la ong, “Katta ka la biang; u Joseph u khun jong nga u dang im shisha: ngan leit ban ïohi ïa u shuwa ba ngan ïap.”"
		},
		"46": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Israel u la mih noh bad baroh katba u la don, bad u la wan poi ha Beer-sheba, bad u la ainguh da ki jingkñia ïa U Blei jong u Isaak u kpa jong u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad U Blei u la kren ha u Israel da ki jingithuhpaw mynmiet, bad u la ong, “Ko Jakob, Jakob.” U ruh u la ong, “Ha khmih ma nga.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la ong, “Nga long U Blei, U Blei u kpa jong me: wat sheptieng ban leit hiar sha ka ri Ijipt; naba ngan pynlong ïa me ka jaid bynriew bakhraw hangta.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngan leit hiar ryngkat bad me sha ka ri Ijipt; bad shisha nangta ruh ngan ïalam noh artet pat ïa me: bad u Joseph un ïoh buh ïa la ka kti halor ki khmat jong me.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Jakob u la mih noh na Beer-sheba: bad ki khun shynrang u Israel ki la wallam ïa u Jakob u kpa jong ki, bad la ki khun rit jong ki, bad ïa ki tnga jong ki, ha kita ki kali ïa kiba u Pharaoh u la lah phah lam ïa ka ban kit ïa ki.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ki la shim ïa la ki jingri ruh, bad ïa la ki jingbuh jingsat, ïa kiba ki la lah kamai ha ka ri Kanaan, bad ki la ïawan sha ka ri Ijipt, u Jakob, bad u symbai jong u baroh ryngkat bad u;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ki khun shynrang jong u bad ki khun shynrang jong ki khun shynrang jong u ryngkat bad u, ki khun kynthei, bad ki khun kynthei jong ki khun shynrang jong u, bad u symbai jong u baroh keiñ, u la ïalam bad u sha ka ri Ijipt.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad kine ki long ki kyrteng ki khun shynrang u Israel, kiba la wan sha ka ri Ijipt, u Jakob bad ki khun shynrang jong u: u Reuben, u khun nyngkong u Jakob.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Reuben: u Hanokh, bad u Pallu, bad u Hesron de, bad u Karmi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Simeon: u Jemuel, bad u Jamin, bad u Ohad, bad u Jakhin, bad u Sohar, bad u Shaul de, u khun ka kynja Kanaan.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Lebi: u Gershon, u Kohath, bad u Merari.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Judah: u Er, bad u Onan, bad u Shelah, bad u Phares, bad u Serah: hynrei, ki la ïap u Er bad u Onan ha ka ri Kanaan. Bad ki khun shynrang u Phares ki la long u Hesron bad u Hamul.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Issakhar: u Tola, bad u Puah, bad u Job, bad u Shimron.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Sabulon: u Sered, bad u Elon, bad u Jahlil.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kine ki long ki khun shynrang ki jong ka Leah, ïa kiba ka la kha ïa u Jakob ha Padan-Aram, bad ka Dinah ka khun jong ka: ki mynsiem baroh, ki khun shynrang bad ki khun kynthei jong u ki la long laiphew lai ngut.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Gad: u Siphion, bad u Haggi, u Shuni, bad u Esbon, u Eri, bad u Arodi, bad u Areli de.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Asher: u Jimnah, bad u Ishuah, bad u Isui, bad u Beriah, bad ka Serah ka para jong ki: bad ki khun shynrang u Beriah de; u Heber, bad u Malkhiel.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kine ki long ki khun shynrang ka Silpah, ïa kaba u Laban u la ai ïa ka Leah ka khun jong u, bad ka la kha ïa kine ïa u Jakob, khathynriew ngut ki mynsiem keiñ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki khun shynrang ka Rakhel, ka tnga u Jakob: u Joseph, bad u Benjamin.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ïa u Joseph ha ka ri Ijipt la kha ïa u Manasseh, bad ïa u Ephraim, ïa kiba la kha ka Asenath ka khun u Potipherah, u lyngdoh ka shnong On, ïa u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Benjamin: u Bela, u Bekher, bad u Ashbel, u Gera, bad u Naaman, u Ehi, bad u Rosh, u Muppim, bad u Huppim, bad u Ard.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kine ki long ki khun shynrang ki jong ka Rakhel, ïa kiba la kha ïa u Jakob: baroh ki la long khatsaw ki mynsiem.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang ki jong u Dan: u Hushim.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Naphtali: u Jahsil, bad u Guni, bad u Jeser, bad u Shillem.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kine ki long ki khun shynrang ka Bilhah, ïa kaba u Laban u la ai ïa ka Rakhel ka khun jong u: bad ka la kha ïa kine ïa u Jakob; baroh ki la long hynñiew ki mynsiem.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Baroh kiba la leit bad u Jakob sha ka ri Ijipt, kiba la mih na ka syngkai jong u hi, bad ki tnga ki khun shynrang u Jakob de, baroh keiñ ki la long hynriewphew hynriew ki mynsiem.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Joseph, ïa kiba la kha ïa u ha ka ri Ijipt, ki la long ar ngut: kumta ki mynsiem baroh kiba dei ïa ka ïing u Jakob kiba la leit wan sha ka ri Ijipt, ki long hynñiewphew ngut.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u Jakob u la phah ïa u Judah sha shuwa jong u sha u Joseph, ba un ïalam lynti ha khmat jong u sha ka ri Goshen; bad kumta ki la ïapoi sha ka ri Goshen.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u Joseph u la pynkhreh ïa la ka kali, bad u la leit kiew ban tan ïa u Israel u kpa jong u, sha ka ri Goshen, bad u la pynpaw ïa lade ha u; bad u la noh ha ka ryndang jong u, bad u la ïam slem ha ka ryndang jong u.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Israel u la ong ha u Joseph, “To ngan wat ïap mynta, ynda nga la ïohi ïa ka khmat jong me, ba me dang im shisha.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ong ïa la ki para, bad ïa ka ïing u kpa jong u, “Ngan leit kiew ban ïathuh ha u Pharaoh, bad ngan ong ha u, ‘Ki hynmen hynbew jong nga, bad ka ïing u kpa jong nga, kiba la ju don ha ka ri Kanaan, ki la poi ha nga;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> bad kine ki briew ki long ki nongsharai langbrot, naba ki la ju long kiba buh jingri; bad ïa la ki kynhun, bad ïa la ki jingri, bad ïa baroh katba ki don, ki la ïawallam ryngkat bad ki.’",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad kan jia ruh haba u Pharaoh un khot ïa phi, bad ba un ong de, ‘Kaei ka kam jong phi?’",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te phin ïathuh, ‘Ki shakri jong me ki la ju long kiba ri jingri naduh ba ngi dang long samla haduh mynta, ma ngi ruh bad ki kpa tymmen jong ngi:’ ba phin ïoh shong duh keiñ ha ka ri Goshen; naba u kynja nongsharai langbrot baroh u long ka jingijli ha ki Ijipt.”"
		},
		"47": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joseph u la wan ïathuh ha u Pharaoh, bad u la ong, “U kpa jong nga bad ki hynmen hynbew jong nga, bad ki kynhun jong ki, bad ki masi jong ki, bad baroh katba ki don, ki la ïawan noh na ka ri Kanaan; bad ha khmih, ki ïadon hi ha ka ri Goshen.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la ïalam bad u kiba na ki hynmen jong u, kat san ngut, bad u la buh ïa ki ha khmat u Pharaoh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la ong ha ki hynmen jong u, “Kaei ka kam jong phi?” Ki te ki la ïathuh ha u Pharaoh, “Ki shakri jong me ki long ki nongsharai langbrot, ma ngi ruh bad ki kpa tymmen jong ngi de.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki la ïathuh ruh ha u Pharaoh, “Ïa ka ban shong sohsyiem ha kane ka ri ngi la ïawan; namar ba ki shakri jong me kim don jaka bam phlang ïa la ki kynhun; naba kane ka 'nemsniew ka la jur eh ha ka ri Kanaan: bad mynta, ngi kyrpad ïa me, to shah ba ki shakri jong me kin ïashong sah ha ka ri Goshen.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la kren ha u Joseph, u da ong, “U kpa jong me bad ki hynmen hynbew jong me ki la ïawan sha me.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ka ri Ijipt ka long ha khmat jong me; to pynshong sah ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ki hynmen hynbew ha ka jaka ka babha tam ha ka ri; to kin ïashong sah ha ka ri Goshen: bad lada me tip ba don hapdeng jong ki, ki briew kiba nang, to buh ïa ki te ki nongsharai barangbah halor ki jingri jong nga hi.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ïalam hapoh sa ïa u Jakob u kpa jong u, bad u la buh ïa u ha khmat u Pharaoh: bad u Jakob u la kyrkhu ïa u Pharaoh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la ong ha u Jakob, “Katno ki long ki sngi ki snem ka rta jong me?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Jakob u la ong ha u Pharaoh, “Ki sngi ki snem ka jingïaid ka jingim jong nga ki long shispah laiphew snem: ki sngi ki snem ka jingim jong nga ki la long kiba khyndiat bad ki basniew, bad kim pat kot ïa ki sngi ki snem ka jingim ki kpa jong nga, kumba ha ki sngi ki snem ka jingïaid ka jingim jong ki.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Jakob u la kyrkhu ïa u Pharaoh, bad u la mih noh na khmat u Pharaoh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Joseph u la pynshong neh ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ki hynmen hynbew, bad u la ai ha ki, ïa ka bynta trai ha ka ri Ijipt, ha ka jaka kaba kham bha tam, ha ka khyndew Rameses, kumba u Pharaoh u la lah ai hukum.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Joseph u la bsa ïa la u kpa, bad ïa la ki hynmen hynbew, bad ïa ka ïing u kpa jong u baroh, da u kpu, katba kum ki ba-ha-ïing jong ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ym shym don ka jingbam ha kata ka ri baroh kawei; naba kata ka 'nemsniew ka la jur eh, katba ka ri Ijipt bad ka ri Kanaan ki la kumba ïapler namar kata ka 'nemsniew.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ïalum ïa ki sbai baroh ïa kiba la ïoh shem ha ka ri Ijipt, bad ha ka ri Kanaan, na ka bynta u Kew ba ki la thied: bad u Joseph u la wallam ïa kita ki sbai sha ïing u Pharaoh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ynda la lah lut ki sbai ha ka ri Ijipt, bad ha ka ri Kanaan, ki kynja Ijipt baroh ki la leit sha u Joseph, ki da ong, “To ai jingbam ïa ngi: naba balei ngin ïap ha khmat jong me? namar ki sbai ki la lut noh.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u Joseph u la ong, “To ai noh ïa la ki jingri; bad ngan ai ha phi na ka bynta ki jingri jong phi, lada la lut noh ki sbai.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la wallam ïa la ki jingri ha u Joseph: bad u Joseph u la ai ïa u kpu ha ki na ka bynta ki kulai, bad na ka bynta ki kynhun langbrot, bad na ka bynta ki kynhun masi, bad na ka bynta ki kadda de: bad u la bsa ïa ki da ka jingbam na ka bynta ki jingri baroh jong ki ha kata ka snem.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda la lah kata ka snem, ki la ïawan ha u ha kawei pat ka snem kaba mih, bad ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Ngin ym buhrieh na u kynrad jong ngi ba ki la lah lut noh ki sbai; bad ki jingri ruh ki la long ki jong u kynrad jong ngi; ym sah shuh ei ei ruh ha khmat u kynrad jong ngi, sa tang ki met jong ngi, bad ka khyndew jong ngi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ka balei ngin ïap noh ha khmat jong me, ma ngi ruh bad ka khyndew jong ngi? To da thied ïa ngi bad ïa ka khyndew jong ngi da ka jingbam, bad ma ngi bad ka khyndew jong ngi ngin long ki shakri jong u Pharaoh: bad to ai symbai ha ngi, ba ngin ïoh im, bad ba ngin ym ïap noh, bad ba ka khyndew kan ym kylla khlaw noh.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumta, u Joseph u la thied ïa ka khyndew baroh ka ri Ijipt ïa u Pharaoh; naba kita ki Ijipt ki la die noh uwei uwei ruh baroh ïa la ka lyngkha, naba kata ka 'nemsniew ka la nang kham jur halor jong ki: kumta ka khyndew ka la hap ha u Pharaoh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ïa u paidlang, ruh u la pynkynriah sha ki nongbah na kawei ka bakut sha kawei pat ka bakut jong ka ri Ijipt.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Tang ïa ka khyndew jong ki lyngdoh ym shym la thied; naba kita ki lyngdoh ki la ïoh ïa la ka jingsam na u Pharaoh, bad ki la ïabam na kata ka bynta ïa kaba u Pharaoh u la ai ha ki: namar kata, kim shym la die ïa la ka khyndew.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joseph u la ong ha uta u paidlang, “Ha khmih, nga la thied ïa phi mynta bad ïa ka khyndew jong phi ïa u Pharaoh: ha khmih, une u symbai ïa phi, to phin bet symbai ruh ha ka khyndew.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kan jia ruh haba u la mih, ba phin ai ïa kaba san bynta ha u Pharaoh, bad saw bynta kin long ki jong phi hi, ïa ka ban ïoh symbai ïa ka khyndew, bad ban ïoh jingbam ïa phi, bad ïa kita ki ba-ha-ïing jong phi, bad ïa ka ban ïoh ka jingbam ïa ki khun khynnah jong phi de.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki la ïa-ong, “Me la ri pynim ïa ngi: to shah ba ngin shem ka jingsngewbha ha khmat u kynrad jong ngi, bad ma ngi ruh ngin long ki shakri jong u Pharaoh.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Joseph u la pynlong ba kata kan long ka rukom haduh kane ka sngi halor ka khyndew ka ri Ijipt, ba u Pharaoh un ïoh ïa kaba san bynta; hynrei, tang ka khyndew jong ki lyngdoh, ka bym shym la hap ha u Pharaoh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U Israel ruh u la shong duh ha ka ri Ijipt, ha ka khyndew Goshen; bad ki la ïoh ki bynta trai ha ka, bad ki la ïaman bha, bad ki la ïa nang roi shikatdei eh ruh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U Jakob ruh u la im ha ka ri Ijipt khathynñiew snem: kumta, ki sngi ka rta jong u Jakob, ki snem ka jingim jong u keiñ ki la long shispah sawphew hynñiew snem.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ki sngi jong u Israel ki la nang jan ba un ïap noh: te u la khot ïa u Joseph u khun jong u, bad u la ong ha u, “Lada mynta nga la shem ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong me, to buh, nga kyrpad ïa me, ïa la ka kti hapoh ka skhep jong nga, bad to pyni ïa nga ïa ka jingsngewbha bad ïa ka jingshisha; to wat tep ïa nga, nga kyrpad ïa me, ha ka ri Ijipt:",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> hynrei, ngan ïohthiah bad ki kpa jong nga, te men pynbah noh ïa nga na ka ri Ijipt, bad to men tep ïa nga ha ka jingtep jong ki.” U ruh u la ong, “Ngan leh keiñ kat kumba ka long ka ktien jong me.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u la ong, “To smai ha nga.” U te u la smai ha u. Ynda kumta, u Israel u la dem ha khlieh ka jingthiah."
		},
		"48": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ka la jia ruh, ynda la lah kine kiei kiei ruh, ba uwei u la leit ïathuh ha u Joseph, “Ha khmih, u kpa jong me u pang:” ynda kumta, u la shim ïa ki khun shynrang jong u baroh ar ngut lem bad u, u Manasseh bad u Ephraim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad uwei ruh u la ïathuh ha u Jakob de, u la ong, “Ha khmih, u Joseph u khun jong me u wan sha me:” te u Israel u la pynshait ïa lade, bad u la shong ha ka jingthiah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Jakob u la ong ha u Joseph, “U Blei U Badonbor Baroh u la mihpaw ha nga ha Lus ha ka ri Kanaan, bad u la kyrkhu ïa nga,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> u la ong ruh ha nga, ‘Ha khmih, ngan pynlong ïa me uba sei soh kyrhai, bad ngan nang pynroi ïa me, bad ngan pynlong ïa me ka jaid bynriew babun paidbah; bad ngan ai ïa kane ka khyndew ïa u symbai jong me hadien jong me ba kan long ka bynta trai junom.’",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad mynta ki khun jong me baroh ar ngut, ïa kiba la kha ïa me ha ka ri Ijipt mynshuwa ba nga la poi sha me sha ka ri Ijipt, kin long ki jong nga: u Ephraim bad u Manasseh kin long ki jong nga, kum u Reuben bad u Simeon.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ki khun jong me, ïa kiba men pynkha hadien jong ki, kin long ki jong me hi, bad yn sa khot ïa ki ha ka kyrteng la ki hynmen ha ka jingïoh bynta trai jong ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ynda nga la wan na Padan-Aram, ka Rakhel ka la ïap noh bad nga ha ka ri Kanaan ha lynti, haba dang don sa shi mail ka lynti haduh Ephrath: bad nga la tep ïa ka hangta ha ka lynti jong ka Ephrath; kaba long ka Bethlehem.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Israel u la ïohi ïa ki khun shynrang u Joseph, bad u la ong, “Kiei kine?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ïathuh ha la u kpa, “Kine ki khun shynrang jong nga, ïa kiba U Blei u la ai ha nga shane.” Ynda kumta, u la ong, “To wallam ïa ki sha nga, nga kyrpad ïa me, bad ma nga, ngan kyrkhu ïa ki.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ki khmat u Israel ki la ïabyrngut namar ba la tymmen, katba um lah imat shuh: bad u la wallam ïa ki hajan jong u; bad u la doh ïa ki, bad u la kdup ïa ki ruh de.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Israel u la ong ruh ha u Joseph, “Ngam shym la ngeit ba ngan ïohi ïa ka khmat jong me shuh: te ha khmih, U Blei u la pyni ha nga ïa u symbai jong me ruh putet.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Joseph u la pynmih noh ïa ki napdeng ki khohsiew jong u, bad u la nguh haduh ka khyndew ha khmat jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U Joseph ruh u la shim ïa ki baroh ar ngut, ïa u Ephraim ha la ka kti kamon shaphang ka kti kadiang jong u Israel, bad ïa u Manasseh ha ka kti kadiang jong u shaphang ka kti kamon jong u Israel, bad u la wallam ïa ki hajan jong u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Israel u la kner ïa la ka kti kamon, bad u la buh ïa ka halor ka khlieh u Ephraim, uba long u bakhatduh, bad ïa la ka kti kadiang halor ka khlieh u Manasseh, u da ïalam tipbriew ïa la ki kti de; naba u Manasseh u la long u khun nyngkong.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la kyrkhu ïa u Joseph, bad u la ong, “U Blei uba ha khmat jong u ki la ïaid ki kpa jong nga, u Abraham bad u Isaak, uta U Blei uba la bsa ïa nga naduh ba nga la long haduh kane ka sngi,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> uta u angel uba la pyllait im ïa nga na ka basniew baroh, un kyrkhu ïa kine ki samla; ïa ka kyrteng jong nga ruh bad ka kyrteng ki kpa jong nga u Abraham bad u Isaak, yn sa khot ha ki; to ai ba kin ïakha roi ruh kum ki dohkha ha ka jingbun hapdeng kata ka ri.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Joseph haba u la ïohi ba u kpa jong u, u buh ïa ka kti kamon jong u halor ka khlieh u Ephraim, ka la pynsngewsih ïa u: bad u la bat ïa ka kti u kpa jong u, ïa ka ban pynkynriah ïa ka na ka khlieh u Ephraim sha ka khlieh u Manasseh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U Joseph u la ong ruh ha la u kpa, “Ym kumta, ko kpa: naba une u long u khun nyngkong; to buh ïa la ka kti kamon halor ka khlieh jong u.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u kpa jong u, u la kyrngah bad u la ong, “Nga tip ma nga, ko khun, nga tip ma nga: une ruh un long u paidbah, bad un long u bakhraw une ruh de: hynrei, shisha u para uba hadien jong u un long uba kham khraw ïa u, bad u symbai jong u un long ka jingpyndap ki jaid bynriew.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u la kyrkhu ïa ki ha kata ka sngi, u da ong, “Ha me u kynja Israel un kyrkhu, u da ong, ‘U Blei un pynlong ïa me kum u Ephraim bad kum u Manasseh:’ ” Bad u la buh ïa u Ephraim ha shuwa ïa u Manasseh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U Israel u la ong ruh ha u Joseph, “Ha khmih, ngan sa ïap noh: hynrei, U Blei un long ryngkat bad phi, bad un ïalam pat ïa phi sha ka ri ki kpa jong phi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad nga la ai ha me kawei ka bynta tam nalor ki hynmen hynbew jong me, ïa kaba nga la knieh na ka kti ki kynja Amor da la ka waitlam bad da la ka ryntieh.”"
		},
		"49": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jakob u la khot ïa la ki khun shynrang, bad u la ong, “To ïalang hajuh, ba ngan ïathuh ha phi kaei kan jia ïa phi ha ki sngi ki ban sa wan.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To ïalang hajuh, bad to sngew phi ki khun shynrang u Jakob; ho-oid keiñ, to sngew ïa u Israel u kpa jong phi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “U Reuben, me u khun nyngkong jong nga, ka jingkhlaiñ jong nga, bad ka jingsdang ka bor jong nga, ka jingbha tam ka burom, bad ka jingbha tam ka bor:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> uba kyrsoi thnam kum ka um, men ym long uba kham donnam tam; naba me la kiew sha ka jingthiah u kpa jong me; bad kumta, me la pyntngit ïa ka: sha ka jingthiah jong nga keiñ u la kiew.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “U Simeon bad u Lebi ki ïalong shipara; ki tiar ka jingleh-jubor ki long ki waitlam jong ki.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Wat ai ba ka mynsiem jong nga kan wan hapoh ka jingïasylla jong ki: ka burom jong nga kan ym ïasoh bad ka jingïalang jong ki: naba ha la ka jingbitar ki la pynïap ïa u briew, bad ha la ka jingmon pathar hi ki la ot noh ïa ki masi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Long ba la tim ïa ka jingbitar jong ki, naba ka la sat eh; bad ïa ka jingpynhiar kput jong ki, naba ka la i runar eh: ngan pynïakhlad ïa ki ha u Jakob, bad ngan pynsaphred ïa ki ha Israel.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Ma me u Judah, ki para jong me kin ïaroh ïa me: ka kti jong me kan long ha ka ryndang ki nongshun jong me; ki khun u kpa jong me kin nguh ngon ïa me.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Judah u long u khun sing: na ka jinglute, ko khun, me la wan kiew: u la dem, u la thiah kum u sing, bad kum ka sing kmie; uei u ban kyrsiew ïa u?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U dieng synshar un ym kynriah na u Judah, lymne u nongthaw aiñ napdeng ki sla'jat jong u, ha ban da wan u Shiloh; bad ïa u ki jaid bynriew kin ïakohnguh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U da teh ïa la ka kadda khynraw ha u dieng soh Waiñ, bad ïa la i khun kadda ha u dieng soh Waiñ u babha tam; u la sait ïa la ki jaiñ ha ka umsoh, bad ïa la ka barandi ha ka snam ki soh Waiñ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U saw la ki khmat na ka umsoh, bad u lieh la ki bniat na ka dud.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “U Sabulon un shong harud ka duriaw; bad un long ïa ka jaka rieh ki lieng bah, bad ka pud jong u kan long haduh Sidon.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “U Issakhar u long u kadda uba shong dem ryngkhung ba dem hapdeng ar tylli ki jingkit:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ynda u la ïohi ba kaba jahthait ka long ka babha, bad ïa ka khyndew ba ka long kaba itynnad; un pyndem ïa la ka tyrpeng ban bah, bad un long uba shakri hapoh ka khajna.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “U Dan un bishar ïa la ki briew, kum uwei na ki jaid Israel.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Dan un long u bseiñ ha ka lynti bah, bad u 'seiñ tyrnem ha ka lynti khlaw, uba puh ïa ka khongdong'jat u kulai, katba un kyllon da dien u trai bashong.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nga la khmih kyrmen ïa ka jingpynim jong me, A Trai.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “U Gad, ka kynhun bah kan ban ïa u: te u un ban ha ka bakhatduh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “U Asher, ka khleiñ kan long ka jingbam jong u, bad un sei ki soh bashngiam rai rai ba bit ïa u syiem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “U Naphtali u long ka skei ba la pyllait: u kren ki ktien ba sngewtynnad.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “U Joseph un long ka tnat basei soh byrhien, ka tnat basei soh byrhien harud ka pukri, ki tnat jong u kin pur ïa ka kynroh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ki nongsiat khnam ki la pynsngewsih sat ïa u bad ki la ïasiat, bad ki la behbeiñ ïa u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, ka ryntieh jong u pynban ka la neh bor, bad ki ksang'ti jong u ki la nang kham khlaiñ da ki kti jong U Bakhrawbor u Jakob; (nangta u long u Nongsharai, u Mawsiang jong u Israel),",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> da U Blei u kpa jong me keiñ, u ban ïarap ïa me, bad U Badonbor Baroh, u ban kyrkhu ïa me da ki jingkyrkhu ka bneng na jrong, bad da ki jingkyrkhu kiba jylliew ba long shapoh, bad da ki jingkyrkhu ki jymbuiñ bad jong ka kpoh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki jingkyrkhu u kpa jong me kiba kham bha ïa ki jingkyrkhu ki kmie ki kpa jong nga haduh ka bakut ki lum ki bymjukut: kin long ha ka khlieh u Joseph, bad ha ka shynrong khlieh uta ïa uba la pynkyrpang na la ki para.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “U Benjamin un lute kum u suri: mynstep un bam duh ïa ka jinglute, bad mynmiet un sam ïa kaba la lah lute.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kine ki long ki khat-ar jaid Israel baroh: bad kane ka long ba la kren u kpa jong ki ha ki, bad u la kyrkhu ïa ki; uwei uwei ruh katba kum ka jingkyrkhu jong u, u la kyrkhu ïa ki.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ynda kumta, u la hukum ïa ki, bad u la ong ha ki, “Ïa nga yn sa lum sha la ki briew; to tep ïa nga bad ki kpa jong nga ha ka krem kaba ha ka lyngkha u Ephron u kynja Hit,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ha kata ka krem kaba ha ka lyngkha Makhpelah, kaba marpyrshah ïa ka Mamre, ha ka ri Kanaan, ïa kaba u Abraham u la thied lem bad ka lyngkha na u Ephron u kynja Hit, ïa ka ban long ka bynta trai kum ka jaka tep.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hangta ki la ïatep ïa u Abraham bad ïa ka Sara ka tnga jong u; hangta ki la ïatep ïa u Isaak bad ïa ka Rebekka ka tnga jong u; bad hangta ruh nga la tep ïa ka Leah:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> kata ka lyngkha keiñ bad ka krem hapoh jong ka, ïa kaba la thied na ki khun u Heth.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ynda u Jakob u la wai noh ban hukum ïa la ki khun shynrang, u la ring ïa la ki kjat sha ka jingthiah bad u la ïap, bad la ïalum ïa u sha la ki briew."
		},
		"50": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Joseph u la noh ha ka khmat u kpa jong u, bad u la ïam halor jong u, bad u la doh ïa u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Joseph u la hukum ïa ki nongpynkhiah kiba long ki shakri jong u ba kin kyllan masla ïa u kpa jong u: te kita ki nongpynkhiah ki la kyllan masla ïa u Israel.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad la pyndep ïa ki sawphew sngi ïa u; naba kumta ki ju pyndep ïa ki sngi jong kita ïa kiba ki kyllan masla: ynda kumta, ki Ijipt ki la ïaïambriew ïa u hynñiewphew sngi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ynda la dep kita ki sngi ka jingïambriew ïa u, u Joseph u la kren ha kita kiba na ka ïing u Pharaoh, u da ong, “Lada mynta nga la shem ka jingsbun ha khmat jong phi, to da kren ha u Pharaoh, nga kyrpad ïa phi, da ong,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> u kpa jong nga u la pynsmai ïa nga, u da ong, ‘Ha khmih, ngan sa ïap noh: ha ka jingtep jong nga ïa kaba nga la tih ïa lade hi keiñ ha ka ri Kanaan, hangta men tep ïa nga.’ Bad mynta to shah, nga kyrpad ïa me, ba ngan leit kiew khnang ban ïoh tep ïa u kpa jong nga, hadien kata, ngan wan phai pat.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la ong, “To khie leit kiew, bad to tep ïa u kpa jong me, kumba u la pynsmai ïa me.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joseph u la leit kiew ïa ka ban tep ïa la u kpa: bad ki shakri jong u Pharaoh baroh, ki bakhraw batri ka ïing jong u, bad ki bakhraw batri baroh jong ka ri Ijipt, ki la ïaleit kiew ryngkat bad u,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad ka ïing u Joseph baroh, bad ki hynmen hynbew jong u, bad ka ïing u kpa jong u: hynrei, tang ïa la ki barit bad ïa la ki kynhun langbrot bad ïa la ka jingri, ki la iehnoh ha ka ri Goshen.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad la leit kiew ryngkat bad u ki kali ïapom, bad ki riewshong kulai ruh de: ka la long ka jingïalang briew bakhraw eh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba ki la ïapoi ha ka pynthor Atad, kaba sha shiliang ka Jordan, ki la ïa-pynlong hangta ïa ka jingïambriew ka bakhraw bad kaba jur: namar u la pynlong ka jingïambriew na ka bynta u kpa jong u hynñiew sngi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ki kynja Kanaan kiba shong sah ha kata ka ri, ynda ki la ïohi ïa kata ka jingïambriew ha ka kyntem ka pynthor Atad, ki la ïa-ong, “Kane ka bakhraw ka jingïambriew ka jong ki Ijipt:” namar kata, ki la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “Ka Abel-Misraim”, kaba sha shiliang ka Jordan.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kumta, ki khun shynrang u Jakob ki la leh ïa u kumba u la hukum ïa ki;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> naba ki khun shynrang jong u ki la ïawallam noh ïa u sha ka ri Kanaan, bad ki la ïatep ïa u hapoh ka krem kaba ha ka lyngkha ka Makhpelah, ïa kaba u Abraham u la lah thied lem bad ka lyngkha, ïa ka ban long ka jaka jingtep, na u Ephron u kynja Hit, marpyrshah ïa ka Mamre.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Joseph, ynda u la lah tep ïa la u kpa, u la leit phai pat sha ka ri Ijipt: ma u bad ki hynmen hynbew jong u, bad baroh kat kiba la leit kiew ryngkat bad u ïa ka ban tep ïa u kpa jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ki hynmen jong u Joseph ynda ki la ïohi ba u la ïap u kpa jong ki, ki la ïa-ong, “Lehse mynta u Joseph un isih ïa ngi, bad un siew kylliang pat kaba biang ïa ngi ïa kata ka basniew baroh ïa kaba ngi la leh ïa u.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Namar kata, ki la ïaphah ïathuh ha u Joseph, “U kpa jong me u la bthah mynshuwa ba u la ïap, u da ong,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ‘Kumne phin ong ha u Joseph, “To map noh, nga kyrpad ïa me mynta, ïa ka jingpalat ki hynmen jong me, bad ïa ka pop jong ki; naba ki la ïaleh bymman ïa me; te mynta, to map noh, nga kyrpad ïa me, ïa ka jingpalat ki shakri jong U Blei u kpa jong me.” ’ ” Bad u Joseph u la ïam haba ki la ïakren ha u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki hynmen jong u ki la wan bad ki la dem ngon ha khmat jong u; bad ki la ïa-ong, “Ha khmih, ngi long ki shakri ïa me.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ïathuh ha ki, “Wat sheptieng; naba hato nga long ma nga ha ka jaka jong U Blei?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Phi shisha, phi la lah thmu ïa ka basniew pyrshah ïa nga; hynrei U Blei u la thmu ïa ka, ïa ka ban pynbha, ïa ka ban pynlong ka lad, kumba ka long ha kane ka sngi, ïa ka ban pynim ïa ki paidbah babun.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Namar kata, mynta, wat sheptieng: ngan ri bsa ïa phi, bad ïa ki barit jong phi.” Bad u la pyntngen ïa ki, bad u la kren pynsngewbha ïa ka dohnud jong ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumta, u Joseph u la shong sah ha ka ri Ijipt: ma u bad ka ïing u kpa jong u. Bad u Joseph u la im shispah shiphew snem.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u Joseph u la ïohi ïa la ki ksiew ar pateng ksiew ruh na u Ephraim: bad la ri bsa ïa ki khun u Makhir u khun u Manasseh ruh ha ki khohsiew u Joseph.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u Joseph u la ong ha ki hynmen hynbew jong u, “Nga te ngan sa ïap noh: hynrei, U Blei shisha un wan khmih ïa phi, bad un ïalam noh ïa phi na kane ka ri sha kata ka ri ïa kaba u la smai ha u Abraham, ha u Isaak, bad ha u Jakob.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Joseph u la pynsmai ïa ki khun shynrang u Israel, u da ong, “U Blei shisha un wan khmih ïa phi, bad phin lam noh artad ïa ki shyieng jong nga na kane ka ri.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kumta, u Joseph u la ïap, uba shispah shiphew snem ka rta: bad ki la kyllan masla ïa u, bad la buh ïa u ha ka synduk tep briew ha ka ri Ijipt."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;